2
00:06:10,24 --> 00:06:12,43
你一个师爷敢冒充县长？
You dare to impersonate the Governor?

3
00:07:38,40 --> 00:07:40,03
那就要看你的本事了
That's all up to you.

4
00:07:41,84 --> 00:07:44,43
师爷，当夫妻最要紧的是什么？
What's important for a couple?

5
00:07:44,64 --> 00:07:45,59
恩爱！
In love.

6
00:07:45,76 --> 00:07:47,35
听不见，再说一遍
I can't hear you.

7
00:07:47,60 --> 00:07:48,71
恩爱！
In love.

8
00:07:48,88 --> 00:07:50,02
来，见过母亲大人
Six, come greet your Mom.

9
00:07:50,20 --> 00:07:52,39
母亲大人好，小六子有礼了！
I wish you well, Mother.

10
00:07:52,60 --> 00:07:54,59
你出生入死，还带着儿子啊？
You bring your son to battles?

11
00:07:54,76 --> 00:07:56,83
他爹是我的兄弟，阵亡了
His father was a comrade. Died in battle.

12
00:07:57,00 --> 00:07:58,87
所以他就成了我的儿子
So I adopted him as my god son.

13
00:07:59,04 --> 00:08:01,11
所以呢，你现在就是我的母亲大人！
Now you're my mother.

14
00:08:01,28 --> 00:08:02,26
等这桩买卖做完后
After we're done with Goose Town,

15
00:01:25,68 --> 00:01:28,14
“天之涯”
"To the end of horizon,"

16
00:01:28,68 --> 00:01:31,55
“地之角”
"four corners of Earth,"

17
00:01:31,92 --> 00:01:37,35
“知交半零落”
"scattered one's true friends"

18
00:01:37,56 --> 00:01:43,35
“一壶浊酒尽余欢”
"A bottle of wine for remaining joy,"

19
00:01:43,56 --> 00:01:48,79
“夕阳山外山”
"as sun sets among the mountains."

20
00:01:48,96 --> 00:01:50,67
好，好好
Brilliant...

21
00:01:50,84 --> 00:01:51,71
汤师爷
Counselor!

22
00:01:51,92 --> 00:01:53,51
是好吃，还是好听？
You prefer the food or my singing?

23
00:01:53,68 --> 00:01:55,59
也好听，也好吃
I love them both!

24
00:01:55,76 --> 00:01:57,55
都好，都好！
Outstanding!

25
00:01:57,72 --> 00:02:00,10
我马某走南闯北
Brain and brawn have helped me far,

26
00:02:00,28 --> 00:02:03,75
靠的就是能文能武，与众不同
that's why I am so unique!

27
00:02:03,92 --> 00:02:08,03
不光吃喝玩乐，更要雪月风花
One must learn to live in style!

28
00:02:11,96 --> 00:02:14,83
马县长此番风度
Governor, with your style and poise,

29
00:02:15,16 --> 00:02:16,75
正好比
you remind me of...

30
00:02:16,96 --> 00:02:22,27
大风起兮云飞扬
a modern-day Robin Hood!

31
00:02:22,64 --> 00:02:23,43
屁！
Bullshit!

32
00:02:23,64 --> 00:02:24,91
刘邦是个小人！
Robin Hood is a common thief!

33
00:02:25,08 --> 00:02:27,99
力拔山兮气盖世
with Samson's might and Solomon's wisdom!

34
00:02:28,16 --> 00:02:29,67
屁！ 屁，屁
- Bullshit! - Yes, bullshit!

35
00:02:29,84 --> 00:02:30,79
汤师爷
Counselor,

36
00:02:30,96 --> 00:02:33,03
你要是拍我马屁
if you're trying to flatter me,

37
00:02:33,20 --> 00:02:35,76
就先要先过夫人这一关
you must first woo my wife!

38
00:02:36,96 --> 00:02:38,23
写首诗，写首诗！
Compose a poem in her honour.

39
00:02:38,40 --> 00:02:41,23
要有风，要有肉
It must have a tempest, food,

40
00:02:41,40 --> 00:02:43,59
要有火锅，要有雾
a hotpot, some mist,

41
00:02:43,76 --> 00:02:46,59
要有美女，要有驴！
pretty maidens, and a mule!

42
00:02:58,44 --> 00:02:59,39
起来，起来，起来
Get up!

43
00:02:59,60 --> 00:03:00,99
一起吃！一起唱！
Let's eat, sing and be merry!

44
00:03:01,16 --> 00:03:03,91
报告县长！我们铁血十八星陆军
Sir, we are the elite Republican Guards,

45
00:03:04,08 --> 00:03:05,83
护送县长安全上任！
here to ensure your safe passage!

46
00:03:06,00 --> 00:03:06,79
我们…
We -

47
00:03:07,00 --> 00:03:08,63
不吃饭！
don't - need - to - eat!

48
00:03:18,00 --> 00:03:18,98
没打中？
You missed?

49
00:03:20,64 --> 00:03:22,11
让子弹飞一会儿
Let the bullets fly...

50
00:03:33,44 --> 00:03:34,50
老二老三跟我走
Two and Three come with me.

51
00:03:34,68 --> 00:03:36,19
其他人把白马抓回来！
The rest round up the horses.

52
00:04:51,72 --> 00:04:52,78
火锅？
Raining hot pot?

53
00:05:05,20 --> 00:05:06,79
爹，全都找遍了
Pop, we've looked all over.

54
00:05:07,00 --> 00:05:09,75
没钱，没货，也没有银子
There is absolutely nothing!

55
00:05:10,04 --> 00:05:12,23
人倒是剩两活的，杀不杀？
Should we just kill the two survivors?

56
00:05:18,96 --> 00:05:20,75
钱藏在哪儿了？说出来
Tell me where the money is?

57
00:05:21,24 --> 00:05:22,79
闹钟响之前要是说不出来
Or I'll cut off your head,

58
00:05:22,96 --> 00:05:23,83
脑袋搬家
when the alarm goes off.

59
00:05:26,72 --> 00:05:27,78
哭？
Stop it!

60
00:05:28,28 --> 00:05:29,99
哭也算时间啊
Tears won't stop it from ticking.

61
00:05:31,00 --> 00:05:33,15
有什么就说什么嘛
You'd better come clean with them.

62
00:05:33,68 --> 00:05:35,43
这位夫人，你是谁？
Who might you be, ma'am?

63
00:05:35,64 --> 00:05:37,07
我就是县长夫人啊
I'm the Governor's wife.

64
00:05:37,24 --> 00:05:38,67
失敬！失敬！
Forgive my impudence.

65
00:05:38,84 --> 00:05:40,67
那你就是县太爷？
So you must be the Governor.

66
00:05:43,04 --> 00:05:46,31
有钱！有钱…！
Yes, of course! There's money!

67
00:05:46,52 --> 00:05:47,66
我跟县长进城上任
We're on our way to inauguration.

68
00:05:47,84 --> 00:05:49,15
县长淹死了，现在没有
He ruined it all by getting drowned!

69
00:05:49,28 --> 00:05:50,99
上任就有！上任就有钱
But we can still hit jackpot

70
00:05:51,16 --> 00:05:52,67
上任就有！
if we take his vacant post.

71
00:05:55,20 --> 00:05:57,79
再给你一圈，顺着买官往下说
I'll give you another chance. Tell me more.

72
00:05:57,96 --> 00:05:58,43
有二十万
$200,000...

73
00:05:58,64 --> 00:05:59,59
钱呢？ 买官了
- Where is it? - Bought the post with it.

74
00:06:20,68 --> 00:06:22,79
他，他县长赚过六百四十万！
That's what the "Governor" made.

75
00:06:22,96 --> 00:06:25,19
我不是师爷么，我就赚个零头！
I only get the small change.

76
00:06:25,36 --> 00:06:26,03
没失过手？
Ever failed?

77
00:06:26,20 --> 00:06:28,19
不动手，拼的是脑子，不流血
We use our brains, not brawn.

78
00:06:28,36 --> 00:06:29,67
你这次去哪儿上任？
Where are you heading to?

79
00:06:29,84 --> 00:06:30,95
鹅城
Goose Town.

80
00:06:31,12 --> 00:06:33,11
火车被劫，你的人淹死了怎么交代？
How do you explain the hold-up and the bodies?

81
00:06:33,28 --> 00:06:35,66
车是我买的，人是我雇的，没人追查
I bought the train and hired the soldiers.

82
00:06:35,84 --> 00:06:37,19
没有人追查
No one will ever find out.

83
00:06:37,52 --> 00:06:39,35
别摘！别摘…！千万别摘！
Don't take it off! Leave your mask on!

84
00:06:39,56 --> 00:06:40,15
规矩我懂
I know the rules.

85
00:06:40,32 --> 00:06:41,38
看见你的脸我就活不成
No one lives after seeing a bandit's face.

86
00:06:41,60 --> 00:06:43,31
你把我放了，我上任鹅城
Just wait here for me.

87
00:06:43,52 --> 00:06:45,35
赚了钱，都给你！都给你！
I'll bring you the money once I have it.

88
00:06:45,56 --> 00:06:46,59
弟兄们劫回道
We came to rob a train,

89
00:06:47,32 --> 00:06:48,75
一分钱都没捞着，不合适吧
we can't go empty-handed.

90
00:06:48,92 --> 00:06:49,51
不合适
No, you can't.

91
00:06:49,68 --> 00:06:51,98
你看了我一眼小命就丢了，也不合适吧
If you die for peeking at me...

92
00:06:52,20 --> 00:06:53,42
更不合适
That's even worse.

93
00:06:53,68 --> 00:06:55,39
你那些淹死的兄弟给我用用？
Can I borrow those bodies?

94
00:06:55,60 --> 00:06:58,19
用！…他们欺男霸女，死有余辜
Yes. These bullies deserve no better.

95
00:06:58,32 --> 00:07:00,11
不是，死了有什么用啊？
But what do you want to do with them?

96
00:07:00,28 --> 00:07:02,51
死人有时候比活人有用
They can be more useful than the living.

97
00:07:03,20 --> 00:07:05,03
师爷，睁开眼看我一眼
Take a look at me.

98
00:07:05,20 --> 00:07:06,63
看一眼
Look at me!

99
00:08:42,68 --> 00:08:43,99
你逃过一次
You've escaped once.

100
00:08:44,16 --> 00:08:45,35
你要是再敢耍我…
Try this one more time...

101
00:08:45,56 --> 00:08:47,94
明白！脑袋搬家
You'll have me beheaded!

102
00:08:56,64 --> 00:08:57,43
进城
Let's go!

103
00:09:32,68 --> 00:09:34,55
城里的女人就是白啊
City girls are so fair and delicate!

104
00:09:36,64 --> 00:09:38,27

"Wanted, Dead or Alive!"

105
00:09:39,68 --> 00:09:41,11
爹，你看
Pop, look!

106
00:09:41,28 --> 00:09:42,67
他们怎么把你画成这样了！
Look what they've made of you!

107
00:09:42,84 --> 00:09:44,51
越不像越安全
The less it resembles me, the safer I am!

108
00:09:57,88 --> 00:10:01,19
恭迎县长大人！
Welcome, your honour!

109
00:10:02,04 --> 00:10:04,55
委任状！
Appointment Warrant!

110
00:10:04,72 --> 00:10:09,39
兹委任马邦德为鹅县县长
Ma Bangde is appointed Goose Town Governor

111
00:10:09,60 --> 00:10:15,59
此状，中华民国萨南康省主席巴青泰
by authority of the Provincial Chairman,

112
00:10:15,76 --> 00:10:20,39
中华民国八年八月二十八日
on this 28th day of February, the 8th year of the Republic...

113
00:10:20,56 --> 00:10:24,23
黄老爷驾到
Master Huang has arrived!

114
00:10:26,52 --> 00:10:30,71
黄老爷吉祥！
Greetings to Master Huang!

115
00:10:28,60 --> 00:10:30,71
Good fortune to Master Huang!


116
00:10:30,88 --> 00:10:33,44
此乃南国一霸黄四郎
Huang Silang is the local godfather.

117
00:10:33,60 --> 00:10:37,43
干的是贩卖人口，倒卖烟土的大生意
Made his fortune from opium and human trafficking.

118
00:10:37,64 --> 00:10:39,55
黄老爷百忙无暇
Master is currently engaged.

119
00:10:39,72 --> 00:10:41,75
特命我黄府大管家胡万！
So he sends his majordomo, Hu Wan!

120
00:10:41,92 --> 00:10:44,79
黄府团练教头武智冲！
And his militia coach, Wu Zhichong!

121
00:10:44,96 --> 00:10:48,43
礼帽，礼貌，欢迎县长！
To welcome you, sir, with his hat!

122
00:10:50,68 --> 00:10:52,75
来者不善啊
Who dares win!

123
00:10:53,56 --> 00:10:55,91
你才是来者
Do you dare?

124
00:11:10,76 --> 00:11:11,67
老爷，来了
He's here, sir.

125
00:11:11,84 --> 00:11:12,67
谁呀？
Who's here?

126
00:11:13,76 --> 00:11:14,55
你自己
Yourself!

127
00:11:14,72 --> 00:11:15,91
黄大爷万寿！
Long live Master Huang!

128
00:11:16,08 --> 00:11:18,54
小的杨万楼，这厢有礼
Greetings from Yang Wanlou!

129
00:11:18,72 --> 00:11:20,71
膺品是个好东西！
A remarkable fake!

130
00:11:21,12 --> 00:11:23,23
膺品是个好东西！
A remarkable fake!

131
00:11:23,40 --> 00:11:25,39
走几步
Take a few steps.

132
00:11:26,80 --> 00:11:28,59
走出个虎虎生风
Walk purposefully.

133
00:11:28,76 --> 00:11:31,27
走个虎虎生风
Purposefully...

134
00:11:31,96 --> 00:11:33,51
走出一个一日千里
Walk with spirit.

135
00:11:33,64 --> 00:11:35,39
走个一日千里
Spiritedly...

136
00:11:35,60 --> 00:11:37,59
走出一个恍如隔世
Walk pensively.

137
00:11:37,76 --> 00:11:39,99
走个恍如隔世
Pensively...

138
00:05:59,76 --> 00:06:00,79
买官干什么？ 赚钱
- What for? - To make more money.

139
00:06:00,96 --> 00:06:02,02
能赚多少？ 一倍
- How much? - Twice as much.

140
00:06:02,20 --> 00:06:03,26
多长时间？ 一年
- How long will it take? - A year.

141
00:06:03,44 --> 00:06:04,66
我要等你一年？
I've to wait one year?

142
00:06:04,84 --> 00:06:07,11
半年半年！手气好，一个月也行！
A month, if you're in luck.

143
00:06:07,28 --> 00:06:08,99
县长淹死了，谁去上任？ 我
- Who will be the governor? - Me.

144
00:06:09,16 --> 00:06:10,07
你是谁？ 师爷
- And who might you be? - I'm a counselor.

145
00:19:57,96 --> 00:19:59,07
磕不磕？
Do it!

146
00:19:59,28 --> 00:20:00,31
打！
Flog him!

147
00:20:04,68 --> 00:20:05,95
这个不好使
That's no good.

148
00:20:06,72 --> 00:20:07,78
得使这个！
This is more effective.

149
00:20:07,96 --> 00:20:10,31
哎！别打！我磕！
Stop! I'll do it.

150
00:20:11,04 --> 00:20:12,35
行了
Splendid!

151
00:22:19,84 --> 00:22:21,75
那上面印着他名字的时候
If his name was printed there.

152
00:22:25,80 --> 00:22:28,23
爹，这叫穆扎这人
Pop, this Mozart...

153
00:22:28,40 --> 00:22:31,19
他是怎么把这东西吹到这里边的？
How did he get the sound in there?

154
00:22:31,88 --> 00:22:35,42
你去留完洋，你就什么都知道了
You'll learn by studying abroad.

155
00:13:48,20 --> 00:13:50,23
若是夫人有任何要求
But if you have that urge,

156
00:13:50,40 --> 00:13:51,67
兄弟我…
then yours truly,

157
00:13:51,84 --> 00:13:53,71
也决不推辞
would be happy to oblige.

158
00:13:59,16 --> 00:14:00,59
睡觉
Let's sleep!

159
00:14:14,44 --> 00:14:19,03
一日夫妻百日恩呐
Husband and wife - even for a day...

160
00:14:30,44 --> 00:14:33,27
反正呢，我就想当县长夫人
I've always wanted to be a governor's wife,

161
00:14:33,84 --> 00:14:36,99
谁是县长，我无所谓！
and I don't care who the governor is.

162
00:14:37,96 --> 00:14:39,95
兄弟，别客气嘛
So, brother, be my guest!

163
00:14:40,12 --> 00:14:40,91
我客气吗？
Your guest?

164
00:14:41,08 --> 00:14:41,87
客气呀
Go ahead!

165
00:14:42,04 --> 00:14:43,51
这还算客气？
You make me blush!

166
00:14:44,28 --> 00:14:45,99
你太客气啦
Well, do I?

167
00:14:46,16 --> 00:14:47,99
怎么才能不客气啊？
Then I must oblige.

168
00:14:48,80 --> 00:14:49,67
晚了！
We're late!

169
00:14:49,84 --> 00:14:50,59
前几任县长
Previous governors

170
00:14:50,76 --> 00:14:52,99
把鹅城的税，收到九十年以后了
have levied tax for the next 90 years!

171
00:14:53,16 --> 00:14:56,43
也就是西历二零一零年！
So everyone has paid up to 2010!

172
00:14:56,64 --> 00:14:57,99
咱们来错地方了
We've come to the wrong place!

173
00:14:58,32 --> 00:15:00,03
我倒是觉得这个地方不错
I like this town, though.

174
00:15:00,20 --> 00:15:03,03
百姓成穷鬼了，没油水可榨了
But people here have nothing left.

175
00:15:03,20 --> 00:15:05,66
老子从来就没想刮穷鬼的钱
I never take from the poor.

176
00:15:53,76 --> 00:15:55,03
那你要这么说
If you want to put it that way...

177
00:15:55,20 --> 00:15:57,43
买官当县长还真就是跪着要饭的
Many would love to be in your position,

178
00:15:57,64 --> 00:16:00,31
就这，多少人想跪还没这门路呢！
but few could afford to buy a post.

179
00:16:06,60 --> 00:16:12,31
我问问你，我为什么要上山当土匪？
Do you know why I became an outlaw?

180
00:16:14,56 --> 00:16:17,23
我就是腿脚不方便，跪不下去！
It's because my legs are not built for kneeling!

181
00:16:18,12 --> 00:16:19,71
原来你是想站着赚钱啊！
If you want to make money standing tall,

182
00:16:19,88 --> 00:16:21,23
那还是回山里吧
ride back to the mountains.

183
00:16:22,12 --> 00:16:23,75
这我就不明白了
I don't get this.

184
00:16:24,04 --> 00:16:25,59
我已经当了县长了
I am now governor,

185
00:16:25,76 --> 00:16:27,39
怎么还不如个土匪呀？
how can I be worse off than a bandit?

186
00:16:27,60 --> 00:16:29,27
百姓眼里，你是县长
You may be a governor to the townsfolk.

187
00:16:30,16 --> 00:16:31,91
可是黄四郎眼里
But in the eyes of Huang,

188
00:16:32,16 --> 00:16:33,79
你就是跪着要饭的
you're a mere beggar!

189
00:16:34,64 --> 00:16:37,91
赚钱嘛，生意，不寒酸！
This is only business. There is no shame.

190
00:16:38,08 --> 00:16:39,30
寒酸！
The hell there isn't!

191
00:16:39,72 --> 00:16:40,78
很寒酸
It's shameful!

192
00:16:40,92 --> 00:16:41,95
那你是想站着？
Do you prefer to stand tall,

193
00:16:42,12 --> 00:16:43,15
还是想赚钱呢？
or do you want to make money?

194
