00:13:39,92 --> 00:13:41,39
若是兄弟我…
Just in case,

394
00:13:41,88 --> 00:13:43,71
有冒犯夫人的举动
I overstep my mark,

395
00:13:44,52 --> 00:13:46,75
你可以随时干掉我
shoot me between the eyes.

396
00:20:24,16 --> 00:20:25,30
起来！不准跪！
Stand up everyone!

397
00:20:25,52 --> 00:20:28,67
皇上都没了，没人值得你们跪！
No one is worth kneeling to.

398
00:20:30,16 --> 00:20:31,83
我也不值你们跪！
Least of all to me!

399
00:20:32,08 --> 00:20:34,19
我来鹅城只办三件事
I've brought three things to Goose Town.

400
00:20:34,44 --> 00:20:36,90
公平！
Justice,

401
00:20:35,44 --> 00:20:36,91
justice,


402
00:20:37,08 --> 00:20:39,15
还是公平！
and goddamned justice.

403
00:20:39,32 --> 00:20:41,39
青天大老爷！
Hail, Governor!

404
00:20:41,60 --> 00:20:43,83
站起来！不准跪！
Stand up! No kneeling!

405
00:20:44,44 --> 00:20:46,79
这就对了
That's better.

406
00:20:48,28 --> 00:20:49,42
不准跪？
No kneeling?

407
00:20:49,64 --> 00:20:51,23
这哪是打我的屁股
He was not only flogging me,

408
00:20:51,40 --> 00:20:53,55
这明明是打您的脸
he was slapping you in the face!

409
00:20:56,92 --> 00:20:59,51
老爷，等我把屁股养好了
When my butts stop hurting,

410
00:20:59,68 --> 00:21:01,71
我亲手给你报仇！
I will personally avenge you.

411
00:21:01,88 --> 00:21:03,91
那就把卖凉粉的叫来
Summon the noodle vendor.

412
00:21:04,88 --> 00:21:06,75
县长喜欢判案
If our governor loves to try,

413
00:21:06,92 --> 00:21:10,35
就安排一点案子给他判叹
we'll give him a case to try.

414
00:45:41,32 --> 00:45:43,31
唉！我带夫人来的
I've brought my wife with me.

415
00:45:43,52 --> 00:45:44,99
再收姑娘不方便
So I can't take her home.

416
00:45:45,16 --> 00:45:46,51
那钻石送夫人
Then take the diamonds for your wife.

417
00:45:46,68 --> 00:45:48,35
好！我先替她收着
I accept them on her behalf.

418
00:45:49,64 --> 00:45:50,67
起来吧
Get up.

419
00:45:51,92 --> 00:45:54,87
不是黛玉和晴雯吗？
I thought you'd summoned two girls.

420
00:45:55,04 --> 00:45:57,07
怎么就来了一名女子？
How come there's only her?

421
00:45:57,24 --> 00:45:59,87
莫非她就叫黛玉晴雯？
You mean she is Marie-Claire?

422
00:46:00,04 --> 00:46:01,35
说你不会装糊涂吧
You are really naive!

423
00:46:01,56 --> 00:46:03,19
起了个东洋名字
She's adopted a fashionable name.

424
00:46:03,36 --> 00:46:06,43
黛玉晴雯子！
It's Marie-Claire!

425
00:46:08,32 --> 00:46:10,15
全死了！
There goes the last of them!

426
00:52:35,60 --> 00:52:37,03
为什么朝我床上开枪？
Why did you target my bed?

427
00:52:37,20 --> 00:52:39,76
黄老爷说你霸气外露
Master said you're arrogant,

428
00:52:39,96 --> 00:52:40,94
危险！
a threat!

429
00:52:41,64 --> 00:52:43,55
回去给他带个话，告诉他
Take him a message:

430
00:52:43,72 --> 00:52:45,75
他喜欢让人假死这一套
While he likes people to fake death,

431
00:52:45,92 --> 00:52:49,35
正好，我也喜欢让人多死几回这一套
I'm fond of killing people more than once!

432
00:48:42,84 --> 00:48:45,91
贱货，骚货，妹子，贱货！
Whore! Bitch! Vixen! Tramp!

433
00:48:46,88 --> 00:48:47,63
就是时间不够
If I'd more time,

434
00:48:47,80 --> 00:48:50,43
要不然我活活把你给搞死了！
I'll put you in your place!

435
00:48:50,64 --> 00:48:51,78
好啊，来呀
Come on!

436
00:48:52,16 --> 00:48:53,43
看你怎么办
I dare you!

437
00:48:56,04 --> 00:48:57,75
你就只剩下一张嘴！
You're all talk!

438
00:48:58,12 --> 00:49:00,15
写几个烂戏本的老色鬼！
A perverted, dirty old man.

439
00:49:00,32 --> 00:49:01,38
不是我出钱
Could you have bought the post

440
00:49:01,60 --> 00:49:03,03
谁给你买官当县长啊？
without my money?

441
00:49:03,20 --> 00:49:04,79
你别逼急我了
Don't piss me off!

442
00:49:05,04 --> 00:49:07,03
我还真觉得那个土匪挺有本事的
I think the bandit is more able!

443
00:49:07,72 --> 00:49:08,75
他算什么本事啊？
What do you mean?

444
00:49:08,92 --> 00:49:09,87
比你有本事
He's got more balls than you!

445
00:49:10,04 --> 00:49:11,87
早烂醉如泥了
He's good at getting drunk!

446
00:49:17,00 --> 00:49:20,03
这才是真本事
These will make your day!

447
00:50:54,68 --> 00:50:56,75
杀了你，我还怎么睡啊
I don't sleep with dead bodies!

448
00:51:02,76 --> 00:51:07,15
我不能酒后欺负一个寡妇
I won't take drunken advantage of a widow,

449
00:51:08,12 --> 00:51:09,87
是跟你睡
so I'll just sleep next to you,

450
00:51:10,88 --> 00:51:12,83
不是睡你
not with you!

451
00:52:00,36 --> 00:52:02,03
我居然上了你们的当！
Holy smoke! I was fooled!

452
00:52:02,20 --> 00:52:04,07
你和武举人都是假死是吧？
You and Wu both faked death!

453
00:52:04,24 --> 00:52:04,99
不错
That's right.

454
00:52:05,16 --> 00:52:05,95
为什么冒充麻匪？
Why dressed up as a bandit?

455
00:52:06,12 --> 00:52:08,42
老子就是麻匪，张麻子是我大哥
I'm a bandit. "Pocky" Zhang's my boss!

456
00:52:08,64 --> 00:52:10,19
那你是老几呀？
What's your rank, then?

457
00:52:10,36 --> 00:52:11,03
老三
I am Three!

458
00:52:11,20 --> 00:52:12,75
老三，你出名了
Three, you've hit big time!

459
00:52:12,92 --> 00:52:13,71
有人冒充你了！
You've got yourself a fake!

460
00:52:13,88 --> 00:52:15,67
别听他废话了，大哥
Chief, don't listen to his bullshit!

461
00:52:15,84 --> 00:52:17,03
六子就死在他手上
He plotted Six's death.

462
00:52:17,20 --> 00:52:18,11
你让我一枪崩了他
Let me shoot him now!

463
00:52:18,28 --> 00:52:18,91
大哥？
Chief?

464
00:52:19,08 --> 00:52:20,71
是你大哥张麻子派你来的
Were you sent by "Pocky" Zhang?

465
00:52:20,88 --> 00:52:22,39
还是你老爷黄四郎派你来的？
Or by Master Huang?

466
00:52:22,60 --> 00:52:23,74
不能说错啊！
I want the right answer!

467
00:52:25,20 --> 00:52:26,67
黄老爷 为什么？
- Master Huang. - Why?

468
00:52:26,84 --> 00:52:28,95
他让我们假扮麻匪在城里抢劫
We commit crimes posing as bandits,

469
00:52:29,40 --> 00:52:30,91
他逼县长下令剿匪
forcing governors to launch expeditions.

470
00:46:10,32 --> 00:46:11,87
师爷，高！
A wise counselor!

471
00:46:12,64 --> 00:46:14,23
县长，硬！
A tough governor!

472
00:46:14,52 --> 00:46:17,08
黄老爷又高又硬！
Master, you're both wise and tough.

473
00:46:17,84 --> 00:46:19,99
你到底是不是张麻子？
Are you really "Pocky" Zhang?

474
00:46:21,24 --> 00:46:22,79
要说你是吧
Supposing that you are.

475
00:46:23,80 --> 00:46:25,39
扭断刘都统大腿
You've already made a fortune

476
00:46:25,60 --> 00:46:26,82
赚那么多钱
from "crippling" Liu's runners.

477
00:46:27,16 --> 00:46:30,31
何苦进城当县长呢？
Why bother with Goose Town?

478
00:46:32,32 --> 00:46:34,70
要说你不是吧…
But if you are someone else...

479
00:46:36,24 --> 00:46:37,55
恩人？
Saviour?

480
00:46:55,64 --> 00:46:57,91
今晚，杀鸡取卵！
Kill the chicken and take the eggs.

481
00:46:58,08 --> 00:47:00,35
一定要在县长的床上
Let him die in his own bed.

482
00:47:01,20 --> 00:47:03,95
不要让人以为吃了我的饭
Don't kill him on his way home

483
00:47:04,12 --> 00:47:07,03
死在我家里，死在半路上
after dining as my guest.

484
00:47:07,20 --> 00:47:08,11
明白！
Understood!

485
00:47:08,28 --> 00:47:09,07
哪个是鸡？
Who is the "chicken"?

486
00:47:09,24 --> 00:47:09,87
县长！
The Governor.

487
00:47:10,04 --> 00:47:10,79
那么卵呢？
And the "eggs"?

488
00:49:32,12 --> 00:49:33,23
给你报仇
and avenge your death.

489
00:49:34,88 --> 00:49:36,79
可是中途我改了主意
But I've changed my mind.

490
00:49:38,32 --> 00:49:40,95
鱼死网破报不了仇
I can't take revenge this way.

491
00:49:42,16 --> 00:49:44,39
弟兄们不能再死人了
I can't risk more lives.

492
00:49:44,60 --> 00:49:46,31
大哥，你怎么在这儿啊？
Chief, we're looking for you.

493
00:49:46,52 --> 00:49:47,79
你怎么让我们撤了呀？
Why did you signal retreat?

494
00:49:47,96 --> 00:49:49,79
黄四郎听见你们吹的哨声
Huang heard your whistling.

495
00:49:49,92 --> 00:49:51,75
我就绝对安全了
I knew that I was safe.

496
00:49:52,20 --> 00:49:55,11
去吧，我跟六子单独待会儿
Leave, I want to spend time alone with Six.

497
00:49:57,40 --> 00:49:58,71
今天我算明白了
It has finally dawned on me,

498
00:49:59,88 --> 00:50:03,03
为什么当初我会上山当麻匪
why I became a bandit in the first place.

499
00:50:03,60 --> 00:50:06,06
就是因为跟这帮东西玩不起
I was no match for these people.

500
00:50:06,40 --> 00:50:09,51
现在为了你，我必须玩得起
But I must take them on at their own game now,

501
00:50:10,64 --> 00:50:11,83
还得玩得赢
and to win for you.

502
00:50:19,68 --> 00:50:20,51
谁？
What the heck?

503
00:50:23,64 --> 00:50:26,39
偷我的钻石！
You stole my diamonds.

504
00:50:27,28 --> 00:50:28,71
这石头是给你的吗？
They're not meant for you.

505
00:50:28,88 --> 00:50:30,95
是给县长夫人的
They're a gift for Mrs. Governor!

506
00:50:31,12 --> 00:50:33,63
咱们俩谁是县长？
Which of us is the Governor?

507
00:50:36,72 --> 00:50:37,94
谁是县长？
Who's the Governor?

508
00:50:39,16 --> 00:50:42,43
我问你呢，谁是县长？
Tell me who's the Governor!

509
00:50:42,64 --> 00:50:44,31
你是要杀我？
You want to kill me?

510
00:50:44,64 --> 00:50:45,95
还是要睡我？
Or to sleep with me?

511
00:50:47,60 --> 00:50:48,71
有什么不一样吗？
Is there a difference?

512
00:50:48,88 --> 00:50:49,99
不一样啊！
It's different!

513
00:50:50,16 --> 00:50:52,31
那就先睡，再杀
I can bed you first, and kill you later.

514
00:50:53,08 --> 00:50:54,43
那还是杀了我吧
Then you'd better kill me now.

515
00:52:49,56 --> 00:52:50,75
您要放我回去？
Letting me off again?

516
00:52:50,96 --> 00:52:52,39
只有你的话他听得懂
He can only understand words you say.

517
00:52:52,60 --> 00:52:53,87
大哥，可您到底是？
Chief, you're...

518
00:52:54,04 --> 00:52:55,67
不错，张麻子！
Yes, "Pocky" Zhang.

519
00:44:43,72 --> 00:44:47,67
江湖豪情，侠胆柔肠之大腿
Master Huang's a runner of exceptional courage!

520
00:44:48,08 --> 00:44:48,95
哥！ 弟！
- Brother! - Brother!

521
00:44:49,12 --> 00:44:50,75
你的腿，就是我的腿
We can run side by side!

522
00:44:50,92 --> 00:44:52,63
你的腿，就是我的命
We'll run for our lives!

523
00:44:52,80 --> 00:44:55,63
有道是，江湖本无路
Roads won't exist in this world of chaos,

524
00:44:55,80 --> 00:44:58,63
有了腿，便有了路！
unless people like us run on them!

525
00:47:41,00 --> 00:47:42,59
你永远都活着
you may live on forever!

526
00:47:42,76 --> 00:47:43,71
明白
Understood.

527
00:47:43,96 --> 00:47:46,11
杀鸡取卵！
Kill the chicken, take the eggs!

528
00:47:46,80 --> 00:47:47,94
师爷，大哥呢？
Where's Chief?

529
00:47:48,12 --> 00:47:49,18
马上，喝醉了
Punch drunk!

530
00:47:49,36 --> 00:47:50,67
人呢？哪儿呢？
Where is he?

531
00:47:50,80 --> 00:47:52,79
刚才还说话呢！
We're still chatting just now!

532
00:47:53,16 --> 00:47:54,22
我也喝醉了
I must be drunk, too!

533
00:47:54,40 --> 00:47:54,95
回来跟你算帐
I'll sort you out later.

534
00:47:55,12 --> 00:47:58,66
没在马上么？是不是掉路上了？
He must've fallen off the horse.

535
00:48:05,00 --> 00:48:07,23
听说你睡觉了
I heard that you slept.

536
00:48:09,00 --> 00:48:10,87
你抬起头来跟我说话
Look up when you speak.

537
00:48:11,36 --> 00:48:13,51
听说你昨天睡觉了
I heard that you slept last night.

538
00:48:13,72 --> 00:48:16,15
我哪天不睡觉啊！
I sleep every goddamned night!

539
00:48:16,52 --> 00:48:17,66
你看着我说话
Look at me when you speak.

540
00:48:17,84 --> 00:48:20,43
听说你跟土匪睡觉了
You slept with the bandit?

541
00:48:20,64 --> 00:48:23,71
睡了！你不想知道我们怎么睡的吗？
Do you want a blow-by-blow account?

542
00:48:23,84 --> 00:48:25,23
对，怎么睡的？
Tell me more.

543
00:48:25,40 --> 00:48:28,27
一个青楼女子，跟一个土匪头子
When a seasoned pro meets a bandit chief,

544
00:48:28,44 --> 00:48:31,23
什么睡法都能有
anything could happen!

545
00:48:34,68 --> 00:48:36,03
嘘什么嘘？
What now?

546
00:48:38,64 --> 00:48:41,59
你这个不要脸的骚窑姐，妹子，贱货
Whore! Bitch! Vixen! Tramp!

547
00:48:41,84 --> 00:48:42,71
你说什么！
What did you call me?

548
00:57:30,12 --> 00:57:32,35
千爷，别打了
Butler, hold your fire!

549
00:57:32,56 --> 00:57:34,35
赶紧回去备银子吧！
We need time to prepare the ransom.

550
00:53:29,76 --> 00:53:31,11
她是我老婆！
She was my wife.

551
00:53:31,28 --> 00:53:33,15
我是县长！ 让他进来
- I am the governor! - Let him in.

552
00:53:33,32 --> 00:53:35,88
我就是马邦德！
I am Ma Bangde!

553
00:53:38,92 --> 00:53:41,38
县长如何了？县长如何了？
Is the Governor okay?

554
00:53:41,60 --> 00:53:43,83
你们追！一个麻匪也不能跑！
Give chase! Don't let anyone get away.

555
00:53:48,72 --> 00:53:50,67
天杀的麻匪
Those goddamned bandits!

556
00:53:50,84 --> 00:53:52,71
伤天害理
Scum of the earth!

557
00:53:53,04 --> 00:53:57,03
县长刚刚上任，竟和他的夫人双双…
The Governor has only just arrived...

558
00:54:02,04 --> 00:54:04,71
我说我当不了这个县长！
Said I didn't want to be a governor,

559
00:54:04,88 --> 00:54:08,99
你非得给我花钱买这个官！
but you still bought me this post!

560
00:54:10,16 --> 00:54:13,43
现在官倒是到手了
The governership is now mine,

561
00:54:14,60 --> 00:54:17,67
你倒这么走了！
but you've left me on my own.

562
00:54:20,44 --> 00:54:21,99
她是我老婆！
She was my wife.

563
00:54:22,80 --> 00:54:24,07
我就是县长
I am the governor!

564
00:54:24,24 --> 00:54:26,43
我就是马邦德！
I am Ma Bangde!

565
00:54:27,00 --> 00:54:30,19
你呀，太年轻了
You're too hot-headed.

566
00:21:10,72 --> 00:21:14,03
爹，今天你这县长干得真漂亮
Pop, you were brilliant today.

567
00:21:14,20 --> 00:21:15,87
打武举人打得真过瘾
Flogging that martial scholar was a hoot!

568
00:21:16,28 --> 00:21:17,59
将来我也想当县长
I'd love to be a governor one day.

569
00:21:17,76 --> 00:21:21,07
你不能当县长，也不许当土匪
I don't want you to be a bandit or politician.

570
00:21:22,88 --> 00:21:25,87
你爹死的时候把你交给我
When your father entrusted you to me,

571
00:21:26,56 --> 00:21:29,02
我答应过他，要让你有出息
I promised I'd raise you properly.

572
00:21:29,20 --> 00:21:31,95
那我当什么才有出息？
Then what should I do?

573
00:21:34,04 --> 00:21:37,35
当学生！读书，多听这个
Study and learn to enjoy this.

574
00:21:37,76 --> 00:21:38,90
没声啊！
There is no sound!

575
00:24:10,36 --> 00:24:12,03
我不能…
Then I must not...

576
00:24:12,20 --> 00:24:14,63
让她再守活寡
Ieave her alone uncomforted.

577
00:24:21,84 --> 00:24:23,43
这是第一步
That's my first move.

578
00:24:23,88 --> 00:24:24,71
三步之内…
Within three...

579
00:24:24,88 --> 00:24:27,44
要不让他们滚蛋走人
they'll either leave with tails between their legs,

580
00:24:27,68 --> 00:24:29,11
要不让他们跪下当狗！
or stay and become our poodles!

581
00:24:29,28 --> 00:24:32,23
对，非常对
Right, absolutely right.

582
00:24:33,76 --> 00:24:35,11
老爷，您找我？
You're looking for me, sir?

583
00:24:35,28 --> 00:24:36,79
官府的人还没来？
Have you entertained our new officials yet?

584
00:24:36,96 --> 00:24:37,75
没有
Not yet.

585
00:24:37,92 --> 00:24:39,06
县长不缥妓？
The Governor doesn't frequent brothels?

586
00:24:39,28 --> 00:24:42,39
不好色的县长，不一定是好县长
He'll never make a good governor.

587
00:24:42,60 --> 00:24:43,91
我就是不好色！
I don't indulge much in sex.

588
00:24:44,08 --> 00:24:45,79
所以您当不了县长
So you won't make a good governor either.

589
00:24:49,20 --> 00:24:50,67
我当不了县长？
Why is that so?

590
00:24:50,84 --> 00:24:52,67
县长哪能跟您比呀
The two bear no comparison!

591
00:24:52,84 --> 00:24:54,39
他只是流水的县长
Governors come and go.

592
00:24:54,60 --> 00:24:56,59
您才是铁打的老爷
But you, sir, will always be our godfather!

593
00:24:59,76 --> 00:25:01,91
你真会讲话
You speak well!

594
00:25:02,16 --> 00:25:04,75
他们一定会来，你要好好记住
I'm sure they will come.

595
00:25:04,92 --> 00:25:07,63
他们讲的每一句有用的话
Eavesdrop their every conversation,

596
00:25:07,80 --> 00:25:10,75
都要回来跟我汇报
report their every move.

597
00:25:10,96 --> 00:25:11,63
是
Yes.

598
00:25:11,80 --> 00:25:15,11
走吧，你不要变成小凤仙哦
Go now. Just don't become a Mata Hari!

599
00:25:16,08 --> 00:25:18,75
老爷，谁是小凤仙？
Who's Mata Hari, Master?

600
00:25:19,08 --> 00:25:21,95
小凤仙都不知道还当妓女
What kind of whore are you?

601
00:25:22,12 --> 00:25:26,35
那可是名震京城，誉满全国的妓女
She's the world's most infamous double agent!

602
00:25:32,24 --> 00:25:33,30
你们出去吧
You two can leave.

603
00:25:36,92 --> 00:25:41,31
县长此刻正怀抱夫人，共枕同眠
Now the Governor is in bed with his wife.

604
00:25:42,72 --> 00:25:44,79
让他睡最后一个安稳觉
Let him enjoy one more night in peace!

605
00:25:45,12 --> 00:25:48,03
县长公子，以身试法
The Governor's boy is in trouble,

606
00:25:48,20 --> 00:25:50,66
讲茶大堂，恭迎大驾！
your presence is requested at the teahouse.

607
00:25:50,84 --> 00:25:53,14
讲茶大堂？县衙不是判案的地方吗？
Why don't they convene at the magistracy?

608
00:25:53,32 --> 00:25:54,67
你这个县衙是摆设
The magistracy is just for show.

609
00:25:54,84 --> 00:25:57,95
判案只有去讲茶大堂！那才是真县衙！
All cases are tried at the teahouse.

610
00:25:59,20 --> 00:26:00,39
六爷
Master Six,

611
00:26:01,16 --> 00:26:02,43
你吃了两碗的粉
you've eaten two bowls of jelly,

612
00:15:05,84 --> 00:15:07,79
不刮穷鬼的钱你收谁的呀？
Who are your victims, then?

613
00:15:07,96 --> 00:15:09,51
谁有钱赚谁的
The rich, of course.

614
00:15:09,72 --> 00:15:10,55
当过县长吗？
Ever been a Governor?

615
00:15:10,72 --> 00:15:11,59
没有
No.

616
00:15:11,76 --> 00:15:12,98
我告诉你！
Listen carefully!

617
00:15:13,16 --> 00:15:15,39
县长上任，得巧立名目
You have to devise ways to raise money,

618
00:15:15,60 --> 00:15:17,63
拉拢豪绅，缴税捐款
Make the rich pay first,

619
00:15:17,80 --> 00:15:20,59
他们交了，才能让百姓跟着交钱
townsfolk will follow suit.

620
00:15:20,76 --> 00:15:23,87
得钱之后，豪绅的钱如数奉还
Then reimburse the rich with what they paid,

621
00:15:24,04 --> 00:15:26,42
百姓的钱，三七分成！
and split the rest 30-70!

622
00:15:26,64 --> 00:15:27,75
怎么才七成啊？
We only get 70?

623
00:15:27,88 --> 00:15:29,59
七成是人家的！
No, the rich get 70.

624
00:15:29,76 --> 00:15:32,39
能得三成还得看黄四郎的脸色
We get 30 at Huang's discretion.

625
00:15:32,60 --> 00:15:33,31
谁的脸色？
At whose discretion?

626
00:15:33,52 --> 00:15:34,58
他！
Him.

627
00:15:34,76 --> 00:15:35,39
他？!
Him?

628
00:15:35,60 --> 00:15:37,19
我大老远的来一趟
I come all this way,

629
00:15:37,36 --> 00:15:40,15
就是为了看他的脸色？
only to become his running dog?

630
00:15:40,36 --> 00:15:41,42
对！
Correct.

631
00:15:42,96 --> 00:15:45,15
我好不容易劫了趟火车
It's hard enough robbing your train,

632
00:19:26,40 --> 00:19:27,99
老子是光绪三十一年
During the reign of the last Emperor,

633
00:19:28,16 --> 00:19:29,63
皇上钦点的武举人
I was bestowed a Martial Scholar.

634
00:19:29,80 --> 00:19:31,59
论官职，比你官大
My rank was higher than yours.

635
00:19:31,76 --> 00:19:33,79
你应该给老子跪下
You should kneel in front of me!

636
00:19:33,96 --> 00:19:35,15
跪下！
Kneel!

637
00:19:36,28 --> 00:19:37,59
跪不跪？
Kneel!

638
00:19:37,84 --> 00:19:39,95
还皇上！
This is bullshit!

639
00:19:40,40 --> 00:19:42,63
哪个皇上？我见过吗？
The last Emperor? Have I ever met him?

640
00:19:42,80 --> 00:19:43,99
你要是个文举人
If you'd been a Literary Scholar,

641
00:19:44,16 --> 00:19:45,63
他应该给你磕两百个头
he'd have to kowtow 200 times.

642
00:19:45,80 --> 00:19:48,43
可惜你只是个武举人
But as a Martial Scholar,

643
00:19:48,64 --> 00:19:50,67
他只能给你磕一百个头
you'll get only 100 kowtows.

644
00:19:50,96 --> 00:19:53,11
现在他两百个头磕完了
Since he has already done 200,

645
00:19:53,28 --> 00:19:54,07
你还他一百个
you've to return 100 kowtows.

646
00:19:54,24 --> 00:19:55,03
可我只磕了两个
But I've only kowtowed twice!

647
00:19:55,20 --> 00:19:57,43
两个也得还你一百个
Does it really matter?

648
00:29:14,32 --> 00:29:15,30
才能让我看得见
so that we can all see.

649
00:29:15,52 --> 00:29:18,19
六爷，让大家看看是一碗还是两碗
Show us if there is one or two bowls.

650
00:29:18,36 --> 00:29:19,75
拉！
Out with it!

651
00:29:23,72 --> 00:29:25,71
六爷，碗！
Here's a bowl, sir.

652
00:29:36,92 --> 00:29:39,59
看见了吧！看见了吧！
See! Can you see?

653
00:29:39,88 --> 00:29:42,87
是不是只有一碗！
One bowl!

654
00:29:41,32 --> 00:29:42,87
There's only one bowl, right?


655
00:27:29,12 --> 00:27:30,75
你早说不就得了吗
Let's be frank.

656
00:27:30,92 --> 00:27:31,90
他要个公平
He wants to be treated fairly.

657
00:27:32,08 --> 00:27:34,35
你不是欺负老实人吗？
It's wrong to bully a commoner.

658
00:27:43,72 --> 00:27:46,18
告诉我，你是老实人吗？
Are you an honest person?

659
00:27:46,44 --> 00:27:46,95
我是
Yes, I am...

660
00:27:47,12 --> 00:27:49,27
那你就说实话，我到底吃了几碗粉？
How many bowls did I eat?

661
00:27:49,44 --> 00:27:50,91
你告诉他！
Tell him!

662
00:27:51,28 --> 00:27:52,55
你说不说？
Speak up!

663
00:27:53,08 --> 00:27:56,95
拿枪吓唬一可怜的，卖凉粉的
Stop threatening this poor man with a gun!

664
00:27:57,12 --> 00:28:00,15
有枪是吧？谁没有枪啊！
Who doesn't carry a gun around here?

665
00:28:01,28 --> 00:28:02,55
孙守义
Noodle vendor!

666
00:28:03,00 --> 00:28:05,63
大声说，他吃了几碗
How many bowls did he eat?

667
00:28:09,04 --> 00:28:11,75
守义，在座所有的乡亲
Everyone in this teahouse,

668
00:28:11,92 --> 00:28:15,27
都会为你和你的家人作主的
will bear witness on your behalf.

669
00:28:15,60 --> 00:28:18,23
大声说，几碗
Speak up! How many?

670
00:28:25,12 --> 00:28:26,26
两碗
Two bowls.

671
00:28:34,56 --> 00:28:35,87
你是一个恶人！
You're nasty!

672
00:28:36,96 --> 00:28:39,95
比恶是吧，我比你还恶
But I dare you to match me!

673
00:28:43,88 --> 00:28:45,51
都看好了啊
Take a good look!

674
00:28:45,68 --> 00:28:47,91
今我肚子里要有两碗粉
If there are two bowls of jelly in me,

675
00:28:48,08 --> 00:28:49,03
我白死
I'll die!

676
00:30:14,92 --> 00:30:16,83
杀了他，六子白死
Don't let Six die in vain!

677
00:30:17,00 --> 00:30:19,63
我没有杀他，他自己捅自己的！
I didn't do it. He stabbed himself.

678
00:30:19,80 --> 00:30:20,75
我们在打赌
We'd a wager.

679
00:30:20,92 --> 00:30:21,90
他输了
He lost.

680
00:30:22,16 --> 00:30:23,63
大哥，你让我一枪崩了他！
Let me blast his head off!

681
00:30:23,80 --> 00:30:25,75
你不敢杀我！你不能杀我！
You wouldn't dare! You can't do it.

682
00:30:25,92 --> 00:30:27,87
黄四郎就想看你这样！
Huang is provoking you.

683
00:30:28,04 --> 00:30:29,23
一脸的败相！
He wants you to lose your head.

684
00:30:29,40 --> 00:30:31,19
杀了他就是输，不杀还能赢
We'll lose if we kill him now.

685
00:30:31,36 --> 00:30:32,07
放人
Let him go.

686
00:30:32,24 --> 00:30:34,75
杀人诛心，杀人诛心！
You must destroy Huang's soul!

687
00:30:34,92 --> 00:30:36,55
师爷说得对 放人
- Pop, he's right. - Let him go!

688
00:30:43,52 --> 00:30:48,11
刀进了肚子，那凉粉还是凉粉？
He stabbed himself? What about the jelly?

689
00:30:48,28 --> 00:30:49,31
是
Yes

690
00:30:50,12 --> 00:30:50,51
不是
and no...

691
00:30:50,68 --> 00:30:53,71
我就想知道，凉粉到底还是不是凉粉
Tell me if it was still jelly.

692
00:30:53,88 --> 00:30:54,55
是凉粉！
Yes, it was.

693
00:30:54,72 --> 00:30:56,07
过来过来
Come over here.

694
00:30:57,52 --> 00:30:58,66
那么…
And...

695
00:30:58,96 --> 00:30:59,94
人死了？
is he dead?

696
00:31:00,20 --> 00:31:01,51
死了
Yes.

697
00:31:03,52 --> 00:31:05,82
所以…你就把我供出来了？
Did you implicate me?

698
00:31:06,00 --> 00:31:07,79
我是用老爷的名字吓唬他们
I did invoke your name.

699
00:31:07,96 --> 00:31:09,18
他们被吓着了么？
Were they scared?

700
00:31:09,36 --> 00:31:11,79
他们说杀人诛心！
They said to kill, a person's soul must first be destroyed.

701
00:31:11,96 --> 00:31:15,27
杀人还要诛心？
Murder? Soul destruction?

702
00:31:15,72 --> 00:31:18,15
好可怕啊！
How awful.

703
00:31:22,28 --> 00:31:24,79
六弟，四哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I vow to avenge you!

704
00:31:31,72 --> 00:31:34,35
六弟，五哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I swear I'll avenge you!

705
00:31:40,00 --> 00:31:42,30
六哥，七弟发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I vow to avenge you!

706
00:31:42,52 --> 00:31:44,98
二哥喝醉了，他让我带话
Two is drunk. I am pledging for him.

707
00:31:45,16 --> 00:31:46,91
二哥发誓替你报仇！
He will avenge your death, too.

708
00:31:53,32 --> 00:31:56,31
六弟，三哥发誓替你报仇！
Brother, I swear to avenge you!

709
00:31:56,68 --> 00:31:58,79
二哥没喝醉，他生气了！
Two is sober, he's just pissed off!

710
00:31:59,20 --> 00:32:00,75
大哥不想让大伙拼命
Chief doesn't want to risk our lives.

711
00:32:00,92 --> 00:32:02,91
命都不拼，还算麻匪吗？
Are we boy scouts or what?

712
00:20:13,20 --> 00:20:15,79
你磕头！你数数！
You kowtow, and you do the counting.

713
00:20:16,24 --> 00:20:21,91
一二三四五六…
One, two, three, four...

714
00:20:22,08 --> 00:20:23,99
青天大老爷！
Hail, Governor!

715
00:21:39,88 --> 00:21:42,11
这帮买官的县长，就知道捞钱
Politicians only know how to bully.

716
00:54:30,64 --> 00:54:33,35
不该一进城就枪毙麻匪
You shouldn't have shot those bandits.

717
00:54:33,60 --> 00:54:36,83
他们一定会报复你的
They'll take revenge for sure.

718
00:54:37,68 --> 00:54:39,71
不哭，不哭
Don't cry.

719
00:54:39,88 --> 00:54:42,07
她是为鹅城死的
She died for Goose Town.

720
00:54:42,40 --> 00:54:44,91
得厚葬她呀
She deserves a proper burial!

721
00:54:46,96 --> 00:54:50,07
得让所有的乡绅都过来
Invite every townsfolk to attend.

722
00:56:59,76 --> 00:57:00,67
有粗有细啊！
I am impressed!

723
00:57:00,84 --> 00:57:02,71
三天之内，钱不到就撕票！
We'll kill the hostages in 3 days!

724
00:57:02,88 --> 00:57:05,55
记着，我是九筒！
Remember, I am Nine!

725
00:57:08,40 --> 00:57:09,95
这活办的真爽快！
That was quite a show.

726
00:57:10,12 --> 00:57:11,51
像真的吗？ 像！
- Almost pass for real! - Sure.

727
00:57:11,68 --> 00:57:14,19
要是有人再流点血就更像真的了！
It'll be more convincing with some blood.

728
00:57:14,36 --> 00:57:15,34
对！
Right!

729
00:57:16,84 --> 00:57:18,19
有这个必要吗？
Was that necessary?

730
00:57:18,36 --> 00:57:20,71
有这个必要吗？有这个必要吗？
Was that really necessary?

731
00:57:28,24 --> 00:57:29,95
给我打！给我狠狠打！
Shoot! Give them hell!

732
00:49:20,32 --> 00:49:24,02
六子，黄四郎今天死了三条狗
Three of Huang's dogs died today.

733
00:49:24,96 --> 00:49:28,19
我知道，狗命抵不了你的命
I know they're not worthy of you.

734
00:49:28,56 --> 00:49:29,62
我本来带着弟兄们
I was going to lead our brothers,

735
00:49:29,80 --> 00:49:31,95
要跟黄四郎拼个鱼死网破
engage Huang in a deadly duel,

736
00:55:04,96 --> 00:55:10,08

"Master Six rests here in peace"

737
00:55:10,28 --> 00:55:13,15
…放下今生的担子
...to be relieved of life's burden.

738
00:55:13,36 --> 00:55:17,39
我们就亲切的将他放入土中
Thus we commit their bodies to earth.

739
00:55:18,12 --> 00:55:20,39
他们本是尘土
From which they came,

740
00:55:20,80 --> 00:55:24,75
现在，他们依然是尘土
and do now return.

741
00:55:24,96 --> 00:55:28,95
我们知道，这一切的生命气息
We know we can place ourselves,

742
00:55:29,12 --> 00:55:33,55
都在永生的慈爱的天父手里
in the hands of our Father in Heaven,

743
00:55:33,76 --> 00:55:37,67
而且他应允将永生…
who has promised us eternal life.

744
00:55:39,32 --> 00:55:41,27
我们是张麻子张大爷的队伍！
We're from "Pocky" Zhang's gang.

745
00:55:41,88 --> 00:55:43,27
要钱！不要命！
We're here for the money.

746
00:55:43,68 --> 00:55:44,63
各位乡绅受惊了
Sorry for the intrusion!

747
00:55:44,80 --> 00:55:46,11
我们今天就是来找几个人
We're looking for...

748
00:55:46,28 --> 00:55:49,87
黄四郎！城南两大家族！站出来
Huang, heads of families, show yourselves!

749
00:55:57,40 --> 00:55:58,27
胡万？
Hu Wan?

750
00:55:59,92 --> 00:56:01,59
神父，打扰了
Father, our apologies.

751
00:56:02,04 --> 00:56:02,59
各位父老
Ladies and gentlemen,

752
00:56:02,76 --> 00:56:04,51
剩下的事情就与你们无关了
the rest has nothing to do with this.

753
00:56:04,68 --> 00:56:05,63
再见
Leave!

754
00:56:06,04 --> 00:56:06,95
入袋
Gag them!

755
00:56:08,64 --> 00:56:09,55
起来
Get up!

756
00:56:11,76 --> 00:56:13,27
好汉！我是本县县长
I'm the governor of this county.

757
00:56:13,44 --> 00:56:14,42
要绑，绑我吧
I volunteer to be your hostage.

758
00:56:14,64 --> 00:56:15,62
你不说话不行吗！
Just shut up!

759
00:56:15,80 --> 00:56:17,43
留着你的命，活着替我们收钱
We spare you to deliver our ransom.

760
00:56:17,64 --> 00:56:19,35
三天之内，钱到，放人
Three days, pay up and they go home.

761
00:56:19,60 --> 00:56:20,95
钱不到，撕票 打死我吧
- If not, they die. - Shoot me first!

762
00:56:21,12 --> 00:56:22,43
别打别打！ 打死我！
- Stop it! - Shoot me first!

763
00:56:22,64 --> 00:56:23,43
找打是吧
You're asking for it.

764
00:56:24,16 --> 00:56:26,03
打…！
Beat him up!

765
00:56:26,20 --> 00:56:27,83
你怎么这么多嘴啊！
You talk too much!

766
00:56:28,32 --> 00:56:30,23
让你多嘴
I'll teach you a lesson!

767
00:56:33,72 --> 00:56:35,83
你装模做样的带我的九筒干什么
Stop messing with my mask!

768
00:56:36,00 --> 00:56:36,75
别把事给我办砸了！
Don't screw things up.

769
00:56:37,32 --> 00:56:37,99
带走！
Take them away!

770
00:57:34,56 --> 00:57:38,15
三天收不到钱，麻匪可是要撕票的！
Otherwise they will kill the hostages.

771
00:57:38,32 --> 00:57:40,35
撕！让他们撕！
Let them kill the hostages.

772
00:57:40,56 --> 00:57:42,86
一定要让他们撕
In fact, I want them dead!

773
00:57:43,04 --> 00:57:45,87
替身就是为我干这个的
Why do you think I need a double?

774
00:57:46,04 --> 00:57:48,31
这个钱，我一分钱都不出！
I'll not pay any ransom.

775
00:57:48,52 --> 00:57:50,51
不过两大家族的钱
But the families will pay up.

776
00:57:50,68 --> 00:57:52,31
一定会过你们的手
You'll get your money for sure.

777
00:57:53,24 --> 00:57:54,35
弟弟
Brother,

778
00:57:55,04 --> 00:57:56,55
不要为我担心啊！
I'm fine.

779
00:57:56,72 --> 00:57:59,07
千万不要为我担心！
Don't worry about me.

780
00:58:00,80 --> 00:58:03,23
老爷，我怀疑胡万投靠了张麻子
Hu Wan must have defected to Zhang.

781
00:58:03,40 --> 00:58:04,35
一定要找到胡万！
He must be found,

782
00:58:04,56 --> 00:58:07,27
活要见人，死要见尸
dead or alive!

783
00:52:31,08 --> 00:52:32,59
骗豪绅，刮百姓
Creating more chances for Huang to swindle.

784
00:52:32,76 --> 00:52:33,35
然后呢？
And then?

785
00:52:33,56 --> 00:52:34,23
没了 没了？
- That's all. - Really?

786
00:52:34,40 --> 00:52:35,38
其他事我真不知道！
I don't know anything else!

787
00:52:55,88 --> 00:52:57,19
可大哥您脸上没麻子
Where are your pockmarks?

788
00:52:57,36 --> 00:52:58,91
黄四郎脸上有四吗？
Does your boss have "Huang" inscribed on his face?

789
00:53:00,56 --> 00:53:01,31
懂了
That's true.

790
00:53:01,52 --> 00:53:02,79
兄弟
My friend,

791
00:53:03,64 --> 00:53:05,07
我是张麻子这件事
you must not tell anyone,

792
00:53:05,24 --> 00:53:06,91
要替我永远保密
that I am "Pocky" Zhang.

793
00:53:07,08 --> 00:53:07,75
永远保密！
You have my word!

794
00:53:07,92 --> 00:53:11,03
我说我当不了县长
I never want to be a governor,

795
00:53:11,24 --> 00:53:15,83
你非花钱让我买这个官
but you still bought me this post!

796
00:53:17,56 --> 00:53:21,18
现在官被人家抢走了
The position has been usurped,

797
00:53:21,68 --> 00:53:25,79
你也就这么死了！
and now you're dead too.

798
00:53:26,88 --> 00:53:27,99
黄四郎带人来了
Huang has brought his militia.

799
00:53:28,16 --> 00:53:29,59
说是要帮我们打麻匪
Wanting to fight bandits with us.

800
00:58:15,60 --> 00:58:16,51
砸了
Yes, game's up.

801
00:58:16,68 --> 00:58:20,71
我怎么觉得…刚开始啊！
The fun has only just begun.

802
00:58:20,92 --> 00:58:22,63
阿门！
Amen!

803
00:58:33,24 --> 00:58:34,03
放人！
Release them.

804
00:58:34,20 --> 00:58:36,66
给你们留个纪念，不准回头，滚！
Here's a souvenir. Don't look back. Scram!

805
00:58:42,24 --> 00:58:44,95
夫人，你要是晚走两天
Ma'am, if you're still alive,

806
00:58:45,12 --> 00:58:47,11
就能亲眼看见了
you'd see this for yourself.

807
00:58:47,28 --> 00:58:49,99
嫂子要是不走，这钱都到不了这桌上
If she was alive, there'll be nothing here.

808
00:58:50,16 --> 00:58:53,03
对，我老婆的命换来的这些钱
She traded her life for this.

809
00:58:53,44 --> 00:58:54,91
那我们家小六子的命不算命啊？
Doesn't Six's life count?

810
00:58:55,08 --> 00:58:55,83
那不一样！
It's different.

811
00:58:56,00 --> 00:58:56,83
怎么就不一样啊？
Goddamned it isn't!

812
00:58:57,00 --> 00:58:57,67
夫人！
My wife.

813
00:58:57,84 --> 00:58:58,35
谁夫人啊？
Whose wife?

814
00:58:58,56 --> 00:58:59,19
我夫人！
Mine.

815
00:58:59,36 --> 00:58:59,87
你夫人怎么了？
What about her?

816
00:59:00,04 --> 00:59:01,95
夫人是被黄四郎杀死的
She was murdered by Huang.

817
00:59:02,12 --> 00:59:05,11
你们家六爷自残，自杀！
But Six died at his own hands.

818
00:59:06,00 --> 00:59:06,79
我一枪崩了你
I'll shoot you dead,

819
00:59:06,96 --> 00:59:08,91
你敢说我们家小六子，找死啊！
for demeaning our Six!

820
00:59:09,08 --> 00:59:10,43
老二你把枪放下
Two, put down your gun.

821
00:59:10,64 --> 00:59:11,62
别拿枪对着我
Stop pointing your gun at me!

822
00:59:11,80 --> 00:59:13,95
我见过土匪，没见过练肌肉的土匪
I've never seen bandits as dumb as you!

823
00:59:16,44 --> 00:59:18,87
笑什么啊，别笑，别笑！
Stop laughing! Cut it out.

824
00:59:19,04 --> 00:59:21,91
我是说你们家六爷，你们家六爷这样
I didn't belittle Six! He had courage!

825
00:59:22,08 --> 00:59:23,14
那是英雄
He was a hero!

826
00:59:23,36 --> 00:59:24,67
是，是英雄
Yes, he was heroic.

827
00:59:24,84 --> 00:59:31,02
我老婆睡着觉，就没醒过来
My wife went to sleep and died in bed.

828
00:59:32,00 --> 00:59:33,99
师爷不哭，嫂子也是英雄
Don't cry! Your wife was heroic, too.

829
00:59:34,36 --> 00:59:36,19
各位哥哥，咱们为什么来了？
Brothers, why are we here?

830
00:59:36,36 --> 00:59:37,19
钱啊
To get rich!

831
01:01:11,60 --> 01:01:14,75
老天爷都能当，还收拾不了一个黄四郎？
If I am God, ridding him should be a piece of cake.

832
00:56:39,20 --> 00:56:40,34
是他！ 老三！
- It's him. - Three!

833
00:56:40,56 --> 00:56:41,51
装箱
Pack them!

834
00:56:43,80 --> 00:56:44,99
不见钱不放人啊！
No one goes until we get his ransom.

835
00:56:45,80 --> 00:56:47,87
千哥，忍着！
Butler, stay calm!

836
00:56:50,40 --> 00:56:52,27
一二三！
One, two, three...

837
00:56:52,76 --> 00:56:54,11
黄四郎在里头
Huang is in there!

838
00:56:54,28 --> 00:56:55,95
一二三！
One, two, three...

839
00:56:56,84 --> 00:56:58,51
你抱着我夫人学我哭的时候
You plotted this scheme

840
00:56:58,68 --> 00:56:59,59
就想到这招了
over my wife's dead body?

841
00:59:37,36 --> 00:59:37,99
钱到了吗？
Have we succeeded?

842
00:59:38,16 --> 00:59:39,22
到了
Yes, we have.

843
00:59:40,00 --> 00:59:40,83
走啊！
So let's leave!

844
00:59:41,00 --> 00:59:41,59
走啊
Let's go.

845
00:59:41,76 --> 00:59:42,51
那你还哭什么呀？
Why are you still in tears?

846
00:59:42,68 --> 00:59:43,35
我可以不哭
I'm overjoyed.

847
00:59:43,56 --> 00:59:44,91
大哥，什么时候走？
Chief, when do we leave?

848
01:01:06,64 --> 01:01:08,07
你不就是想当老天爷吗？
Haven't you always wanted to play God?

849
01:01:08,24 --> 01:01:08,91
是啊
Yes.

850
01:01:09,08 --> 01:01:11,43
这跟收拾黄四郎有什么关系呀？
What has it got to do with Huang?

851
01:02:27,44 --> 01:02:29,51
还为了一个女人
and we're bickering over a broad!

852
01:02:43,36 --> 01:02:46,95
我进城那天，带头敲鼓的是你吧
You're the lead drummer at my inauguration?

853
01:02:48,40 --> 01:02:50,86
姑娘，贵姓？
What's your name?

854
01:02:51,08 --> 01:02:53,23
不客气，花姐
Call me Flora.

855
01:02:53,60 --> 01:02:55,59
不是姓黄吧？
Are you related to Huang?

856
01:02:55,88 --> 01:02:58,59
不姓！是黄四郎把我买来的
No, he bought me.

857
01:03:00,32 --> 01:03:03,03
城门口贴的那些告示
There are posters by the city gate.

858
01:03:03,36 --> 01:03:04,99
知道是什么意思吧？
Know what they're for?

859
01:03:05,60 --> 01:03:07,27
通缉张麻子的
Bounty offers for "Pocky" Zhang.

860
01:03:09,00 --> 01:03:11,38
我就是张麻子
I am "Pocky" Zhang.

861
01:03:12,96 --> 01:03:15,79
麻匪发的，铁证如山！
The bandits were behind this.

862
01:03:16,36 --> 01:03:20,55
用面具的就是麻匪？我们也有面具
Is it because of the masks? We have masks too!

863
01:03:20,80 --> 01:03:22,27
那就是县长？
Then it must be the Governor!

864
01:03:24,24 --> 01:03:26,95
有钱不赚，发给穷人
He is giving money to the poor?

865
01:03:30,04 --> 01:03:32,60
这像是个买官的县长做的事吗？
No bogus governor would do that.

866
01:03:35,12 --> 01:03:38,03
今天，我要你们扮成麻匪
I want you to dress up as bandits.

867
01:03:38,20 --> 01:03:39,83
跟他们一模一样
Exactly like them.

868
01:03:40,00 --> 01:03:42,83
他们怎么发，你们就怎么抢！
What they give out, you take away.

869
01:03:43,12 --> 01:03:44,18
搞乱他们！
Let's cause havoc!

870
01:03:44,64 --> 01:03:45,51
明白！
Understood.

871
01:03:45,68 --> 01:03:48,79
三步棋必治他于死地
I'll have him checkmate in 3 moves!

872
01:03:49,60 --> 01:03:52,43
老爷，三步棋，咱们都已经走完了
But we've made 3 moves already.

873
01:03:53,16 --> 01:03:53,63
是吗？
Really?

874
01:03:53,76 --> 01:03:55,67
逼死小六子，杀鸡取卵…
Driving Six to death, killing the chicken for the eggs...

875
00:58:07,60 --> 00:58:10,55
替身这么有用啊！得空帮我也找一个
A double is useful. Find me one, too.

876
00:58:10,72 --> 00:58:13,28
张麻子，你真是死不要脸
Pocky, have you no shame?

877
00:58:13,44 --> 00:58:14,71
玩砸了！
The game's up!

878
00:58:14,88 --> 00:58:15,39
砸了吗？
Really?

879
01:01:26,52 --> 01:01:27,95
这个，我认识
I think I know her.

880
00:54:50,20 --> 00:54:53,59
都来都来，我会安排
Certainly. I'll take care of it.

881
00:54:59,40 --> 00:55:04,26

"Here lies Madam Governor"

882
01:02:13,56 --> 01:02:16,83
见过麻匪真面目的，必死无疑！
Whoever sees a bandit's face has to die.

883
01:02:17,00 --> 01:02:18,51
这可是你下的令
It's your own rule.

884
01:02:18,68 --> 01:02:19,87
师爷
Counselor.

885
01:02:20,60 --> 01:02:22,75
第一个见过麻匪真面目的人
The first to see our faces

886
01:02:22,92 --> 01:02:24,23
是你！
was you!

887
01:02:24,80 --> 01:02:27,26
事还没办呢就起内证！
Our mission is only half accomplished,

888
01:03:57,40 --> 01:03:59,43
现在我要走的新三步
I'm talking about 3 new moves!

889
01:03:59,64 --> 01:04:02,55
第一步，到省城查清马邦德
First, check out the Governor.

890
01:04:02,72 --> 01:04:05,87
我总觉得他不像是个买官的县长
He doesn't act like someone who'd buy a post.

891
01:04:06,60 --> 01:04:08,87
起码，不姓马！
At least, he's not Ma Bangde.

892
01:04:10,24 --> 01:04:11,55
胡万的事怎么样了？
Have you found Hu Wan?

893
01:04:12,24 --> 01:04:14,43
胡万？还没找到
Hu Wan? Not yet.

894
01:04:15,28 --> 01:04:17,31
你怎么可能说还没有找到
How come he is still missing?

895
01:04:17,52 --> 01:04:19,63
老爷你放心，我会去找他，继续找
Don't worry, sir. I'll find him.

896
01:04:19,80 --> 01:04:21,07
你晓不晓得…
Do you know...

897
01:04:22,52 --> 01:04:24,51
我多么的想他
how much I miss him?

898
01:04:38,16 --> 01:04:40,75
黄老爷盼咐我们把他们搞乱
On master's order, let's wreak havoc!

899
01:04:41,16 --> 01:04:43,43
看老子怎么把他们搞乱
Let's show how we can mess things up!

900
01:04:45,88 --> 01:04:46,63
收到银子了？
Did you get your share?

901
01:04:46,80 --> 01:04:48,27
收到了
Yes.

902
01:04:49,00 --> 01:04:50,87
那你打算怎么感谢我们
How are you going to thank us?

903
01:04:51,72 --> 01:04:54,75
怎么感谢都…都行
Any way you like.

904
01:04:55,32 --> 01:04:58,63
怎么感谢都行？你说的！好！
Any way I like? Great, you said it!

905
01:05:00,32 --> 01:05:03,75
知道我们…为什么会给你发银子吗？
Know why we gave you money?

906
01:05:04,08 --> 01:05:06,64
因为麻匪爷对我们好
It is because you're benevolent.

907
01:05:06,80 --> 01:05:07,94
对你好？
Benevolent?

908
01:05:08,12 --> 01:05:09,75
还没好透！
We can do even better!

909
01:05:16,96 --> 01:05:20,58
透！透！透！
Batter! Batter!

910
01:05:28,12 --> 01:05:31,99
青天大老爷做主啊！
Governor, we want justice!

911
01:05:32,20 --> 01:05:34,19
砸了你们！砸了！
It's all over! We're finished!

912
01:05:34,84 --> 01:05:37,27
兔子都知道不吃窝边草
Even rabbits wouldn't do this.

913
01:05:37,64 --> 01:05:39,94
六个人，还当着人家丈夫
Six men, in front of her husband,

914
01:05:40,12 --> 01:05:41,23
还让人看
and in broad daylight!

915
01:05:41,40 --> 01:05:43,35
呸！恶心
Disgusting!

916
01:05:43,56 --> 01:05:45,03
我都关着灯！
I've never even done this with lights on!

917
01:05:46,16 --> 01:05:48,35
这种事你们可以花点钱嘛！
If you're desperate, paid for it!

918
01:05:48,76 --> 01:05:49,95
花点！
Be extravagant!

919
01:05:50,32 --> 01:05:51,91
哪怕缥呢！
Visit a brothel!

920
01:05:52,12 --> 01:05:53,75
花不了多少钱！
It won't cost much!

921
01:05:53,92 --> 01:05:55,39
哪怕偷偷摸摸的
You don't even have to be discreet.

922
01:05:56,00 --> 01:05:58,03
简直就是土匪
This is stupid!

923
01:05:58,20 --> 01:05:59,91
土匪都不如！
You're worse than bandits!

924
01:06:00,96 --> 01:06:03,11
还说让人家百姓夸你们好
And we'd wanted to leave a good impression!

925
00:59:47,64 --> 00:59:48,67
不走！
We're not.

926
00:59:49,04 --> 00:59:51,03
钱不是黄四郎送来的
This is not Huang's money.

927
00:59:51,20 --> 00:59:54,11
大哥，两大家族的钱不算钱啊？
But the money's still good!

928
00:59:54,28 --> 00:59:56,63
我要的是黄四郎的钱！
I want Huang's fortune.

929
00:59:58,00 --> 01:00:00,83
你不刮穷人的钱，也不要大户的钱…
You refuse to take money from rich or poor...

930
01:00:01,00 --> 01:00:04,70
六子，夫人，两条命
The blood debt of Six and Madam,

931
01:00:04,88 --> 01:00:07,03
必须黄四郎来偿！
must be repaid by Huang!

932
01:00:07,20 --> 01:00:09,55
你这是玩命啊！赌徒！
You're gambling with our lives!

933
01:00:09,72 --> 01:00:10,83
这就算赌了？
You call this a gamble?

934
01:00:11,00 --> 01:00:14,03
算！就是！还赌不赢
Yes, and you'll end up a loser!

935
01:00:17,56 --> 01:00:18,70
人不走
We're not leaving.

936
01:00:19,16 --> 01:00:20,27
钱也都不要了！
We don't want this money either.

937
01:00:20,44 --> 01:00:21,39
发出去！
Give them away.

938
01:00:21,60 --> 01:00:22,82
可是，大哥
But Chief...

939
01:00:24,20 --> 01:00:25,87
这钱你都发给谁呢？
Who do you want to give this to?

940
01:00:26,96 --> 01:00:28,35
发给穷人叹！
To the poor.

941
01:00:28,72 --> 01:00:30,27
那谁是穷人啊？
Who are the poor?

942
01:00:30,44 --> 01:00:33,35
谁穷，谁就是穷人
Those in dire need.

943
01:00:56,96 --> 01:00:58,59
劫我的时候，你戴的就是九筒
You wore "Nine" when you ambushed me.

944
01:00:58,76 --> 01:00:59,79
我这是多少？
What am I wearing now?

945
01:00:59,96 --> 01:01:01,18
你自己摸摸
Feel it for yourself.

946
01:01:02,60 --> 01:01:03,79
洲卜产卜 一同
"One"!

947
01:01:04,84 --> 01:01:05,35
过瘾吗？
Fun, isn't it?

948
01:01:05,56 --> 01:01:06,43
过瘾！
Brilliant!

949
01:09:33,32 --> 01:09:34,23
这就能骑？
I can ride that?

950
01:09:34,40 --> 01:09:36,23
我们在上海骑过！
We rode one once in Shanghai.

951
01:09:36,80 --> 01:09:37,99
你们俩去过上海？
You have been to Shanghai?

952
01:09:38,24 --> 01:09:39,11
浦东
Pudong!

953
01:09:39,36 --> 01:09:42,19
不信，骑上准倒！
I'm sure you'd fall over.

954
01:09:43,44 --> 01:09:45,51
来！试试！
Come on. Try it.

955
01:06:39,92 --> 01:06:41,95
大哥，你是了解我的
You know me,

956
01:06:42,28 --> 01:06:43,39
如果是我…
If it was me,

957
01:06:44,16 --> 01:06:46,03
不会有人活着来告状
she wouldn't have lived to squeal.

958
01:06:47,56 --> 01:06:48,70
大哥你是了解我的
You know me.

959
01:06:48,88 --> 01:06:50,55
我老五虽然岁数最大
I may be the eldest,

960
01:06:50,96 --> 01:06:52,87
我…我至今…
but I am...

961
01:06:54,84 --> 01:06:56,11
俗称处男
still a virgin.

962
01:07:00,56 --> 01:07:01,78
别看着我呀
Stop staring at me!

963
01:07:01,96 --> 01:07:03,95
大哥，你是了解我的
You know me well.

964
01:07:04,28 --> 01:07:05,63
如果我出手…
If I was responsible,

965
01:07:05,92 --> 01:07:07,35
那趴在桌子上的
the one on the receiving end,

966
01:07:08,04 --> 01:07:09,63
应该是她老公
would have been her husband!

967
01:07:15,20 --> 01:07:19,63
我听出来了，你们都个个身怀绝技
Each of you is so unique.

968
01:07:21,80 --> 01:07:22,94
但是…
But...

969
01:07:23,28 --> 01:07:24,07
有人骗了我
I've been betrayed.

970
01:07:24,24 --> 01:07:25,38
谁呀？谁呀？
By who?

971
01:07:26,72 --> 01:07:27,94
老汤
Tang!

972
01:07:28,12 --> 01:07:31,11
这么明显的事，一个师爷看不出来？
How could he overlook the obvious?

973
01:07:31,44 --> 01:07:34,51
这明明是黄四郎狗狼养的找人冒充的
Huang is behind this scam.

974
01:07:35,12 --> 01:07:36,99
他今天很反常
Tang's not behaving properly.

975
01:07:37,24 --> 01:07:38,95
心里一定有鬼
He must be up to something.

976
01:07:39,88 --> 01:07:42,23
出来！起来！站起来！
Come out! Stand up!

977
01:07:48,28 --> 01:07:51,79
你最近跟什么人吃过饭？
Who have you been seeing lately?

978
01:07:52,04 --> 01:07:53,02
见过黄四郎？
Master Huang?

979
01:07:53,32 --> 01:07:54,19
不许动！举起腿来！
Don't move! Raise your legs.

980
01:01:28,12 --> 01:01:29,26
我也认识
So do I!

981
01:01:29,52 --> 01:01:30,91
给她发点钱吧
Let's give her some money.

982
01:01:31,64 --> 01:01:33,11
干什么呀？
Hang on!

983
01:01:33,28 --> 01:01:35,95
大哥说了，发穷人！她不穷
She is not exactly poor, is she?

984
01:01:36,12 --> 01:01:38,31
那你说，谁算穷人？
So who are the poor?

985
01:01:38,52 --> 01:01:41,99
穷人？那就得被逼得卖儿卖女！
Those who're forced to sell their own children.

986
01:01:42,16 --> 01:01:45,27
她，就是被穷人卖掉的女儿！
Correct! She was sold by her parents.

987
01:01:45,52 --> 01:01:46,79
对呀！
Make sense!

988
01:02:00,28 --> 01:02:02,84
原来县长的人是麻匪！
So you're bandits in disguise!

989
01:02:03,00 --> 01:02:05,63
我们就想给你发点钱！
We've come to give you money.

990
01:02:06,64 --> 01:02:08,39
杀！必须的！
Kill her. No option!

991
01:07:57,92 --> 01:07:59,14
你是个孩子？
You're a child?

992
01:07:59,52 --> 01:08:00,63
几岁？ 八岁！
- How old are you? - Eight!

993
01:08:01,08 --> 01:08:02,14
出来！
Come out!

994
01:08:05,16 --> 01:08:06,30
这是八岁？!
He's eight?

995
01:08:06,60 --> 01:08:08,15
没人信！我都不信！
I find it hard to believe myself!

996
01:08:08,32 --> 01:08:09,71
三岁跟他妈一样高
As tall as Mom when he was three.

997
01:08:09,88 --> 01:08:12,51
五岁就跟我一样高，八岁就这样了
Taller than me when he was five...

998
01:08:12,80 --> 01:08:14,19
你妈！你妈！
Screw you!

999
01:08:16,36 --> 01:08:17,07
妈！妈！
Mom, mom!

1000
01:08:17,24 --> 01:08:18,35
你妈！
Screw you!

1001
01:08:18,80 --> 01:08:19,71
敢打俺娃！
Hands off my boy!

1002
01:08:19,92 --> 01:08:23,15
你妈！ 你妈！
- Screw you! - Screw you, too!

1003
01:08:23,32 --> 01:08:24,71
你妈！
Screw you!

1004
01:08:27,28 --> 01:08:27,95
这是你亲妈？
She's your mother?

1005
01:08:28,12 --> 01:08:28,91
是我妈
Yes, she is.

1006
01:08:29,04 --> 01:08:29,75
这是你亲爹？
And he's your dad?

1007
01:08:29,92 --> 01:08:32,27
我家的事关你屁事啊！你妈！
None of your goddamned business.

1008
01:08:32,96 --> 01:08:33,99
你妈！
Stop it!

1009
01:08:34,56 --> 01:08:35,83
嫂子！怎么回事？
Ma'am, what's going on?

1010
01:08:36,00 --> 01:08:38,03
我是来要钱的，不给钱我不走
I come for money. I won't leave until he pays.

1011
01:08:38,20 --> 01:08:39,18
不给钱不走
He owes you?

1012
01:08:39,36 --> 01:08:43,27
这个老骗子，八年前在俺山西开矿
It was eight years ago in Shanxi.

1013
01:08:43,44 --> 01:08:46,31
骗了钱我就不说了，还骗了我的身子
This crook made me pregnant.

1014
01:08:46,52 --> 01:08:47,71
还不讲信誉
He is a man of poor repute.

1015
01:08:48,12 --> 01:08:49,15
他欠一屁股帐
Ran up a mountain of debts,

1016
01:08:49,32 --> 01:08:50,35
拍屁股走了
then vanished without trace.

1017
01:08:50,56 --> 01:08:53,31
人家问俺追帐，把我六岁的娃给绑了
Creditors kidnapped my younger son.

1018
01:08:53,52 --> 01:08:55,79
当人质呢，不给钱就撕票了！
He'll die if I don't clear his debts.

1019
01:08:55,96 --> 01:08:56,59
那不是我的
He's not my child!

1020
01:08:56,76 --> 01:08:57,74
那就是你的
He is!

1021
01:08:57,96 --> 01:08:59,10
不是我的 就是你的！
- He isn't. - He is!

1022
01:08:59,28 --> 01:09:01,23
是你的，我算着日子呢！
He is! I counted the days!

1023
01:09:48,60 --> 01:09:49,66
上来
Hop on!

1024
01:09:52,80 --> 01:09:54,11
走，走了！
Let's go!

1025
01:10:02,64 --> 01:10:03,95
自行车！
Bicycle!

1026
01:10:06,08 --> 01:10:07,43
自行车！
Bicycle!

1027
01:10:09,52 --> 01:10:12,43
可是，人肉的自行车
made of flesh and bones...

1028
01:10:14,44 --> 01:10:15,95
我来错地方了？
Have I come to the wrong place?

1029
01:10:16,44 --> 01:10:18,27
我来的不是时候？
Or at the wrong time?

1030
01:10:18,68 --> 01:10:19,35
接客
Serve your customers.

1031
01:10:19,56 --> 01:10:20,27
他们俩都是
They're my customers.

1032
01:03:55,84 --> 01:03:57,23
那是老三步了
Those were old moves!

1033
01:06:03,28 --> 01:06:05,35
就是一句话！恶心！
One word comes to mind: revolting!

1034
01:06:05,56 --> 01:06:07,31
钱肯定是赚不着了！
Our scheme is now in ruin!

1035
01:06:07,56 --> 01:06:09,51
恶心！恶心！
Disgusting!

1036
01:06:09,88 --> 01:06:11,99
恶心呐！恶心！
Filthy, nauseating...

1037
01:06:12,36 --> 01:06:14,79
呸！太恶心！
Revolting!

1038
01:06:24,84 --> 01:06:26,55
大哥，你是了解我的
You know me.

1039
01:06:26,92 --> 01:06:29,15
我从来不做仗势欺人的事
When it comes to this sort of thing,

1040
01:06:29,88 --> 01:06:31,39
我喜欢被动
I prefer to be passive...

1041
01:06:32,60 --> 01:06:34,11
大哥你是了解我的
You know me,

1042
01:06:34,60 --> 01:06:35,87
以我的习’惯
I am a lone wolf,

1043
01:06:36,88 --> 01:06:38,43
万事不求人
always acting on my own.

1044
01:14:40,72 --> 01:14:41,75
他戴的是几筒？
Which mask does he wear?

1045
01:10:36,88 --> 01:10:38,83
那不是麻匪扔进来的吗？
Isn't that bandit money?

1046
01:10:40,40 --> 01:10:42,70
难道他们俩是麻匪？
I wonder if they are also bandits.

1047
01:10:42,88 --> 01:10:45,79
他们不是麻匪，他们是官府的人
No, they work for the Governor.

1048
01:10:47,04 --> 01:10:49,50
你敢拿麻匪的钱给他们付帐？
How dare you pay their tab with bandit money?

1049
01:10:49,68 --> 01:10:51,55
别废话！先把人放了，快点！
Cut the crap! Let her go!

1050
01:10:54,04 --> 01:10:55,83
英雄救美！
White knights to the rescue!

1051
01:10:57,56 --> 01:10:59,35
英雄救美！
White knights to the rescue!

1052
01:11:01,92 --> 01:11:05,43
就算他们是英雄，我也不是美人
I'm no damsel in distress.

1053
01:11:06,20 --> 01:11:09,87
就算我是美人，他们也不是英雄
They're no knights in shining armour.

1054
01:11:32,00 --> 01:11:34,03
老爷，毕竟他们是客人
After all, they're customers.

1055
01:11:34,20 --> 01:11:37,23
今天晚上的钱，我替他们付了
I've already settled their bills.

1056
01:11:37,60 --> 01:11:39,11
您不是常教育我们吗
You taught me yourself,

1057
01:11:39,28 --> 01:11:41,07
客人永远是上帝
customers are always supreme!

1058
01:11:41,36 --> 01:11:42,91
您说对吗？
Isn't that right?

1059
01:11:46,80 --> 01:11:47,83
对！
Yes!

1060
01:11:48,52 --> 01:11:49,58
对！
Correct!

1061
01:12:05,76 --> 01:12:08,95
这就不是英雄救美了
Instead of knights coming to your rescue,

1062
01:12:09,52 --> 01:12:11,71
是美救英雄
they are being saved by a damsel.

1063
01:12:13,04 --> 01:12:17,15
你呀，快成小凤仙儿了
You're turning into a Mata Hari.

1064
01:12:29,68 --> 01:12:30,79
你得罪他了！
You've just pissed him off.

1065
01:12:31,04 --> 01:12:32,31
黄四郎不用得罪
He doesn't need to be pissed off.

1066
01:12:32,52 --> 01:12:33,95
他想让谁死
If he wants you dead,

1067
01:12:34,12 --> 01:12:35,55
谁就得死！
you die!

1068
01:12:35,72 --> 01:12:37,55
我刚才干嘛不一枪打死他呢？
I should've put a bullet through his head.

1069
01:12:37,72 --> 01:12:39,43
我一枪打死他不就完了么！
That would be the end of it.

1070
01:12:40,12 --> 01:12:41,07
别傻了！
Don't be silly.

1071
01:12:41,24 --> 01:12:44,27
大哥说了，留着他是要弄他的钱
Chief wants to go after his fortune.

1072
01:12:45,32 --> 01:12:48,27
既然想弄钱，那…
If you're here for the money, then...

1073
01:12:48,60 --> 01:12:50,55
你们干嘛到处发钱啊？
why are you giving it away?

1074
01:12:52,24 --> 01:12:52,79
这颜色行么
Is this the right colour?

1075
01:12:52,96 --> 01:12:54,27
把伞拿了
Lower the umbrella.

1076
01:12:54,84 --> 01:12:57,27
红倒是够了，你…你过来
The red is fine. Come over here!

1077
01:12:58,44 --> 01:13:00,35
先是绿，再弄红
First apply green, then red.

1078
01:13:00,56 --> 01:13:01,43
明白
Okay, got it.

1079
01:13:01,64 --> 01:13:02,91
明白这意思吧？
Understand?

1080
01:13:04,28 --> 01:13:05,50
你把那锁好了啊
Don't forget to lock up.

1081
01:13:05,68 --> 01:13:06,99
带上铁锹 知道了
- Bring the shovels. - Got it.

1082
01:13:07,20 --> 01:13:09,39
六把铁锹 知道了
- Six shovels! - Got it.

1083
01:13:13,08 --> 01:13:13,75
大哥你看我…
Chief, how do I look?

1084
01:13:13,92 --> 01:13:16,83
头不用梳了，脸够红，你过来！
Hair is fine. Face is flushed. Come here...

1085
01:07:54,36 --> 01:07:55,87
谁？！ 孩子！孩子
- Who's there? - A boy, my child!

1086
01:07:56,00 --> 01:07:57,11
孩子？ 我的！
- Your child? - Yes, mine.

1087
01:09:06,24 --> 01:09:07,83
把你的小儿子绑架了
and kidnapped your younger son.

1088
01:09:08,72 --> 01:09:09,43
不给钱就撕票
Threatening death...

1089
01:09:09,64 --> 01:09:11,43
撕票，所以我要钱呢！
Yes, so I need the money.

1090
01:09:11,64 --> 01:09:12,67
给钱！
Pay her.

1091
01:09:13,16 --> 01:09:14,38
钱，石头！
Money! The stones...

1092
01:09:16,04 --> 01:09:17,75
嫂子，初次见面
Just a small gift,

1093
01:09:18,24 --> 01:09:19,55
不成敬意
to mark our acquaintance.

1094
01:09:20,12 --> 01:09:22,58
石头我不要，不给钱我不走
I don't want these. I want real money.

1095
01:09:22,76 --> 01:09:24,15
你个傻…
You stupid idiot...

1096
01:09:24,68 --> 01:09:27,14
这比钱值钱！这是宝石
These diamonds are worth a fortune!

1097
01:09:27,32 --> 01:09:29,23
啊！真的！
No kidding?

1098
01:09:32,08 --> 01:09:33,14
自行车
Bicycle!

1099
01:17:35,96 --> 01:17:37,18
听不见
I can't hear you.

1100
01:17:41,00 --> 01:17:42,06
听不见！
I can't hear you!

1101
01:17:42,24 --> 01:17:43,30
城里麻匪火拼
There was a shoot-out.

1102
01:17:43,52 --> 01:17:46,67
死了六个人！咱们的人安然无恙！
Six killed. We're unscathed.

1103
01:17:55,96 --> 01:17:58,23
师爷，来来，请
Counselor, come take a look.

1104
01:18:01,12 --> 01:18:03,55
或许…是你的恩人呐
Your saviour may be among them.

1105
01:13:17,20 --> 01:13:19,43
死人的脸是绿的，加上点别的色
Apply that to a dead man's face

1106
01:13:19,64 --> 01:13:20,86
然后再变成这种红
will turn it into pinkish red.

1107
01:13:21,04 --> 01:13:22,59
明白了 明白了吧
- Got it. - Good.

1108
01:13:22,76 --> 01:13:23,67
绿
Green.

1109
01:13:24,80 --> 01:13:25,99
你过来
Come here.

1110
01:13:26,60 --> 01:13:27,79
绿在底下
Green is the base colour.

1111
01:13:28,04 --> 01:13:30,11
加上那个再变成这个就对了！
Add that and you'll get this!

1112
01:13:30,68 --> 01:13:32,87
明白了 明白吗
- Oh, I see... - Got it?

1113
01:13:33,04 --> 01:13:33,95
是这样的铁锹吗？
You want shovels like these?

1114
01:13:34,12 --> 01:13:35,18
锯短，装包里
Shorten them and put them in the bag.

1115
01:13:35,36 --> 01:13:35,91
多短？
How short?

1116
01:13:36,08 --> 01:13:37,19
能装包里
Short enough for the bag.

1117
01:13:37,32 --> 01:13:38,83
快去啊，六把啊
Hurry up! Six shovels!

1118
01:13:39,00 --> 01:13:40,11
去哪啊这是？
Where are you going?

1119
01:13:40,28 --> 01:13:41,67
怎么还扮上了？
What's with the make-up?

1120
01:13:41,84 --> 01:13:43,19
不是要跑吧？
Are you leaving for good?

1121
01:13:45,04 --> 01:13:47,55
你去不去？我们去发钱
Come with us to give out money?

1122
01:14:41,92 --> 01:14:42,51
九筒！
"Nine".

1123
01:14:42,68 --> 01:14:46,59
好极了！今晚不抢钱，杀人！
Splendid. Tonight we shall only kill!

1124
01:14:46,76 --> 01:14:47,39
杀谁？
Our target?

1125
01:14:47,60 --> 01:14:48,71
戴九筒的县长！
The Governor, wearing "Nine"!

1126
01:14:48,88 --> 01:14:52,50
杀县长不用戴面具，您等着验尸吧
Masked or not, consider this done!

1127
01:14:52,68 --> 01:14:54,75
回来！全给我戴上！
All of you, put on your masks!

1128
01:14:56,08 --> 01:14:57,43
麻匪火拼
"Firefight with bandits,

1129
01:14:58,16 --> 01:15:00,23
县长暴死
intrepid Governor killed!"

1130
01:15:01,20 --> 01:15:04,90
听着多么川页耳！
That would be music to my ears!

1131
00:21:42,24 --> 00:21:43,91
唱机都撂坏了
This gramophone was broken,

1132
00:21:44,40 --> 00:21:45,75
修好了
Now it is fixed.

1133
00:21:45,92 --> 00:21:48,22
这单活干完了，爹赚了钱
Once we're done here,

1134
00:21:48,40 --> 00:21:49,95
我送你去留洋
I'll let you study abroad.

1135
00:21:50,76 --> 00:21:51,82
东洋三年
3 years in the east,

1136
00:21:52,00 --> 00:21:53,55
西洋三年
3 in the west,

1137
00:21:53,84 --> 00:21:54,59
南洋三年
and 3 more in the south.

1138
00:21:54,76 --> 00:21:56,27
北洋，北洋三年
How about 3 years in the north?

1139
00:21:56,44 --> 00:21:59,83
傻孩子，你生在北洋，不必留了
No, you're born in the north.

1140
00:22:00,92 --> 00:22:02,39
这是谁吹的？
Who is this by?

1141
00:22:05,00 --> 00:22:08,59
听着像穆扎
I think it's Wolfgang.

1142
00:22:09,12 --> 00:22:10,31
他们那边叫穆扎
Sometime known as Amadeus.

1143
00:22:10,52 --> 00:22:12,27
咱们这边叫莫札特
We call him M-o-z-a-r-t.

1144
00:22:12,44 --> 00:22:15,00
你还能听出来是谁吹的呢？!
You can tell by listening?

1145
00:22:15,64 --> 00:22:16,43
得分时候
It depends.

1146
00:22:16,64 --> 00:22:18,11
什么时候？
On what?

1147
00:23:12,20 --> 00:23:13,23
是我自己要去的
It's my own plot.

1148
00:23:13,40 --> 00:23:15,70
没有人让我去，是我自己
There are no co-conspirators.

1149
00:23:16,92 --> 00:23:18,83
恩人！恩人！
Saviour! My saviour!

1150
00:23:21,00 --> 00:23:22,11
恩人！
Saviour!

1151
00:23:24,76 --> 00:23:26,51
你是叫我呢？
You're addressing me?

1152
00:23:27,44 --> 00:23:29,51
我什么时候成你恩人了？
Since when have I become your saviour?

1153
00:23:30,04 --> 00:23:32,19
不杀之恩为大恩！
You spared my life,

1154
00:23:32,44 --> 00:23:36,19
为报不杀之恩，我也救你一命
and I'll save yours in return.

1155
00:23:36,40 --> 00:23:38,51
哦？你快说
Do tell.

1156
00:23:39,84 --> 00:23:42,59
寡妇，不能睡啊！
Never sleep with a widow.

1157
00:23:44,28 --> 00:23:45,99
必有大灾！
It's very bad luck!

1158
00:23:50,64 --> 00:23:52,15
她…
She?

1159
00:23:52,76 --> 00:23:54,71
真的是寡妇么？
Is she really a widow?

1160
00:23:55,56 --> 00:23:57,07
我看着不像
She doesn't act like one.

1161
00:23:57,40 --> 00:24:00,03
我亲眼看见他丈夫淹死的
But I witnessed her husband drowned!

1162
00:24:07,16 --> 00:24:09,23
她已经成了寡妇
If she really is a widow,

1163
00:33:32,72 --> 00:33:34,31
就是恶霸请土匪！
It's just a meeting between two thugs!

1164
00:33:34,52 --> 00:33:36,11
项羽请刘邦啊！
It's like MacBeth hosting Banquo.

1165
00:33:36,28 --> 00:33:37,55
刘邦后来干什么去了？
What'd become of Banquo the guest?

1166
00:33:37,72 --> 00:33:38,31
当皇帝了
His son became king.

1167
00:33:38,52 --> 00:33:39,66
项羽呢？
And MacBeth the host?

1168
00:33:40,64 --> 00:33:43,23
那，赴宴？
So we should go.

1169
00:33:45,28 --> 00:33:48,27
赴宴！正好借机把黄四郎也笼络过来
We can also sound out Huang,

1170
00:33:48,44 --> 00:33:50,51
咱们三个联手一起捞钱
and see if we can work together.

1171
00:33:50,84 --> 00:33:52,43
“把家伙拿来”
"Bring the guns."

1172
00:33:55,60 --> 00:33:56,95
“换上黄家衣服跟我走”
"Dress up as Huang's militia and follow me."

1173
00:33:57,12 --> 00:33:57,95
明白
Got it!

1174
00:33:58,12 --> 00:33:59,55
“干掉黄四郎，给六子报仇”
"Kill Huang and avenge Six!"

1175
00:33:59,72 --> 00:34:01,07
明白
Understood!

1176
00:34:01,80 --> 00:34:06,07
老汤，你是把六子的死当捞钱的成本了？
You see Six's death as a shortcut to bonanza?

1177
00:34:06,52 --> 00:34:09,43
我看你当成本，赚的钱会更多
Perhaps your severed head can make us more.

1178
00:34:09,76 --> 00:34:10,79
这是什么意思？
What do you mean?

1179
00:34:11,72 --> 00:34:13,99
走！去会会你的新朋友
Let's go and meet your new pal.

1180
00:34:14,16 --> 00:34:15,55
立正！
Attention!

1181
00:34:38,72 --> 00:34:43,66
县长，师爷，大驾光临！有失远迎！
Governor, counselor! Welcome!

1182
00:34:43,88 --> 00:34:46,95
黄老爷的宅邸，竹林掩映，碉楼耸立
Master's citadel dominates Goose Town.

1183
01:15:13,80 --> 01:15:16,43
看清楚了，他们领头的戴几筒？
Which mask is their leader wearing?

1184
01:15:16,64 --> 01:15:17,70
九筒！
"Nine".

1185
01:15:17,96 --> 01:15:19,63
全都换上四筒！
Let's all change to "four"!

1186
01:15:20,96 --> 01:15:23,63
四筒是自己人，其他人全打死
Kill anyone who is not a "four"!

1187
01:15:23,84 --> 01:15:25,79
那边领头的戴的是几筒，看见了吗？
Which mask is their leader wearing?

1188
01:15:25,96 --> 01:15:27,10
四筒
"Four".

1189
01:15:27,32 --> 01:15:28,91
那咱们应该戴几筒，你知道吗？
Know what we'll be wearing, then?

1190
01:15:29,08 --> 01:15:29,99
明白
Got it.

1191
01:09:03,36 --> 01:09:04,75
他骗了人家钱
He swindled someone.

1192
01:09:05,08 --> 01:09:06,06
人家到你那去要帐
His victims tracked you down,

1193
01:10:20,44 --> 01:10:22,63
我们可是先来的
We're here first.

1194
01:10:22,80 --> 01:10:23,67
付钱了吗？
Have they paid?

1195
01:10:23,84 --> 01:10:25,83
自行车能算钱吗？
The "bicycle ride" doesn't count.

1196
01:10:27,12 --> 01:10:27,87
送客！
Show them out.

1197
01:10:28,04 --> 01:10:29,83
上次我给过你很多钱
But I've paid my dues.

1198
01:10:31,52 --> 01:10:32,66
什么钱？
With what?

1199
01:10:33,68 --> 01:10:36,19
窗户外边扔进来的银子？
Money you received through the window?

1200
01:14:24,24 --> 01:14:27,11
要慢，沉住气
you have to stay calm,

1201
01:14:27,32 --> 01:14:29,35
越慢越好
make it nice and slow.

1202
01:14:29,96 --> 01:14:30,99
你亲眼看见的？
You saw it with your own eyes?

1203
01:14:31,16 --> 01:14:32,07
我亲眼看见的！
Indeed.

1204
01:14:32,28 --> 01:14:36,06
你亲眼看见县长亲自带队出发？
You saw the Governor leading his men out?

1205
01:14:36,28 --> 01:14:36,95
我亲眼看见了！
Yes, with my own eyes.

1206
01:14:37,12 --> 01:14:39,31
你亲眼看见县长亲自带队出发去发钱？
They've gone to give out money?

1207
01:15:52,84 --> 01:15:55,07
黄老爷，你怎么在这啊？
Master Huang, what brings you here?

1208
01:15:55,84 --> 01:15:57,79
县衙我不能来吗？
Can I not visit the magistracy?

1209
01:15:59,24 --> 01:16:00,55
点上
Light it!

1210
01:16:00,96 --> 01:16:04,95
你们玩空城计，我就趁虚而入！
When the cat prowls, the mouse seizes control!

1211
01:16:07,08 --> 01:16:08,35
坐
Sit down!

1212
01:16:11,88 --> 01:16:13,35
县长呢？
Where's the Governor?

1213
01:16:18,52 --> 01:16:20,55
都是四筒，下不了手啊！
Everyone is a "Four"? I'm confused!

1214
01:16:20,72 --> 01:16:21,67
下不了手
I'm confused, too!

1215
01:16:21,84 --> 01:16:23,95
打雷天站在雨里头有点不讲究
It's bad to stay out in a thunderstorm.

1216
01:16:24,12 --> 01:16:24,99
太不讲究！
Yes, it's awful.

1217
01:16:25,16 --> 01:16:27,03
那改天再约，撤吧
Let's reschedule. Split!

1218
01:16:27,20 --> 01:16:28,15
撤！
Be in touch!

1219
01:16:28,32 --> 01:16:29,23
怎么撤？
What now?

1220
01:16:29,40 --> 01:16:30,71
从哪儿来，回哪儿去叹
It's back to square one.

1221
01:16:30,88 --> 01:16:32,63
好，从哪儿来，回哪儿去
Yes, square one.

1222
01:16:32,96 --> 01:16:35,26
一二三，撤！
Split! 1, 2, 3.

1223
01:16:46,56 --> 01:16:49,63
听，枪一响，就有人死
Listen! Someone's been shot.

1224
01:16:49,88 --> 01:16:52,63
有人死，就有人哭
Soon someone will mourn.

1225
01:16:53,16 --> 01:16:56,94
人一哭，就要说心里话
Mourning will lead to confessions.

1226
01:16:58,88 --> 01:17:00,15
说吧
Confess!

1227
01:13:47,72 --> 01:13:48,91
糟践东西，不去！
No, what a waste!

1228
01:13:49,08 --> 01:13:50,03
不去是吧 不去
- So you're not coming? - No.

1229
01:13:54,84 --> 01:13:55,63
那我告诉你
Now listen.

1230
01:13:55,80 --> 01:13:57,55
我这次去，可能回得来
This time, I may come back,

1231
01:13:57,72 --> 01:13:58,91
也可能回不来
but, then again, I may not.

1232
01:13:59,08 --> 01:14:01,03
我要是回来，你就跟我跑
If I do, you can leave with us.

1233
01:14:01,24 --> 01:14:03,87
我要是回不来，你就自己跑
If not, you plan your own getaway.

1234
01:14:39,52 --> 01:14:40,55
我亲眼看见了！
Yes, indeed.

1235
01:22:43,80 --> 01:22:45,31
我把人就埋在了那！
The bodies were buried there all along.

1236
01:22:46,84 --> 01:22:49,59
人埋在哪儿，事儿就出在哪儿！
I ensure the standoff was at their burial site.

1237
01:22:50,08 --> 01:22:53,51
事儿出在哪儿，黄四郎就得跟到哪儿！
That's where I led Huang to.

1238
01:22:55,92 --> 01:22:57,99
那你真是张麻子
I'm convinced you're "Pocky" Zhang.

1239
01:22:59,80 --> 01:23:00,91
坐！
Sit down.

1240
01:23:05,68 --> 01:23:06,99
我姓张
My name is Zhang.

1241
01:23:07,20 --> 01:23:08,03
知道
I know that.

1242
01:23:08,20 --> 01:23:09,39
叫牧之
Zhang Muzhi.

1243
01:15:30,16 --> 01:15:32,19
先弄死九筒！走！
Let's get rid of "Nine"!

1244
01:19:14,36 --> 01:19:18,14
你们看到了没有！这是当麻匪的下场！
Take a good look at a bandit's fate!

1245
01:19:18,32 --> 01:19:20,70
就算是我亲爹也得死！
I'd still have him shot

1246
01:19:21,20 --> 01:19:22,51
死有余辜！
if he was my father...

1247
01:19:23,84 --> 01:19:25,03
早晚！
sooner or later!

1248
01:19:29,16 --> 01:19:32,99
麻匪胡万又让黄老爷枪毙了五回
You just shot Hu Wan 5 more times.

1249
01:19:33,16 --> 01:19:34,19
大义灭亲？
You want to show justice?

1250
01:19:34,36 --> 01:19:35,91
杀人灭口？
Or to make sure he's dead?

1251
01:19:36,08 --> 01:19:40,79
杀人灭口，你就是麻匪的头子张麻子
Only "Pocky" Zhang would want to silence him.

1252
01:19:41,80 --> 01:19:44,59
要是大义灭亲，那好办！
If you'd only wanted to show justice,

1253
01:20:47,60 --> 01:20:48,95
接上他的腿
to fund an expedition to fix his broken leg!

1254
01:20:50,84 --> 01:20:52,43
大哥这个是惊喜啊
What a nice surprise!

1255
01:20:52,80 --> 01:20:54,43
小弟我愿意等你三天
I'm willing to wait 3 days.

1256
01:20:58,00 --> 01:20:58,95
黄老爷
Master Huang.

1257
01:20:59,24 --> 01:21:01,80
汤师爷是我的至爱
I adore my Counselor,

1258
01:21:02,28 --> 01:21:05,11
你可不能夺我所爱啊
I can't let you have him.

1259
01:21:06,12 --> 01:21:08,31
了然，了然
Fair enough.

1260
01:21:16,12 --> 01:21:17,23
六子
Six.

1261
01:21:17,84 --> 01:21:20,95
事已经办了九成了
We're almost there.

1262
01:21:22,04 --> 01:21:23,39
算七成吧
Say, 70% done.

1263
01:21:23,76 --> 01:21:25,59
今天我就派你二哥出城
I've asked Two to take off first.

1264
01:21:25,96 --> 01:21:27,79
到青石岭去接应我们
He'll wait for us at Emerald Creek.

1265
01:21:28,20 --> 01:21:31,59
乘l下的事，我会说到做到
I will keep my promise.

1266
01:21:35,56 --> 01:21:36,83
你明白了吧？
Know what you have to do?

1267
01:21:37,32 --> 01:21:38,67
明白
Yes.

1268
01:21:42,16 --> 01:21:43,83
一百八十万两银子到手
When $1.8 million is in hand,

1269
01:21:44,00 --> 01:21:47,23
我觉着小六子的仇算是报了
I'll consider Six avenged.

1270
01:21:48,92 --> 01:21:50,11
我觉着啊！
I feel that...

1271
01:21:51,76 --> 01:21:54,79
不光六子，夫人的仇也算报了
my wife's death is also avenged.

1272
01:21:59,00 --> 01:22:02,15
你不会真跟黄四郎玩命吧，恩人呐
Saviour, you still want to kill Huang?

1273
01:22:02,32 --> 01:22:04,51
我不是你恩人，黄四郎才是你恩人
I'm not your saviour. Huang is.

1274
01:22:06,80 --> 01:22:09,31
你是恩人，他不是！
You're my saviour. Not him.

1275
01:22:09,84 --> 01:22:11,87
你当时真的以为我死了？
Did you think I was lying dead back there?

1276
01:22:12,04 --> 01:22:13,99
没有！绝对没有
No, of course not.

1277
01:22:14,16 --> 01:22:14,67
没有？
Sure?

1278
01:22:14,84 --> 01:22:16,39
从没这么想过！
Never crossed my mind.

1279
01:22:21,52 --> 01:22:22,99
我可真算服了你了
I've to hand this to you.

1280
01:14:04,04 --> 01:14:05,91
去…去哪啊？不是发钱吗？
Aren't you just giving out money?

1281
01:14:06,08 --> 01:14:06,99
是发钱
Yes, we are.

1282
01:14:07,16 --> 01:14:08,35
还有…
By the way,

1283
01:14:11,84 --> 01:14:13,11
半夜的时候
at midnight tonight,

1284
01:14:13,76 --> 01:14:15,63
可能有人来找你
someone may come calling.

1285
01:14:15,80 --> 01:14:17,35
他要找你聊什么
Engage him in conversation.

1286
01:14:17,60 --> 01:14:19,15
你就跟他聊什么
Whatever the topics,

1287
01:14:19,60 --> 01:14:22,27
他怎么聊，你就怎么聊
just chat along with him.

1288
01:14:22,72 --> 01:14:24,03
但是…
But...

1289
01:17:01,00 --> 01:17:04,03
你至少有三句要说
You've at least three confessions to make.

1290
01:17:04,96 --> 01:17:06,99
我不该拿你的钻石送人
I shouldn't have given your diamonds away.

1291
01:17:14,56 --> 01:17:16,11
不是这句
Try again.

1292
01:17:17,04 --> 01:17:18,91
杀人诛心是我说的
I suggested "to kill someone, first destroy his soul".

1293
01:17:19,32 --> 01:17:21,43
也不是这句
Not that either.

1294
01:17:26,20 --> 01:17:28,71
鸿门宴要是我们请就好了
We should have hosted the banquet instead.

1295
01:17:29,44 --> 01:17:30,99
鸿门宴？
The banquet?

1296
01:19:56,96 --> 01:19:59,03
现在又成了你的恩人
Now he's your boss, too.

1297
01:19:59,60 --> 01:20:00,71
你给翻译翻译
Please act as our interpreter.

1298
01:20:01,44 --> 01:20:02,87
什么叫惊喜？
What is a "nice surprise"?

1299
01:20:03,40 --> 01:20:05,75
翻译翻译，什么叫惊喜？
Interpret for me.

1300
01:20:05,92 --> 01:20:06,98
这还用翻译？都说了…
There's nothing to interpret

1301
01:20:07,16 --> 01:20:10,51
我让你翻译给我听，什么叫惊喜
What on earth is a "nice surprise"?

1302
01:20:10,68 --> 01:20:11,87
不用翻译，就是惊京喜啊
It is what it is.

1303
01:20:12,04 --> 01:20:13,26
难道你听不懂什么叫惊喜
You just don't get it, do you?

1304
01:20:13,44 --> 01:20:16,15
我就想让你翻译翻译，什么叫惊喜！
Go ahead and interpret. What is it?

1305
01:20:16,32 --> 01:20:16,91
1京喜嘛…
A nice surprise!

1306
01:20:17,08 --> 01:20:18,06
翻译出来给我听
Translate for me!

1307
01:20:18,24 --> 01:20:20,95
什么他妈的叫惊喜！
What is this "nice surprise"?

1308
01:20:21,12 --> 01:20:25,07
什么他妈的叫他妈的惊喜！
What is this goddamned "nice surprise"?

1309
01:20:25,24 --> 01:20:27,15
什么他妈的叫惊喜啊？
What is this "nice surprise"?

1310
01:20:27,32 --> 01:20:28,71
惊喜就是三天之后
It means that in 3 days,

1311
01:20:28,88 --> 01:20:31,79
我出一百八十万，给你们出城剿匪
I'll put up $1.8 million for your campaign,

1312
01:20:31,96 --> 01:20:33,18
接上我的腿！
to fix my crippled leg!

1313
01:20:33,36 --> 01:20:34,55
明白了吗？
Is that clear?

1314
01:20:34,72 --> 01:20:36,15
这就是惊喜呀
That's the "nice surprise"!

1315
01:20:36,32 --> 01:20:38,19
翻译翻译
Interpret.

1316
01:20:41,52 --> 01:20:42,03
翻译翻译！
Interpret.

1317
01:20:42,20 --> 01:20:44,07
惊喜就是三天之后
The nice surprise is that,

1318
01:20:44,24 --> 01:20:47,39
给你一百八十万两银子，出城剿匪
he will give you $1.8 million in 3 days,

1319
01:18:03,72 --> 01:18:05,83
您才是我的恩人
No, you are my saviour.

1320
01:18:08,40 --> 01:18:09,83
既然我是你的恩人
If that is the case,

1321
01:18:10,00 --> 01:18:11,63
那就听恩人的话，揭开看看
remove his mask,

1322
01:18:11,80 --> 01:18:12,63
去吧，看看！
and have a good look.

1323
01:18:12,80 --> 01:18:14,91
来！照上照上！
Come on, lights!

1324
01:18:21,00 --> 01:18:22,35
什么情况？
What's going on?

1325
01:18:22,56 --> 01:18:24,55
什么情况？什么情况？
What's happening here?

1326
01:18:27,96 --> 01:18:29,02
胡万！
It's Hu Wan!

1327
01:18:29,32 --> 01:18:30,51
胡…胡万？
Hu Wan?

1328
01:18:30,68 --> 01:18:32,11
怎么会是胡万？
How come it's Hu Wan?

1329
01:18:32,72 --> 01:18:34,23
怪了
This is weird!

1330
01:18:35,72 --> 01:18:36,11
四筒啊
All those wearing "four"

1331
01:18:36,28 --> 01:18:37,34
全是黄家的人！
are my men!

1332
01:18:37,56 --> 01:18:39,55
麻匪呢？
Where are the bandits?

1333
01:18:39,72 --> 01:18:42,55
胡万，就是麻匪！
Where are they?

1334
01:18:39,72 --> 01:18:42,55
Hu Wan was a bandit!


1335
01:18:42,72 --> 01:18:45,02
麻匪，就是胡万！
He was one of them!

1336
01:18:45,56 --> 01:18:48,91
杀县长夫人，绑架豪绅
Murderers and kidnappers,

1337
01:18:49,08 --> 01:18:51,15
祸害鹅城百姓
those who terrorised Goose Town,

1338
01:18:51,32 --> 01:18:54,83
就是你黄老爷家的胡万！
were led by your own Hu Wan!

1339
01:18:55,20 --> 01:18:57,83
我说你为什么不出钱剿匪？
I wondered why you didn't fund the expedition.

1340
01:18:58,00 --> 01:19:01,31
原来你是贼喊捉贼啊！
You may even be the bandit chief himself!

1341
01:19:02,76 --> 01:19:04,19
你拿枪指着我？
You dare to turn your guns on me?

1342
01:19:05,00 --> 01:19:06,51
你拿枪指着我？!
You dare to turn your guns on me?

1343
01:19:07,92 --> 01:19:09,91
你想跟我火拼？
Do you want a shoot-out?

1344
01:27:17,76 --> 01:27:18,39
因为你是好人
Because you're a good person.

1345
01:23:40,00 --> 01:23:41,27
我回来了
I came back alone.

1346
01:23:41,96 --> 01:23:47,23
碰上军阀混战，天下大乱
The country was in total chaos.

1347
01:23:47,92 --> 01:23:51,62
我只得浪迹江湖，落草为寇
So I became a bandit.

1348
01:23:51,84 --> 01:23:55,19
牧之也被叫成了麻子
They nicknamed me "Pocky".

1349
01:23:56,12 --> 01:24:00,43
可惜啊！多好的一个牧字
Shame! You're so handsome.

1350
01:24:00,64 --> 01:24:02,55
人们不愿意相信
People have an odd way of thinking,

1351
01:24:02,92 --> 01:24:06,03
一个土匪的名字叫牧之
that bandits shouldn't have proper names.

1352
01:24:06,36 --> 01:24:08,71
人们更愿意相信他叫麻子
They love calling their bandits "Pocky".

1353
01:24:08,88 --> 01:24:10,79
人们特别愿意相信
Not only that,

1354
01:24:11,56 --> 01:24:15,34
他的脸上应该长着麻子
they want their bandits scarred and scary.

1355
01:24:17,88 --> 01:24:19,67
这人可真够驴蛋的
People can be so ignorant.

1356
01:24:20,88 --> 01:24:24,71
我的故事…却是这样…
My own story started like this...

1357
01:24:25,40 --> 01:24:29,71
那年我也十七岁
I too was a tenderly 17,

1358
01:24:30,16 --> 01:24:32,91
她也十七岁
and so was she.

1359
01:24:33,16 --> 01:24:35,87
停！我不愿意听你的故事
Stop, I'm not interested.

1360
01:24:36,00 --> 01:24:39,99
我一般不跟人说心里话
I don't confess to just anyone.

1361
01:24:40,28 --> 01:24:42,23
这都到嘴边了，你不能让我咽回去吧
I've to continue now that I started.

1362
01:24:42,40 --> 01:24:43,62
咽回去吧
Take it back!

1363
01:24:43,80 --> 01:24:45,83
因为你说出来也是假的
It's all made up anyway.

1364
01:24:46,32 --> 01:24:47,75
你是个骗子
You're a conman!

1365
01:24:52,52 --> 01:24:54,59
北国我不知道
In our part of China,

1366
01:24:56,28 --> 01:25:00,99
在我南国，这样的珍藏版地雷
There are only two such landmines.

1367
01:25:01,56 --> 01:25:02,91
只有两颗
Both limited edition.

1368
01:26:23,12 --> 01:26:24,75
了然，我是假麻子！
No problem, sir. I'm a fake.

1369
01:26:24,92 --> 01:26:27,07
老爷给我多少那是对我的恩赐
I'll take whatever you can spare.

1370
01:26:27,40 --> 01:26:29,23
那么，什么时候炸？
When do you want it to blow up?

1371
01:26:29,40 --> 01:26:31,63
什么时候炸那是第三步
That's our denouement!

1372
01:26:31,96 --> 01:26:35,11
且让我把第二步慢慢走好
Let's play out our second act slowly.

1373
01:26:35,44 --> 01:26:36,55
都别动！
Hold still!

1374
01:26:37,20 --> 01:26:38,26
让她说！
Let her speak.

1375
01:26:38,92 --> 01:26:40,71
老二不辞而别
Two left without saying goodbye.

1376
01:19:44,76 --> 01:19:46,59
你出钱，我剿匪！
why not fund my expedition instead.

1377
01:19:46,80 --> 01:19:47,83
好啊！
Done deal!

1378
01:19:48,60 --> 01:19:53,59
三天之后，一定给县长一个惊喜
You shall receive a nice surprise in 3 days.

1379
01:19:53,76 --> 01:19:56,67
汤师爷，他是胡万的恩人
He was Hu Wan's boss.

1380
01:22:40,20 --> 01:22:43,39
我为什么要把人埋在衙门里
They weren't buried at the magistracy.

1381
01:25:13,08 --> 01:25:17,27
美国制造，一九一零
Made in U.S.A. - 1910!

1382
01:25:18,88 --> 01:25:22,99
呼！一响，它就没了
Bang and everything's in smithereens!

1383
01:25:24,68 --> 01:25:28,67
所以，不带走几条人命
So if it doesn't take some lives with it,

1384
01:25:29,44 --> 01:25:33,35
那就是卑鄙的浪费！
it'd be such a waste.

1385
01:25:33,88 --> 01:25:35,02
那么…
Well...

1386
01:25:35,92 --> 01:25:37,63
另外一颗地雷呢？
where's the other one?

1387
01:25:37,80 --> 01:25:38,51
炸了！
It exploded.

1388
01:25:38,68 --> 01:25:39,23
炸了？
Really?

1389
01:25:39,40 --> 01:25:41,59
辛亥革命的第一响
The first bang during the 1911 Revolution!

1390
01:25:41,76 --> 01:25:43,31
我知道了
Oh yes, I've heard!

1391
01:25:43,52 --> 01:25:45,19
炸在辛亥这个地方了
It went off at Xinhai!

1392
01:25:47,60 --> 01:25:50,75
辛亥不是个地方，是一种革命
Xinhai's not a place! It's a revolutionary icon!

1393
01:25:50,92 --> 01:25:52,71
您要早这么说我就了然了
You should've said so earlier.

1394
01:25:52,88 --> 01:25:54,75
那还是说说这颗吧
Now, tell me about this one.

1395
01:25:54,96 --> 01:25:56,51
谁让你问那颗的？
You must stay focused.

1396
01:25:56,80 --> 01:25:59,31
所以，它要炸得惊天
I want it to shake the world,

1397
01:27:18,60 --> 01:27:19,79
什么？
What?

1398
01:27:20,24 --> 01:27:22,07
这是什么狗屁道理？
What kind of stupid logic is that?

1399
01:27:22,24 --> 01:27:23,99
好人就得让人拿枪指着？
You threaten me because I'm good?

1400
01:27:25,28 --> 01:27:27,19
花姐，大哥说得对！
Flora, Chief is right!

1401
01:27:27,56 --> 01:27:28,95
回来！坐下！
Go back! Sit down!

1402
01:27:29,56 --> 01:27:30,67
你们这群王八蛋
You bunch of idiots!

1403
01:27:30,88 --> 01:27:32,95
我让你们把钱发给穷人
I told you to give money to the poor.

1404
01:27:33,12 --> 01:27:34,03
你们发给一个女人？
And you gave it to her?

1405
01:27:34,16 --> 01:27:36,62
我说什么来着？没人听啊！
I warned you but nobody listened.

1406
01:27:36,80 --> 01:27:38,55
闭嘴！天生的老骗子！
Shut up! You're a born cheat!

1407
01:27:38,72 --> 01:27:40,15
时时刻刻想骗我！
Always plotting to swindle me.

1408
01:27:40,32 --> 01:27:42,15
跟黄四郎勾勾搭搭！
Working with Huang behind my back.

1409
01:27:42,32 --> 01:27:44,39
一个土匪碰见一个恶霸
When a bandit confronts a godfather,

1410
01:27:44,60 --> 01:27:45,79
多么简单的事！
the outcome should be simple.

1411
01:27:45,96 --> 01:27:47,91
让你们给弄成这么烂七八糟的
How can you screw up so badly?

1412
01:22:23,16 --> 01:22:26,07
狸猫变太子，嘎登变出一胡万来
Abracadabra, and Hu Wan magically appeared!

1413
01:22:26,76 --> 01:22:28,67
可是我有一事不明
But I really didn't get it.

1414
01:22:29,52 --> 01:22:30,55
六具尸体
Those six bodies,

1415
01:22:30,76 --> 01:22:32,35
这么长的距离，那么短的时间
such a distance, so little time,

1416
01:22:32,56 --> 01:22:34,71
还抹着红脸蛋，你们是怎么搬来的？
how did you move them so quickly?

1417
01:22:34,88 --> 01:22:37,03
我跟黄四郎可是一路小跑过来的
Huang and I took the shortcut.

1418
01:22:37,20 --> 01:22:38,23
你们搬着六个人
You've to carry six bodies.

1419
01:22:38,40 --> 01:22:39,87
来不及呀！
How did you manage?

1420
01:23:09,60 --> 01:23:11,11
好名字！
A fine name!

1421
01:23:11,28 --> 01:23:13,51
充州牧，豫州牧
It has auspicious meanings.

1422
01:23:13,80 --> 01:23:18,07
牧之，令尊是望子成大器
You father must have high hopes.

1423
01:23:18,60 --> 01:23:20,11
从讲武堂出来
After graduating from military academy,

1424
01:23:20,92 --> 01:23:23,91
我追随过松坡将军
I enlisted in General Cai's army.

1425
01:23:24,36 --> 01:23:26,39
给他做过手枪队长
Served as captain of his riflemen.

1426
01:23:26,76 --> 01:23:28,07
那年你多大？
How old were you then?

1427
01:23:28,24 --> 01:23:29,51
十七
Seventeen.

1428
01:23:29,80 --> 01:23:31,71
少年得志啊
A youthful genius!

1429
01:23:32,36 --> 01:23:36,11
后来庐州会战，将军负了伤
Cai was wounded during the Battle of Luzhou,

1430
01:23:36,88 --> 01:23:39,79
再后来，将军死在了日本
and later died in exile in Japan.

1431
01:27:50,04 --> 01:27:51,51
不敢拿枪，当不了麻匪
If I don't dare to draw a gun on you,

1432
01:27:51,68 --> 01:27:53,35
我敢拿枪指着你
I'll never make a good bandit.

1433
01:27:54,12 --> 01:27:55,18
我胆儿大吧
I dare you all!

1434
01:27:59,00 --> 01:28:00,79
你们谁给她出的这个主意？
Whose quirky idea is this?

1435
01:28:01,24 --> 01:28:02,35
谁？
Whose?

1436
01:28:03,28 --> 01:28:04,91
我就是跟她说着玩的
I was just teasing her.

1437
01:28:10,52 --> 01:28:11,95
你是想当麻匪？
You want to become one of us?

1438
01:28:12,12 --> 01:28:14,99
对呀！我想跟你们一块儿发钱
Yes, to give money out to the poor,

1439
01:28:15,16 --> 01:28:18,07
把钱袋子扔到窗户里，听他们笑
to hear and share their joy.

1440
01:28:20,56 --> 01:28:21,39
你现在就是了
You're now one of us.

1441
01:28:21,60 --> 01:28:22,74
我还没准备好呢
But I am not prepared.

1442
01:28:22,96 --> 01:28:23,99
不用准备
No need!

1443
01:28:24,16 --> 01:28:25,35
你们都准备过吗？
Did you make preparation?

1444
01:28:25,56 --> 01:28:26,39
没有
No.

1445
01:28:26,60 --> 01:28:27,19
你准备过吗？
How about you?

1446
01:28:27,36 --> 01:28:29,51
没有啊，我吃着火锅唱着歌
I was eating hotpot and singing songs.

1447
01:28:29,68 --> 01:28:32,35
扑通一下掉水里，出来就到这儿了
My train plunged and I ended up here.

1448
01:28:35,92 --> 01:28:37,59
我们要离开鹅城
We're leaving Goose Town soon.

1449
01:28:37,96 --> 01:28:38,75
你就留在鹅城
But you have to stay.

1450
01:28:38,92 --> 01:28:39,83
不！
No.

1451
01:28:40,68 --> 01:28:42,35
当麻匪要听命令
A bandit must have discipline.

1452
01:28:42,56 --> 01:28:43,95
大哥说得对
Chief is right.

1453
01:28:45,40 --> 01:28:46,87
刚才说的也对
But she has a point, too.

1454
01:28:53,04 --> 01:28:55,31
我有个很重要的事交给你
I have an important mission for you.

1455
01:28:56,04 --> 01:28:57,83
我看你挺合适
I think you can manage.

1456
01:28:58,84 --> 01:29:00,35
这就是惊喜！
This is our nice surprise!

1457
01:29:01,32 --> 01:29:02,91
果然是个惊京喜
A nice surprise indeed.

1458
01:29:03,80 --> 01:29:05,15
果然他不姓马！
He is not Ma!

1459
01:29:09,28 --> 01:29:10,75
有了这个惊喜
Now that we know,

1460
01:29:13,00 --> 01:29:17,23
我的第二步就能走的更加悠然
My next move can be more leisurely.

1461
01:29:17,40 --> 01:29:18,79
悠然？
Leisurely?

1462
01:29:19,84 --> 01:29:22,27
盗官欺爵，放在前清
Impersonating a governor warrants capital punishment.

1463
01:25:59,52 --> 01:26:02,95
还要动地，还要泣鬼神
I want it to rock and roll!

1464
01:26:03,16 --> 01:26:03,87
了然
Understood.

1465
01:26:04,04 --> 01:26:05,23
选个好地方
Pick a good spot,

1466
01:26:05,96 --> 01:26:07,31
选个好时辰
find an auspicious time...

1467
01:26:07,52 --> 01:26:09,31
那么…炸谁？
So, who's our target?

1468
01:26:09,52 --> 01:26:10,74
你应该问…
You should've asked...

1469
01:26:10,92 --> 01:26:11,67
炸在哪
"Where"?

1470
01:26:11,84 --> 01:26:13,15
炸在哪？
Where, then?

1471
01:26:13,84 --> 01:26:15,27
剿匪的路上
Where the expedition force must pass.

1472
01:26:15,64 --> 01:26:17,94
这么快又要剿匪了？
Yet another expedition?

1473
01:26:18,20 --> 01:26:19,79
那这回我能多分点吧
Can I have a bigger cut this time?

1474
01:26:20,00 --> 01:26:22,95
你要是真的张麻子，钱都给你
You can have it all if you're the real Pocky!

1475
01:27:07,44 --> 01:27:09,74
你是被黄四郎买来的
You were bought by Huang?

1476
01:27:09,92 --> 01:27:10,51
对
Yes.

1477
01:27:10,68 --> 01:27:11,82
他打过你吗？ 打过
- Been mistreated? - Yes.

1478
01:27:12,04 --> 01:27:13,15
我打过你么？ 没有
- Have I ever laid hands on you? - No.

1479
01:27:13,32 --> 01:27:14,38
你恨他吗？ 恨
- Hate him? - Yes.

1480
01:27:14,60 --> 01:27:15,39
恨我吗？ 不恨
- And me? - No.

1481
01:27:15,60 --> 01:27:17,59
那你不拿枪指着他！你拿枪指着我？
Then why threaten me with a gun?

1482
01:38:18,12 --> 01:38:23,91
“大哥有令，散开，别开枪”
"Hold your fire. Scatter!"

1483
01:38:24,08 --> 01:38:30,83
“往山顶上跑，抓住他们的头儿”
"Run for the peak. Grab their leader."

1484
01:38:36,72 --> 01:38:37,63
西边十个
10 to the west.

1485
01:38:38,16 --> 01:38:39,22
南面六个
6 to the south.

1486
01:29:30,36 --> 01:29:32,95
我还要好好地耍耍这两只猴！
I want to toy with these circus monkeys.

1487
01:29:33,16 --> 01:29:34,27
我的老爷
But Master,

1488
01:29:34,68 --> 01:29:36,59
这两只猴子不值得您耍！
they're not worth your while.

1489
01:29:36,76 --> 01:29:39,27
要耍！一定要耍！
No, I must toy with them!

1490
01:29:39,72 --> 01:29:42,95
不耍猴，我怎么赚到两大家族的钱？
Otherwise, I couldn't get others to pay,

1491
01:29:43,12 --> 01:29:47,15
不耍猴，他们怎么心甘情愿地去剿匪？
the Governor couldn't go and fight the bandits,

1492
01:29:47,40 --> 01:29:51,71
不剿匪，他们怎么能踩到地雷呢？
and they wouldn't trot on my landmine!

1493
01:29:52,08 --> 01:29:53,30
黄四郎有个替身
Huang has a double.

1494
01:29:53,52 --> 01:29:54,83
跟他长得一模一样
They are indistinguishable.

1495
01:29:55,00 --> 01:29:59,07
我弄不清楚他是黄四郎，还是他替身
I can't tell if this is really Huang.

1496
01:29:59,76 --> 01:30:00,82
你帮我去看看
I need you to check for me.

1497
01:30:05,08 --> 01:30:06,06
假的！
He's a fake.

1498
01:30:06,76 --> 01:30:08,07
他不是黄四郎
He's not Huang.

1499
01:30:08,24 --> 01:30:10,27
我已经跟你们说过我不是他
Told you I'm not Huang!

1500
01:30:10,44 --> 01:30:12,39
我真的不是他
I really am not him.

1501
01:30:12,40 --> 01:30:13,23
肯定不是
I'm certain.

1502
01:30:13,40 --> 01:30:14,87
放了我吧，放了我
Let me go.

1503
01:30:15,04 --> 01:30:17,11
那好，你帮我们看住他
Keep an eye on him until our return.

1504
01:30:17,28 --> 01:30:19,91
等我们回来，就用你手里的枪
If you have to, use your guns.

1505
01:31:46,92 --> 01:31:49,83
黄老爷见笑，马某走南闯北
I've travelled all over China,

1506
01:31:50,00 --> 01:31:52,07
在九个地方做过县长
I have been governor in 9 counties.

1507
01:31:52,24 --> 01:31:56,27
靠的就是以假乱真、鱼目混珠之章法
I excel in confusing facts with fiction!

1508
01:31:56,52 --> 01:31:58,15
那么…马县长…
So, Governor Ma...

1509
01:31:58,32 --> 01:31:59,23
你说
Yes?

1510
01:31:59,96 --> 01:32:01,31
叫我呐！
He's addressing me.

1511
01:32:02,04 --> 01:32:03,02
黄老爷继续
You were saying?

1512
01:32:03,20 --> 01:32:05,19
我刚摸清你们的底细
Just as I uncover the truth,

1513
01:32:05,84 --> 01:32:07,71
你们就不打自招
you blow your own cover!

1514
01:32:08,04 --> 01:32:08,63
太巧了吧？
What a coincidence.

1515
01:32:08,80 --> 01:32:13,11
有道是，展颜消宿怨
"Stop frowning to dispel ill feelings,

1516
01:32:13,28 --> 01:32:15,15
一笑泯恩仇啊
and brush aside quarrels with a smile."

1517
01:32:15,32 --> 01:32:16,79
你想跟我和解？
Want to make peace?

1518
01:32:17,40 --> 01:32:19,11
好啊！我的替身呢？
Splendid. Where's my double?

1519
01:32:19,84 --> 01:32:22,27
还给我，前面的账一笔勾销
Return him and we'll call it quits.

1520
01:32:22,44 --> 01:32:23,63
撕票了
We've killed him.

1521
01:32:24,40 --> 01:32:26,43
哪个王八蛋让你撕票的？
Which asshole ordered his execution?

1522
01:32:26,64 --> 01:32:28,39
你个王八蛋让我撕票的！
You're that asshole!

1523
01:32:31,08 --> 01:32:32,91
开枪，你开枪我也能先打死你
I dare you to pull your trigger!

1524
01:32:33,80 --> 01:32:34,55
放下！
Lay down your guns!

1525
01:32:34,96 --> 01:32:37,15
开枪！你先开枪，我也能先打死你
I know I could take you out first.

1526
01:32:38,40 --> 01:32:41,19
把枪放下！我数三下
Put down your guns on my count of three!

1527
01:32:41,36 --> 01:32:44,07
一！二！三！
One, two, three!

1528
01:32:45,96 --> 01:32:47,27
老黄，你先放下
Huang, put it down!

1529
01:32:47,52 --> 01:32:49,15
他不懂事儿，你也不懂事啊？
He may be a brute, but you too?

1530
01:26:41,64 --> 01:26:43,23
老三又要走了
Now Three is leaving too.

1531
01:26:43,44 --> 01:26:45,27
我们活活的被你们拆散了！
You are tearing us apart!

1532
01:26:46,72 --> 01:26:49,31
女侠，你是为了老二还是为老三啊？
You're doing this for Two or Three?

1533
01:26:49,52 --> 01:26:50,87
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1534
01:26:52,12 --> 01:26:53,43
你左手的意思我懂
I know your left hand's intention,

1535
01:26:53,64 --> 01:26:54,83
右手的意思我也懂
I know your right hand's intention.

1536
01:26:55,00 --> 01:26:56,91
两只手这么待着，我看不懂
But both hands together...I don't get it.

1537
01:26:57,08 --> 01:26:58,79
要么成，要么死
I'd rather be dead!

1538
01:26:58,96 --> 01:26:59,75
AB型！
Typical Scorpian!

1539
01:27:00,32 --> 01:27:01,35
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1540
01:27:02,52 --> 01:27:03,58
你们都坐下
Sit down, all of you.

1541
01:27:04,12 --> 01:27:05,43
我再跟她聊聊
Let me talk to her.

1542
01:27:48,08 --> 01:27:49,75
你还敢拿枪指着我？
How dare you still point your gun at me?

1543
01:29:22,44 --> 01:29:24,15
满门抄斩
His whole clan dies with him!

1544
01:29:24,32 --> 01:29:25,87
老爷，你等着
Master, just you wait.

1545
01:29:26,52 --> 01:29:27,74
我这就一枪崩了他！
I'll go and blow him away!

1546
01:29:27,92 --> 01:29:28,98
不！
No!

1547
01:29:29,16 --> 01:29:30,19
他们死以前
Before they die,

1548
01:40:37,08 --> 01:40:38,19
死了吧？
Is he dead?

1549
01:40:45,00 --> 01:40:47,19
我弄死你妈的呀！
Goddamned it!

1550
01:32:58,72 --> 01:33:00,11
出不了城，剿不了匪
We can't fight without leaving!

1551
01:33:00,60 --> 01:33:02,83
黄老爷，您说话不算数啊！
You've failed to live up to your promise.

1552
01:33:03,00 --> 01:33:04,35
鸿门宴上说得好
You had agreed to

1553
01:33:04,56 --> 01:33:05,70
你带头出钱
Iead the contribution

1554
01:33:05,88 --> 01:33:07,75
再套出两大家族的钱来
in order to make the others pay.

1555
01:33:07,92 --> 01:33:09,55
可是你不但不出钱
Not only have you not put up any money,

1556
01:33:09,72 --> 01:33:12,95
