Wrong! You saw my men dressed up as bandits.

1558
01:33:17,00 --> 01:33:18,87
我看见的麻匪，是你们扮的
I saw yours posing as bandits, too.

1559
01:33:19,08 --> 01:33:20,51
可是他们看见的麻匪
But when the others see these bandits,

1560
01:33:20,68 --> 01:33:22,43
他们以为是真的！
they wouldn't know that they're fakes.

1561
01:33:22,68 --> 01:33:25,91
现在正是让他们出钱剿匪的好时机！
Now is the time to pay for the expedition.

1562
01:33:26,08 --> 01:33:28,43
只要我出钱，他们一定会出
If I pay, others will follow suit.

1563
01:33:28,64 --> 01:33:30,07
你的钱呢？
Where's your money?

1564
01:33:38,80 --> 01:33:40,83
早已经为你准备好了
It's all here.

1565
01:33:41,32 --> 01:33:43,03
鹅城到处都是我的钱
I've money stowed away everywhere!

1566
01:33:43,36 --> 01:33:44,58
都在这儿？
It's all here?

1567
01:33:44,76 --> 01:33:46,19
这只是一半
This is only half of my share.

1568
01:33:46,44 --> 01:33:50,43
我们想赚多少，他们必须出多少
Each family will have to put up the same.

1569
01:33:50,64 --> 01:33:51,86
三舅，有诈！
Uncle, this is a trap.

1570
01:33:52,80 --> 01:33:53,78
诈？
A trap?

1571
01:33:55,16 --> 01:33:56,91
来回这么多趟，死了这么多人
After all these confrontations,

1572
01:33:57,08 --> 01:33:57,91
他一分钱都不出
he has not put up a dime.

1573
01:33:58,08 --> 01:33:59,99
今天怎么突然出了这么多钱？
Why so generous all of a sudden?

1574
01:34:00,16 --> 01:34:01,19
你觉得突然？
Did I surprise you?

1575
01:34:02,04 --> 01:34:02,63
太突然了
Yes, you did.

1576
01:34:02,80 --> 01:34:04,02
我也觉得突然
I surprised myself too!

1577
01:34:04,32 --> 01:34:05,27
想知道吗？
Want to know why?

1578
01:34:05,76 --> 01:34:06,82
过来
Come here.

1579
01:34:09,00 --> 01:34:10,79
我要当…
I - want - to - be -

1580
01:34:11,16 --> 01:34:11,79
县长
Governor!

1581
01:34:11,96 --> 01:34:13,02
你？
You?

1582
01:34:13,16 --> 01:34:14,67
我做不了县长？
I won't make a Governor?

1583
01:34:15,60 --> 01:34:16,79
我不像个县长？
Don't I look the part?

1584
01:34:16,96 --> 01:34:19,55
像！我们一走，你就上任鹅城
Yes, you can swear in as soon as we leave.

1585
01:34:19,72 --> 01:34:21,15
鹅城？
Goose Town?

1586
01:34:22,32 --> 01:34:24,11
我买了六个县的县长！
I bought governorship of 6 more counties!

1587
01:34:24,28 --> 01:34:26,51
我一个人当不过来
I can't handle all on my own!

1588
01:34:27,04 --> 01:34:28,15
所以…
That is why...

1589
01:34:28,36 --> 01:34:29,42
出去
Get out!

1590
01:34:29,96 --> 01:34:31,31
退下
Leave us.

1591
01:34:32,40 --> 01:34:35,23
老马，你来帮我当三个县的县长
I need you to govern three of them for me.

1592
01:34:35,40 --> 01:34:37,67
好啊！这事我拿手
Brilliant! I'm good at governing.

1593
01:34:37,88 --> 01:34:38,99
等会！
Hey, wait...

1594
01:34:39,16 --> 01:34:41,19
那…那我干什么呀？
What about me, then?

1595
01:34:41,36 --> 01:34:42,55
你嘛…
You...

1596
01:34:43,60 --> 01:34:45,63
来当一个假的张麻子！
can play "Pocky" Zhang!

1597
01:34:47,72 --> 01:34:48,91
好啊
Great idea!

1598
01:35:23,96 --> 01:35:25,83
自宣统皇帝退位以后
Since the abdication of the last Emperor,

1599
01:35:26,84 --> 01:35:29,11
鹅城一共来过51任县长
Goose Town has 51 governors.

1600
