But our beloved Governor Ma,

1602
01:35:37,04 --> 01:35:39,07
他不是王八蛋，不是畜生
is neither a bastard, parasite,

1603
01:35:39,24 --> 01:35:41,70
不是禽兽，也不是寄生虫
Ieech, nor a beast!

1604
