Yes,

1614
01:30:48,00 --> 01:30:50,27
那时候我还很瘦
I was slimmer then.

1615
01:30:50,76 --> 01:30:52,07
这就不是你
I don't think it's you.

1616
01:30:52,36 --> 01:30:53,55
你说他不是我？
It isn't?

1617
01:30:53,80 --> 01:30:54,59
不是！
No, it isn't.

1618
01:30:54,76 --> 01:30:56,23
我说他也不是我！
I don't think so either.

1619
01:30:56,40 --> 01:30:58,63
这根本就不是我！
No, that ain't me.

1620
01:30:59,84 --> 01:31:01,03
那到底是怎么回事？
What is this all about?

1621
01:31:01,20 --> 01:31:03,15
我还想知道是怎么回事
I was totally baffled myself.

1622
01:31:03,68 --> 01:31:07,27
花钱买了个县官，我总得有个证件吧
When I bought the post, I needed papers.

1623
01:31:07,96 --> 01:31:10,87
我去照相馆照相，取照片的时候
I had my picture taken at a gallery,

1624
01:31:11,20 --> 01:31:12,55
他们给我的就是这张
and that's what they gave me.

1625
01:31:12,72 --> 01:31:14,91
我说这不是我，他们说这就是你
I said the man in the photo wasn't me.

1626
01:31:15,24 --> 01:31:18,75
我说他不是我！他们说这就是你
They insisted that it was.

1627
01:31:19,12 --> 01:31:20,83
没办法，我就把它贴在这了
I've no choice but to use it.

1628
01:31:21,32 --> 01:31:22,51
哦！是这样！
Is that so?

1629
01:31:22,80 --> 01:31:24,27
哦什么呀？
Bullshit!

1630
01:31:24,68 --> 01:31:26,51
这明明是我！
That's obviously me!

1631
01:31:27,12 --> 01:31:28,71
我才是马邦德！
I am the real Ma Bangde.

1632
01:31:29,20 --> 01:31:31,19
哦！是这样
Is that so?

1633
01:31:31,32 --> 01:31:34,94
是这样！我进城以前遇见麻匪
I was ambushed by bandits on my way here.

1634
01:31:35,52 --> 01:31:37,67
幸亏有他，才躲过一劫
He saved my life.

1635
01:31:37,84 --> 01:31:40,63
我一想，索性让他假扮县长
So I let him take the post.

1636
01:31:40,80 --> 01:31:43,39
毕竟是自家外甥嘛
After all, he's my nephew.

1637
01:31:43,60 --> 01:31:44,95
三舅，这话能跟他说吗？
Uncle, we shouldn't be telling him this.

1638
01:31:45,12 --> 01:31:46,18
闭嘴！
Shut up!

1639
01:36:12,44 --> 01:36:15,91
出了城，吃着火锅，还唱着歌
singing, eating hot pot and be merry,

1640
01:36:16,08 --> 01:36:19,27
突然就被麻匪劫了！
when bandits jump on you from nowhere!

1641
01:36:20,04 --> 01:36:22,27
所以，没有麻匪的日子
I long for a world without thieves,

1642
01:36:22,68 --> 01:36:24,55
才是好日子！
for days of wine and roses!

1643
01:36:25,88 --> 01:36:26,99
县长，请！
Governor, please!

1644
01:36:29,16 --> 01:36:31,35
出发！
March!

1645
01:36:46,20 --> 01:36:46,99
恩人
Saviour,

1646
01:36:47,28 --> 01:36:48,67
给你看个宝贝
want to check this out?

1647
01:36:50,16 --> 01:36:51,19
这不就是委任状嘛
Isn't that the warrant?

1648
01:36:51,32 --> 01:36:52,67
念念，念念
Read it out loud.

1649
01:36:54,20 --> 01:36:56,79
兹委任马邦德…怎么了？
Ma Bangde is hereby appointed...

1650
01:36:56,96 --> 01:36:57,83
后面！
Read on!

1651
01:36:58,00 --> 01:36:59,71
中华民国八年八月…
8th month of the 8th year of the Republic...

1652
01:36:59,88 --> 01:37:01,23
念你没念过的字，当中！
Don't miss out the words in between...

1653
01:37:01,40 --> 01:37:04,79
兹委任马邦德为康城县长…
Ma Bangde is hereby appointed Kang County governor...

1654
01:37:05,56 --> 01:37:06,35
等会…
Hang on...

1655
01:37:07,52 --> 01:37:08,43
康城？
Kang County?

1656
01:37:09,56 --> 01:37:10,51
不是鹅城吗？
Not Goose Town?

1657
01:37:10,68 --> 01:37:12,27
从来都是康城
It has always been Kang County.

1658
01:37:12,44 --> 01:37:12,99
好小子
You bastard!

1659
01:37:13,16 --> 01:37:14,07
怨你啊
Blame yourself!

1660
01:37:14,24 --> 01:37:16,99
你把我泡水里，九筒扣脸上
When you dumped me in the river,

1661
01:37:17,20 --> 01:37:19,58
闹钟咔咔咔响，吓死我了！
scared as I was, I had an inspired moment.

1662
01:37:19,76 --> 01:37:22,32
我灵机一动，让你去鹅城
I brought you to Goose Town.

1663
01:37:22,52 --> 01:37:25,87
这鹅城和康城有什么不一样啊？
What's their difference?

1664
01:37:26,04 --> 01:37:28,71
康城富饶，鹅城凶险
Kang County is affluent. Goose Town is deadly.

1665
01:37:28,88 --> 01:37:30,31
那你为什么让我去啊？
Why Goose Town for me?

1666
01:37:30,52 --> 01:37:32,07
你鬼扯叹，截火车！
You're a tough cookie, aren't you?

1667
01:37:32,24 --> 01:37:36,02
告诉你啊，你进了鹅城就有两种情况
There can only be two outcomes.

1668
01:37:36,24 --> 01:37:39,23
第一，你进城就被黄四郎弄死
Either Huang kills you dead,

1669
01:40:51,52 --> 01:40:53,95
告诉弟兄们，上东边去
Tell everyone to go east.

1670
01:40:54,88 --> 01:40:56,43
抓着活的，问出他们头在哪
Bring one in for interrogation.

1671
01:40:56,64 --> 01:40:57,75
我亲手宰了他！
I'll kill their leader myself.

1672
01:40:58,96 --> 01:40:59,99
上东边
Let's move.

1673
01:41:05,40 --> 01:41:05,83
头在哪儿？
Where's your leader?

1674
01:41:06,00 --> 01:41:07,55
北面，脸上有麻子的就是
In the north, with a pockmarked face.

1675
01:41:07,76 --> 01:41:08,90
北面！山顶上
Go north! On the hill.

1676
01:41:14,40 --> 01:41:14,87
我没死吧？
Am I dead?

1677
01:41:15,04 --> 01:41:15,91
没有！没死！
No, you're still alive.

1678
01:41:16,08 --> 01:41:18,19
没死！要说什么？我帮你吹
Do you want to signal a message?

1679
01:41:19,60 --> 01:41:20,79
怎么吹？怎么吹？
How do you whistle?

1680
01:41:30,76 --> 01:41:31,51
你带我走吧！
Can you lead the way?

1681
01:41:31,68 --> 01:41:33,55
不…跑不动！…
No, I can't run any more.

1682
01:41:33,72 --> 01:41:34,23
我带你走
Follow me, then.

1683
01:41:34,40 --> 01:41:35,62
跑不动…！
I can't run.

1684
01:41:35,80 --> 01:41:36,94
不是嘴坏了吗？
You've only blown up your cheeks.

1685
01:41:37,44 --> 01:41:39,11
嘴坏了用脚跑啊！
Your legs are fine.

1686
