“大哥死了，大哥死了”
"Chief is dead! Chief is dead!"

1687
01:41:47,40 --> 01:41:48,31
大哥死了？
The Chief is dead?

1688
01:41:50,80 --> 01:41:52,15
你把大哥给吹死了
You just signalled the Chief's death!

1689
01:41:52,68 --> 01:41:54,19
老五，你去看看
Five, go check it out.

1690
01:41:55,80 --> 01:41:56,86
大哥
Chief!

1691
01:41:57,64 --> 01:41:58,62
大哥
Chief!

1692
