他们说你死了！
They said you're dead.

1694
01:42:02,28 --> 01:42:05,15
放他妈的屁！我这不还活着吗？
Bullshit! Am I not alive?

1695
01:42:05,56 --> 01:42:07,79
“大哥没死”
"Chief is alive and well!"

1696
01:42:08,76 --> 01:42:10,15
放他妈的屁怎么没吹啊？
Why missed out signalling "bullshit"?

1697
01:42:10,28 --> 01:42:11,95
“放你妈的屁”
"You're full of shit!"

1698
01:42:12,12 --> 01:42:13,15
听见没
Hear that?

1699
