骂咱们放你娘的屁呢！
He said we're full of shit.

1700
01:42:18,08 --> 01:42:19,11
等会儿
Wait.

1701
01:32:52,80 --> 01:32:54,07
你最不懂事！
You're the worst!

1702
01:32:54,56 --> 01:32:55,75
你们什么时候出城剿匪？
When are you leaving for your expedition?

1703
01:32:55,96 --> 01:32:56,99
走不了
We aren't.

1704
01:32:57,24 --> 01:32:58,55
钱不到手，出不了城
We can't leave without funding.

1705
01:53:39,44 --> 01:53:41,11
枪在手，跟我走！
Those with guns follow me.

1706
01:53:41,28 --> 01:53:48,19
杀四郎，抢碉楼！
Kill Huang and storm his citadel...

1707
01:53:48,88 --> 01:53:50,31
枪在手，跟我走！
Those with guns follow me.

1708
01:53:50,52 --> 01:53:55,95
杀四郎，抢碉楼！
Kill Huang and storm his citadel...

1709
01:53:56,12 --> 01:53:57,71
枪在手，跟我走！
Those with guns follow me.

1710
