Kill Huang and storm his citadel...

1711
01:54:09,84 --> 01:54:11,55
枪在手，跟我走！
Those with guns follow me.

1712
01:56:57,72 --> 01:56:58,35
去看看
Go and take a look.

1713
01:56:58,56 --> 01:56:59,78
要出人命啦！
Someone will die!

1714
