东边…
East...

1715
01:43:44,44 --> 01:43:47,07
你到底是不是张麻子？
Are you really "Pocky" Zhang?

1716
01:43:47,28 --> 01:43:48,11
我是
Yes, I am.

1717
01:43:48,28 --> 01:43:50,91
我可是快要死的人了
I am about to kick the bucket,

1718
01:43:51,64 --> 01:43:53,35
别骗我
don't lie to me.

1719
01:43:53,92 --> 01:43:55,11
放心
Don't worry.

1720
01:43:56,00 --> 01:43:57,43
我就是张麻子
I really am "Pocky" Zhang.

1721
01:43:58,40 --> 01:44:00,70
麻子
Pocky!

1722
01:44:00,88 --> 01:44:02,91
屁股…
My ass...

1723
01:44:03,52 --> 01:44:05,71
屁股疼
it hurts.

1724
