On my ass over there,

1728
01:44:21,80 --> 01:44:23,99
有五张委任状
I have another five warrants.

1729
01:44:24,52 --> 01:44:26,27
都给你
Take them.

1730
01:44:26,80 --> 01:44:31,23
听我的，千万别回鹅城
Promise never to return to Goose Town.

1731
01:44:31,72 --> 01:44:36,35
你呀，弄不过黄四郎
You can't beat Huang.

1732
01:44:36,56 --> 01:44:39,75
带上银子，走吧
Take the money and run.

1733
01:44:40,12 --> 01:44:42,50
