I lied about two other things.

1735
01:44:49,24 --> 01:44:50,59
骗了就骗了吧
No big deal.

1736
01:44:50,76 --> 01:44:52,27
不行
No.

1737
01:44:52,96 --> 01:44:56,95
我死之前，我必须告诉你
I must confess before I die.

1738
01:44:57,12 --> 01:44:59,35
你说，头一档子
What was the first lie, then?

1739
01:44:59,72 --> 01:45:03,99
我…我能说这第二档子事儿吗？
Can I confess my second lie first?

1740
01:45:04,16 --> 01:45:05,30
好
Yes.

1741
01:45:05,56 --> 01:45:09,31
那谁…你还记得吗？
Do you still remember...

1742
01:48:07,72 --> 01:48:09,71
咱们一个字，斩！
We simply want them...dead!

1743
01:48:10,04 --> 01:48:11,35
可他说过
He has sworn publicly,

1744
01:48:12,36 --> 01:48:14,27
三天之后斩我人头
to behead me in 3 days.

1745
01:48:14,44 --> 01:48:17,71
荆柯当年还说要斩秦始皇呢
Some said I'd win the lottery too!

1746
01:48:22,16 --> 01:48:23,87
大哥，三天
Can the four of us

1747
01:48:24,36 --> 01:48:26,19
就我们四个要杀黄四郎？
kill Huang in three days?

1748
01:48:26,88 --> 01:48:27,27
对
Yes.

1749
01:48:27,44 --> 01:48:28,50
还把话说出去了
We've been telling everyone that.

1750
01:48:28,68 --> 01:48:31,14
话不说出去，事就办不成
We can't back out now!

1751
01:48:31,32 --> 01:48:32,51
胜算有几成啊？
What are our chances?

1752
01:48:33,84 --> 01:48:34,75
“三成”
"30%"

1753
01:48:34,96 --> 01:48:36,43
三成不是玩命吗？
30%? Are we out of our mind?

1754
01:48:37,72 --> 01:48:39,71
我去睡会儿啊，你们在这盯着
Time for a nap. Keep watch.

1755
01:48:53,72 --> 01:48:54,19
南风
Queen!

1756
01:48:54,36 --> 01:48:54,95
北风
Knave!

1757
01:48:55,12 --> 01:48:56,43
胡啦
Bingo!

1758
01:48:57,72 --> 01:48:58,78
大哥，银子都没了！
Chief, the money is gone.

1759
01:48:58,96 --> 01:48:59,59
我看见了
I could see that.

1760
01:48:59,76 --> 01:49:00,74
现在有四成了吧
We must have a 40% chance now!

1761
01:49:00,92 --> 01:49:01,59
五成？
50%?

1762
01:49:01,76 --> 01:49:02,74
七成？
70%?

1763
01:49:03,44 --> 01:49:04,19
不能吧
Surely not!

1764
01:49:04,36 --> 01:49:06,63
老百姓把钱都拿回家了，还三成啊？
Still only 30% after they took the money?

1765
01:49:06,80 --> 01:49:08,23
银子要是这么被拿走了
If things are that simple,

1766
01:49:08,40 --> 01:49:09,75
那钱就白发了
our efforts will be in vain.

1767
01:49:11,00 --> 01:49:11,91
出车！
Send the carriages!

1768
01:49:16,96 --> 01:49:19,71
我要你看一看，什么叫做草船借箭
I'll show you how to "borrow arrows with a straw boat"!

1769
01:35:41,88 --> 01:35:45,75
他今天亲自带队，出兵剿匪
He risks his life to combat the bandits.

1770
01:35:46,12 --> 01:35:49,39
他是我们的大英雄
He is our hero!

1771
01:35:52,68 --> 01:35:53,90
师爷，请！
Counselor, please.

1772
01:35:56,88 --> 01:36:00,03
大风起兮云飞扬
It's time for heroes to take centre stage!

1773
01:36:00,24 --> 01:36:03,39
安得猛士兮走四方
It's time for heroes to show their mettle!

1774
01:36:03,60 --> 01:36:07,07
麻匪，任何时候都要剿
We must rid ourselves of these bandits.

1775
01:36:07,28 --> 01:36:08,79
不剿不行
We don't have a choice.

1776
01:36:09,00 --> 01:36:11,79
你们想想，你带着老婆
Imagine, if you take your wife out,

1777
01:37:39,40 --> 01:37:41,31
我马走康城，从容上任
and I'll move on to Kang County.

1778
01:37:41,52 --> 01:37:44,35
第二，你有种，咱俩办了黄四郎
Or we sort out Huang instead,

1779
01:37:44,56 --> 01:37:45,78
就像现在这样
Iike what's happening now.

1780
01:37:45,96 --> 01:37:47,91
好！说得好，马邦德
Very clever!

1781
01:37:48,08 --> 01:37:48,87
你这个骗子
You goddamned crook!

1782
01:37:49,04 --> 01:37:50,87
早晚有一天你会被张麻子
One day Pocky will get you,

1783
01:37:51,04 --> 01:37:52,15
一枪崩了
and blast you to hell!

1784
01:37:52,32 --> 01:37:53,15
你崩了我？
You won't.

1785
01:37:53,32 --> 01:37:54,79
你舍不得
You love me too much.

1786
01:37:54,96 --> 01:37:57,71
你还真相信我就是张麻子？
You still think I'm "Pocky" Zhang?

1787
01:37:58,92 --> 01:38:01,03
你要不是张麻子，这山上可就有真麻子
If not, the real one must be somewhere around.

1788
01:39:21,08 --> 01:39:21,71
告诉他们
Tell them!

1789
01:39:21,88 --> 01:39:23,99
让老三去找老四，把南边干掉
Three joins Four to secure our south.

1790
01:39:24,12 --> 01:39:25,51
老七回来保护师爷！
Seven back to protect the Counselor.

1791
01:39:27,84 --> 01:39:30,79
“老三去找老四，干掉南面”
"Three and Four to secure the south."

1792
01:39:30,96 --> 01:39:34,39
“老七回来保护师爷”
"Seven back to guard the Counselor."

1793
01:39:45,88 --> 01:39:48,18
“我被包围了”
"I'm out-flanked."

1794
01:39:51,72 --> 01:39:52,67
“听我口令，甩斗笠”
"Throw the hats on my signal!"

1795
01:39:52,84 --> 01:39:54,91
“东边归我，西边归你”
"I'll take the east. You the west."

1796
01:40:11,72 --> 01:40:13,59
大哥，老三老四他们得手了
Three and Four are done.

1797
01:40:14,20 --> 01:40:15,91
大哥我到了！大哥我到了！
I'm back. I'm back.

1798
01:40:17,52 --> 01:40:18,31
师爷交给你了，快！
Stay with the Counselor!

1799
01:40:18,52 --> 01:40:19,39
明白！
Understood.

1800
01:40:19,72 --> 01:40:20,78
师爷，快！
Counselor, come!

1801
01:40:24,16 --> 01:40:25,07
三哥！
Three!

1802
01:40:26,52 --> 01:40:27,55
好像是二哥
It looks like Two.

1803
01:40:27,84 --> 01:40:30,35
南国张麻子在此
Pocky Zhang is here.

1804
01:40:31,84 --> 01:40:35,67
钱留下，银子也留下… 是二哥
- Leave your money... - It's Two.

1805
01:47:42,20 --> 01:47:44,66
老爷，散不了吧！
The money is not being taken!

1806
01:47:45,28 --> 01:47:49,75
你瞧，除了鹅，没有活物敢过去
No one dare to go near except those geese!

1807
01:47:59,28 --> 01:47:59,79
我去找花姐
I'll go and find Flora!

1808
01:47:59,96 --> 01:48:01,95
你把花姐和替身都给我找回来
Bring her and Huang's double back.

1809
01:48:02,12 --> 01:48:03,59
三天之内必须找回来！
We only have three days.

1810
01:48:03,76 --> 01:48:05,91
这个张麻子到底要干嘛呢？
What is on his mind?

1811
01:48:06,04 --> 01:48:07,55
他们干什么都是白干！
They're a bunch of clowns!

1812
01:49:19,88 --> 01:49:22,79
老爷，咱们放的是马，不是船
But we just sent horses, not straw boats.

1813
01:49:23,88 --> 01:49:24,63
你这个傻瓜
Idiot!

1814
01:49:24,80 --> 01:49:27,79
这叫比喻！比喻！…
It's only a metaphor!

1815
01:49:28,00 --> 01:49:29,31
不就是赤壁嘛！
You're almost metaphysical!

1816
01:49:51,32 --> 01:49:52,79
银子都被黄四郎收走了
Huang has taken all the silvers.

1817
01:49:53,60 --> 01:49:55,51
胜算都不到一成了
We've no chance of winning.

1818
01:49:57,04 --> 01:49:58,87
“六成”
"60%"

1819
01:49:59,04 --> 01:50:00,35
黄四郎都没出面啊
Huang didn't even have to show up,

1820
01:50:00,56 --> 01:50:02,35
老百姓把所有钱都交出去了
everyone has surrendered their money.

1821
01:50:02,56 --> 01:50:03,59
哪来六啊？
How can it be 60%?

1822
01:50:03,76 --> 01:50:04,82
说得对！
Well said!

1823
01:50:05,04 --> 01:50:05,67
为什么？
So why 60%?

1824
01:50:05,84 --> 01:50:06,75
怕啊！
It's because of fear.

1825
01:50:06,92 --> 01:50:08,27
怕里边有什么？
What lies beneath fear?

1826
01:50:08,96 --> 01:50:10,15
有怒！
Rage!

1827
01:50:10,80 --> 01:50:13,51
我一定把他们心里的怒给勾出来
We need to bring forth their rage!

1828
01:50:22,80 --> 01:50:24,19
满街枪弹在你手！
As guns and ammos wait for you,

1829
01:50:25,08 --> 01:50:27,15
十成白银在碉楼！
Huang hoards fortune in his citadel.

1830
01:50:28,28 --> 01:50:29,87
满街枪弹在你手！
As guns and ammos wait for you,

1831
01:50:31,16 --> 01:50:32,91
十成白银在碉楼！
Huang hoards fortune in his citadel.

1832
01:50:59,08 --> 01:51:00,99
屡败还屡战！
Never-say-die!

1833
01:51:01,20 --> 01:51:01,71
我喜欢！
I like that!

1834
01:51:01,88 --> 01:51:04,71
那是枪啊！要不，放马？
Those are guns! Send carriages?

1835
01:51:04,88 --> 01:51:09,39
拿银子，是贪！拿枪，是反
Money incites greed. But guns are seditious!

1836
01:51:09,88 --> 01:51:11,27
他们没这个胆！
They wouldn't dare.

1837
01:51:12,72 --> 01:51:15,15
银子被收走了，枪也没人拿
The money's gone, but the guns remain!

1838
01:51:15,80 --> 01:51:16,71
怎么办，大哥？
What do we do now?

1839
01:51:16,88 --> 01:51:18,15
胜算几成？
What are our chances?

1840
01:51:18,72 --> 01:51:20,23
“七成”
"70%"

1841
01:51:22,12 --> 01:51:23,91
黄四郎把所有的钱都给收了
Huang has taken all the money.

1842
01:51:24,08 --> 01:51:25,19
我们发的枪也没人拿
But no one takes our guns.

1843
01:51:25,36 --> 01:51:26,58
哪来的七成啊？
How come it's 70%?

1844
01:51:26,76 --> 01:51:29,55
黄四郎要是不收银子，我发枪干什么？
If he hadn't taken the money, I wouldn't have to distribute the guns!

1845
01:51:30,04 --> 01:51:32,67
黄四郎不收银子，我发枪干什么？
...wouldn't have distributed the guns!

1846
01:51:32,84 --> 01:51:33,95
我…
I...

1847
01:51:34,76 --> 01:51:35,90
去睡会儿
need a nap.

1848
01:51:48,32 --> 01:51:48,83
东风
King!

1849
01:51:49,00 --> 01:51:50,35
南风 胡了
- Queen! - Bingo!

1850
01:51:54,20 --> 01:51:55,11
我明白了
I got it!

1851
01:51:55,28 --> 01:51:57,66
你发的不是枪，你发的就是怒！
You were inciting rage and anger!

1852
01:51:58,08 --> 01:51:58,99
收枪
Collect the guns.

1853
01:52:13,76 --> 01:52:14,71
没动静啊
You missed?

1854
01:57:00,08 --> 01:57:02,07
要出人命了！
There will be fatalities!

1855
01:57:04,32 --> 01:57:05,83
至少得死一个
At least one of them will die!

1856
01:57:07,44 --> 01:57:08,35
起！
Hoist!

1857
01:57:09,92 --> 01:57:12,67
弟兄们，我们打赢了，凯旋
Brothers! We've won the war!

1858
01:57:12,92 --> 01:57:13,23
明白吗？
Understood?

1859
01:57:13,40 --> 01:57:14,03
明白！
Understood!

1860
01:38:40,08 --> 01:38:41,11
东边还有一大片！
Another group to the east.

1861
01:38:41,32 --> 01:38:42,51
让老七去找老三
Tell Seven to join Three!

1862
01:38:42,96 --> 01:38:44,02
先把西边的收拾掉
Secure our west flank.

1863
01:38:47,64 --> 01:38:52,27
“老七去找老三，干掉西面”
"Seven and Three to secure west flank!"

1864
01:38:57,64 --> 01:38:59,91
“我到了”
"I'm there!"

1865
01:39:00,60 --> 01:39:01,66
“不是十个，是十一个”
"There are 11 of them, not 10!"

1866
01:39:01,84 --> 01:39:04,99
“没事，你四，我七”
"No sweat, let's share them!"

1867
01:39:14,36 --> 01:39:15,23
“落停”
"Done!"

1868
01:39:15,40 --> 01:39:16,87
老三来信，西边搞定
Message from Three. West is secured.

1869
01:39:18,44 --> 01:39:20,90
这鸡叫成电台了，我看行！
These pheasant calls really work wonder!

1870
01:42:22,88 --> 01:42:24,10
假麻子抓到了
They caught the fake!

1871
01:42:25,36 --> 01:42:26,58
你是张麻子？
You're "Pocky" Zhang?

1872
01:42:27,00 --> 01:42:28,22
你脸上怎么没有麻子呢？
Where are your pockmarks?

1873
01:42:28,64 --> 01:42:29,51
这事谁问谁死！
No one asking that question has survived.

1874
01:42:29,68 --> 01:42:30,95
明白了！不问了
Oops! I take it back.

1875
01:42:32,52 --> 01:42:33,83
我这儿有一宝贝
I've got something special.

1876
01:42:34,16 --> 01:42:35,07
送给你了
You can have them,

1877
01:42:35,24 --> 01:42:36,67
能换我一条命吧？
in exchange for my life.

1878
01:42:39,84 --> 01:42:41,19
那…那两个人呢？
What happened to them?

1879
01:42:41,32 --> 01:42:43,15
说实话能换一条命吧
If I tell you, will you spare me?

1880
01:42:43,32 --> 01:42:43,75
快说！
Speak!

1881
01:42:43,92 --> 01:42:46,11
大个的被我给锯了， 比矮个的还矮
I sawed the legs off the tall one.

1882
01:42:46,28 --> 01:42:47,11
矮的呢？
And the short one?

1883
01:42:47,28 --> 01:42:48,19
当场就被吓死了
She died of fright at the sight!

1884
01:42:51,72 --> 01:42:52,19
师爷！
Counselor.

1885
01:42:52,32 --> 01:42:53,43
师爷！师爷！
Counselor...

1886
01:42:53,64 --> 01:42:54,55
谁让你冒充我的？
Who's behind this scam?

1887
01:42:54,72 --> 01:42:55,83
黄老爷
Master Huang.

1888
01:42:56,68 --> 01:42:57,74
麻子哪儿来的？
Nice pockmarks!

1889
01:42:57,92 --> 01:42:58,59
他烫的
He burnt them.

1890
01:42:58,76 --> 01:42:59,74
劫了几任县官？
How many governors have you robbed?

1891
01:42:59,92 --> 01:43:01,19
说出来能换条命吗？
Will you spare me?

1892
01:43:01,36 --> 01:43:01,95
快说！
Speak!

1893
01:43:02,12 --> 01:43:04,79
五回！五个县长全被我给干掉了
I've killed five governors,

1894
01:43:04,96 --> 01:43:06,23
钱我跟黄老爷给分了
and shared the loot with Master Huang.

1895
01:43:06,40 --> 01:43:07,43
那是什么？
What's that?

1896
01:43:07,64 --> 01:43:09,51
万民伞！那五个被我干掉的县长留下的
A governor's silver umbrella.

1897
01:43:09,68 --> 01:43:10,87
全都给你！
Take it!

1898
01:43:11,20 --> 01:43:12,99
山西往哪边走啊？ 我还有四把呢
- Which way to Shanxi? - I have four more.

1899
01:43:13,16 --> 01:43:14,38
我知道
I know the way.

1900
01:43:14,60 --> 01:43:15,71
说出来能换条人命吧？
Will you spare me if I tell you?

1901
01:43:15,88 --> 01:43:16,86
快他妈说！
Goddamned it! Speak!

1902
01:43:17,04 --> 01:43:18,75
往东！往东！
To the east, to the east!

1903
01:43:19,60 --> 01:43:22,63
哎呀！不能往东！千万不能往东！
Come back! You mustn't go that way!

1904
01:43:29,84 --> 01:43:31,87
山西确实是在东边
But Shanxi really is to our east.

1905
01:59:39,40 --> 01:59:41,35
一刀给砍了！
by that stupid Governor!

1906
01:59:41,72 --> 01:59:44,79
何止是愚蠢，简直就是愚蠢
That was stupid! That was ignorant!

1907
01:59:44,96 --> 01:59:45,87
这公平吗？
That's not justice!

1908
01:59:46,04 --> 01:59:46,87
不公平！
No! It's not!

1909
01:59:47,08 --> 01:59:48,19
乡亲们答应吗？
Can you let this pass?

1910
01:59:48,36 --> 01:59:49,34
不答应！
No!

1911
01:59:49,56 --> 01:59:50,35
我不是他
I am not him.

1912
01:59:50,56 --> 01:59:51,43
我知道你是替身
I know you're his double.

1913
01:59:51,64 --> 01:59:53,35
替他享福！替他作恶！
But you shared his life and committed his crimes.

1914
01:59:53,56 --> 01:59:56,19
你就应该替他，把他没受过的罪
So you should be punished

1915
01:59:56,36 --> 01:59:57,27
给我受够了！
as if you were him!

1916
01:59:57,44 --> 01:59:58,71
跪下！ 我真的不是他
- Kneel down! - I really am not him!

1917
01:59:58,88 --> 02:00:00,63
跪下！跪下！…
Kneel down! Kneel!

1918
02:00:00,80 --> 02:00:01,78
别让我发脾气
Don't make me mad!

1919
02:00:01,96 --> 02:00:02,59
我数三下！
On my count of three!

1920
02:00:02,76 --> 02:00:03,67
一！
One!

1921
02:00:05,28 --> 02:00:06,34
二！
Two!

1922
02:00:07,08 --> 02:00:07,87
一！
One!

1923
02:00:08,24 --> 02:00:09,15
二！
Two!

1924
02:00:09,32 --> 02:00:11,51
谁？哪个欠打的？
What the...? Who's the son-of-a-bitch?

1925
02:00:11,68 --> 02:00:13,31
又想挨板子了是吧？
Want your ass kicked again?

1926
02:00:13,52 --> 02:00:15,03
大人，我讨厌吗？
Am I bothering you, sir?

1927
02:00:15,20 --> 02:00:17,15
如果我讨厌，我立马消失！
Say the word and I'll disappear.

1928
