你是个体面人
You're a man of honour.

2033
02:03:21,20 --> 02:03:22,42
只有一颗子弹
There's only one bullet left.

2034
02:03:24,12 --> 02:03:25,23
够
That's enough.

2035
02:03:25,92 --> 02:03:27,11
等等
Wait.

2036
02:03:27,64 --> 02:03:28,91
有话要我带给老汤？
Any message for Tang?

2037
