I lied to him.

2040
02:03:36,36 --> 02:03:37,75
你骗了他什么？
What was your lie?

2041
02:03:38,00 --> 02:03:40,30
我跟他说不回鹅城了
I said I wouldn't come back.

2042
02:03:40,76 --> 02:03:41,71
可是我回来了
But here I am.

2043
