They're here.

2075
01:56:16,96 --> 01:56:17,94
你可回来了！
You're back, at last.

2076
01:56:18,12 --> 01:56:20,27
我不是他，我只是个唱戏的！
I'm not Huang! I'm just an actor!

2077
