Let him go?

2092
01:59:26,64 --> 01:59:29,63
欠打的过来！过去！…
You bastard, go over here! Over there!

2093
01:59:29,80 --> 01:59:30,35
站好了！
Stand properly!

2094
01:59:30,56 --> 01:59:31,78
乡亲们！
My fellow townsfolk!

2095
01:59:31,96 --> 01:59:33,63
黄四郎是死了
Huang has died!

2096
01:59:33,84 --> 01:59:35,67
