I have 9 ways to skin this cat!

2104
02:04:52,16 --> 02:04:53,35
九种！
Nine ways!

2105
02:04:54,96 --> 02:04:56,23
听我的雷声！
You'll hear my roar!

2106
02:04:57,12 --> 02:04:59,03
是有这么回事，怎么了？
Maybe just a little. Why?

2107
