02:01:09,16 --> 02:01:11,79
那帽子挺好，我喜欢
It was a nice hat. I liked it.

2134
02:01:12,04 --> 02:01:15,11
那不是最好的，我家里还有更好的
I have nicer ones at home.

2135
02:01:16,16 --> 02:01:17,27
转头送给你
I can give them to you.

2136
02:01:20,40 --> 02:01:22,15
一下子弄成了这样
Everything's gone in a flash.

2137
02:01:23,96 --> 02:01:25,99
你让我输得很惨啊！
You've totally wiped me out.

2138
02:01:27,80 --> 02:01:29,59
惨吗？黄老爷
It's not that bad.

2139
02:01:29,76 --> 02:01:31,31
你现在还抽着烟
You're still having a smoke,

2140
02:01:31,88 --> 02:01:33,43
还说着话
still chit-chatting.

2141
02:05:13,80 --> 02:05:14,86
还想回山里啊？
Still want to resume banditry?

2142
02:05:15,04 --> 02:05:16,59
您这腿脚都不利落了
You're too old for this.

2143
02:05:17,24 --> 02:05:19,67
怎么也不跟我打个招呼
You should've given me a heads-up.

2144
02:05:20,16 --> 02:05:21,87
这不正要跟您打招呼了嘛
That's what we're doing!

2145
02:05:22,92 --> 02:05:25,27
你不是要跟我当麻匪，到处发钱吗？
Didn't you want to be one of us?

2146
02:05:25,44 --> 02:05:27,11
今天不是把钱都发光了吗？
I just helped to dish out the money.

2147
02:05:27,28 --> 02:05:28,83
还有比今天更过瘾的？
I've never had a more satisfying day!

2148
02:05:29,08 --> 02:05:30,55
你看我都穿上这身了！
I'm even dressed for the part!

2149
02:05:31,72 --> 02:05:32,83
这么说…
So...

2150
02:05:34,04 --> 02:05:34,91
你改主意了？
you've changed your mind?

2151
02:05:35,08 --> 02:05:36,51
那还用说吗
That goes without saying!

2152
02:05:38,92 --> 02:05:40,95
老三，你有什么打算？
What's your plan, Three?

2153
02:05:41,96 --> 02:05:43,71
我要替二哥娶她
I'm going to marry her, on behalf of Two.

2154
02:05:45,84 --> 02:05:48,14
老二啊老二…
Two...

2155
02:05:48,92 --> 02:05:51,51
大哥，我是老三
Chief, I'm Three!

2156
02:05:54,56 --> 02:05:56,91
老三，你跟我在一起
Three, it no longer thrills you

2157
02:05:58,16 --> 02:06:00,11
不高兴吗？ 高兴
- to ride with me? - Yes!

2158
02:06:00,64 --> 02:06:01,75
就是…
But...

2159
02:06:02,60 --> 02:06:03,87
有点不轻松
it's been hard going lately.

2160
02:06:05,72 --> 02:06:06,78
你们俩呢？ 有点
- What about you? - We've had...

2161
02:06:06,96 --> 02:06:08,35
不轻松
better days.

2162
02:06:08,76 --> 02:06:09,59
老七呢？
Seven?

2163
02:06:14,08 --> 02:06:16,03
大哥…
Chief...

2164
02:06:17,56 --> 02:06:18,87
姑娘
Flora,

2165
02:06:19,88 --> 02:06:21,35
你这么拿着枪
hold your guns like this,

2166
02:06:21,96 --> 02:06:23,15
更好看
makes you look even cooler.

2167
02:06:28,76 --> 02:06:29,87
送你了
They're yours.

2168
02:06:32,52 --> 02:06:34,11
大哥，那我们先走一步啊！
Chief, we've got to go.

2169
02:06:34,28 --> 02:06:34,83
走了，大哥
Goodbye, Chief.

2170
02:06:35,00 --> 02:06:35,39
走！
Go!

2171
02:06:35,60 --> 02:06:37,31
走了，大哥
Bye, Chief!

2172
02:06:37,52 --> 02:06:39,63
别忘了下回跟我打个招呼啊
Give me a heads-up next time.

2173
00:34:47,12 --> 00:34:49,71
易守难攻，万夫莫开！
It is simply impregnable.

2174
00:34:50,12 --> 00:34:53,15
县长英雄气概，师爷文采斐然
An intrepid governor, an erudite counselor.

2175
00:34:53,32 --> 00:34:55,59
珠联璧合！二位请！
What a dream team!

2176
00:34:59,04 --> 00:35:01,71
六爷的死，壮烈！
Master Six has died heroically.

2177
00:35:02,20 --> 00:35:04,07
今天请县长来
I've invited you here today

2178
00:35:04,24 --> 00:35:08,59
就是要当面为六爷讨回这个公道！
to witness how justice is done.

2179
00:35:08,80 --> 00:35:10,63
如果真的是黄某指使
If I'm proven to be the instigator,

2180
00:35:10,80 --> 00:35:12,02
那我就像六爷一样
I will follow Master Six's footstep,

2181
00:35:12,20 --> 00:35:14,03
当众剖腹自杀！
and disembowel myself!

2182
00:35:14,20 --> 00:35:16,95
不但自杀，还请县长您
I invite you to be my second,

2183
00:37:14,88 --> 00:37:17,75
老大往往是空架子
It is hard to be a boss.

2184
00:37:18,04 --> 00:37:21,51
每天眼一睁，几百人吃、喝、拉、撒
Hundreds of people everyday

2185
00:37:21,68 --> 00:37:23,15
都要等着我伺候
waiting to be fed.

2186
00:37:23,32 --> 00:37:25,67
真正落到我嘴里的，能有几口
There is little left for me.

2187
00:37:25,84 --> 00:37:29,51
如果县长真的急着赚钱
If you're looking to make a fast buck,

2188
00:37:29,68 --> 00:37:31,83
我倒是有个好去处！
I know exactly what to do.

2189
00:37:32,64 --> 00:37:34,07
哦？请讲！
Please tell.

2190
00:37:34,96 --> 00:37:37,52
张麻子
Pocky Zhang!

2191
00:37:44,20 --> 00:37:45,55
真死了！
One of them just died!

2192
00:38:00,20 --> 00:38:01,55
张麻子？
Pocky Zhang?

2193
00:38:01,72 --> 00:38:03,87
对，张麻子！
Yes, Pocky Zhang!

2194
00:38:04,08 --> 00:38:07,91
那么这个张麻子，是跟我们有关系呢？
What has he got to do with us?

2195
00:38:08,08 --> 00:38:09,99
还是跟钱有关系？
Or with our money?

2196
00:38:10,16 --> 00:38:11,14
都有关系！
Everything!

2197
00:38:11,32 --> 00:38:13,35
莫非他在鹅城？
Is he here in Goose Town?

2198
00:38:13,56 --> 00:38:14,70
在…
Well, yes...

2199
00:38:16,64 --> 00:38:18,03
也不在！
and no!

2200
00:38:23,28 --> 00:38:26,31
黄老爷这话，还挺有玄机啊！
Master Huang speaks in riddles!

2201
00:29:43,04 --> 00:29:46,27
六爷，挺住！我去给你请大夫！
Hang in there! I'll get a doctor!

2202
00:29:47,16 --> 00:29:50,59
别走！是不是只有一碗！
There's only one bowl, right?

2203
00:29:50,80 --> 00:29:53,91
是不是只有一碗！是不是！
There's only one bowl, right?

2204
00:30:00,92 --> 00:30:02,14
该你了
Your turn!

2205
00:30:02,60 --> 00:30:04,51
我知道你只吃了一碗
I knew it all along.

2206
00:30:05,40 --> 00:30:07,15
你上当了
You fell for it.

2207
00:30:07,92 --> 00:30:11,67
不能杀…！我不能放！
You mustn't kill him! No, I won't!

2208
00:30:12,08 --> 00:30:12,95
为什么不能杀？
Tell me why I should spare him,

2209
00:30:13,12 --> 00:30:14,75
说不出说法来，我把你一起杀了
or I'll shoot you, too.

2210
00:23:05,20 --> 00:23:05,83
我
No, it's "me"!

2211
00:23:06,00 --> 00:23:06,63
你？
You?

2212
00:23:06,80 --> 00:23:08,63
你，你自己
You, you yourself!

2213
00:23:08,80 --> 00:23:10,71
我自己，我自己
Yes, me and me alone.

2214
00:23:10,88 --> 00:23:12,02
听不见
I can't hear you.

2215
00:26:02,64 --> 00:26:03,70
只给了一碗的钱
and paid only for one.

2216
00:26:03,88 --> 00:26:05,39
放屁，我就吃了一碗的粉
Bullshit! I have only eaten one bowl!

2217
00:26:05,60 --> 00:26:06,99
给了他一碗的钱！
And I paid him for one.

2218
00:26:07,16 --> 00:26:08,11
他吃了几碗？
How many bowls did he eat?

2219
00:26:08,28 --> 00:26:09,19
两碗
Two...

2220
00:26:09,36 --> 00:26:10,50
不可能！
No way!

2221
00:26:10,68 --> 00:26:12,19
六爷是县长的儿子
Master Six is the Governor's godson,

2222
00:26:12,36 --> 00:26:14,07
怎么能欠你的粉钱呢？
why would he want to cheat you?

2223
00:26:14,24 --> 00:26:16,15
就是吃了两碗，只给了一碗的钱
But he ate two bowls and paid for one.

2224
00:26:16,36 --> 00:26:20,83
县长要给我们鹅城一个公平
The Governor brings justice to our town.

2225
00:26:21,00 --> 00:26:22,11
好！
Good!

2226
00:26:22,28 --> 00:26:24,35
我今天讨的就是一个公平
And justice is what I seek today!

2227
00:26:24,56 --> 00:26:25,15
对
Hear hear!

2228
00:26:25,36 --> 00:26:28,75
问谁讨？问县长儿子。为什么？
From the Governor's son, of course.

2229
00:26:28,92 --> 00:26:32,11
他吃了两碗粉，只给了一碗的钱
Ate two bowls, paid for one!

2230
00:26:32,28 --> 00:26:34,23
这就叫作不公平！
That's so wrong!

2231
00:26:34,40 --> 00:26:36,55
既然县长儿子带头不公平
Since his boy is guilty of unjust,

2232
00:26:36,72 --> 00:26:38,31
那县长说的话就是个屁
the Governor's crusade is bullshit!

2233
00:26:38,52 --> 00:26:39,19
我操
Screw you!

2234
00:26:39,36 --> 00:26:42,98
六爷…
Master Six...

2235
00:26:43,76 --> 00:26:46,35
胡万，六爷是县长的儿子
Master Six is the Governor's godson!

2236
00:26:46,56 --> 00:26:47,95
怎么会欠他的粉钱呢？
Would he cheat over a bowl of jelly?

2237
00:26:48,12 --> 00:26:49,91
你亲眼看见了？
Did you see it with your own eyes?

2238
00:26:50,08 --> 00:26:53,39
嘿，你个吃里爬外的东西
You double-crosser!

2239
00:26:53,56 --> 00:26:54,75
怎么着？
What's wrong with you?

2240
00:26:55,00 --> 00:26:56,19
屁股不疼了？
You're thinking with your butts?

2241
00:26:57,04 --> 00:26:59,03
今不聊屁股的事
It's not about my butts.

2242
00:26:59,32 --> 00:27:00,63
就聊凉粉
We're here for the truth!

2243
00:27:00,80 --> 00:27:03,39
一碗就是一碗，两碗就是两碗
One or two bowls?

2244
00:27:03,56 --> 00:27:04,62
不能含糊
No beating about the bush!

2245
00:27:04,80 --> 00:27:07,39
六爷，汉子！佩服！
I admire your courage, sir.

2246
00:27:10,92 --> 00:27:12,79
一就是一，二就是二
I know how to count!

2247
00:27:12,96 --> 00:27:14,07
我今天就吃了一碗凉粉
I ate only one bowl!

2248
00:27:14,24 --> 00:27:16,75
你给了一碗的钱，吃了两碗粉
You ate two and paid for one.

2249
00:27:16,92 --> 00:27:19,75
你没钱是吧，我帮你给！
If you can't afford it, my treat!

2250
00:27:21,08 --> 00:27:23,07
看见了吗？多少碗我都付得起！
I can afford all the jelly in this world!

2251
00:27:23,24 --> 00:27:25,51
但是吃一碗的粉，就给一碗的钱
But I pay only for what I ate.

2252
00:27:25,68 --> 00:27:28,95
这么多钱，他吃了多少碗粉啊
How many bowls did he eat?

2253
00:36:07,68 --> 00:36:10,06
马某人这个县长，买来的
I bought this governorship.

2254
00:36:10,24 --> 00:36:11,75
买官就是为了赚钱
Sole purpose is to get rich.

2255
00:36:11,92 --> 00:36:15,39
而且，马某人不喜欢赚穷人的钱
But I don't take from the poor.

2256
00:36:15,60 --> 00:36:17,27
那你想赚谁的钱呢？
Then who are you targeting?

2257
00:36:17,44 --> 00:36:19,35
谁有钱就赚谁的！
Only the wealthy people.

2258
00:36:19,56 --> 00:36:20,31
那谁有钱？
Who are the wealthy?

2259
00:36:20,52 --> 00:36:21,79
你有钱
Such as you.

2260
00:36:23,04 --> 00:36:27,43
爽快！县长看上什么了，随便拿
Whatever you fancy, help yourself.

2261
00:36:31,88 --> 00:36:34,03
我不是土匪！我是县长
I'm no bandit. I'm a governor.

2262
00:36:34,20 --> 00:36:37,95
县长赚钱得讲究个名正言顺才是
I make my fortune the proper way.

2263
00:36:38,12 --> 00:36:38,87
说得好
Well said!

2264
00:36:39,24 --> 00:36:40,99
我们鹅城有两大家族
Goose Town has two big families.

2265
00:36:41,16 --> 00:36:44,07
都是把人卖到美国修铁路
They sell people to America to build railroads,

2266
00:36:44,24 --> 00:36:46,80
赚的都是美金
in return for dollars!

2267
00:36:46,96 --> 00:36:48,35
还说刀的事
What do you mean by dolls?

2268
00:36:48,56 --> 00:36:52,18
不是…美金是美国人用的钱
No, d-o-l-l-a-r-s! American money.

2269
00:36:52,36 --> 00:36:53,42
美金！懂吗？
Dollar! You know?

2270
00:36:53,64 --> 00:36:54,99
美金，收到了
Oh, dollars!

2271
00:36:55,16 --> 00:36:58,91
黄老爷一来，钱就到了
I can smell it in your presence!

2272
00:37:01,08 --> 00:37:02,30
喝一杯吧 好，来
- Let's drink to that! - Great, cheers!

2273
00:37:02,52 --> 00:37:03,87
来…
Cheers!

2274
00:37:06,16 --> 00:37:08,99
黄老爷，客气了
Master Huang is so modest.

2275
00:37:09,16 --> 00:37:11,23
整个南国谁不知道
It is an open secret that,

2276
00:37:11,52 --> 00:37:12,66
在鹅城
in Goose Town,

2277
00:37:13,16 --> 00:37:14,71
你黄四郎是老大！
Master Huang is our real boss!

2278
00:38:36,84 --> 00:38:37,90
明白吗？ 不明白
- Know what I mean? - No

2279
00:38:38,12 --> 00:38:39,75
我是做什么生意的？明白吗？
Know what I do for a living?

2280
00:38:39,92 --> 00:38:40,59
不明白
No.

2281
00:38:40,76 --> 00:38:42,67
小半个民国的烟土
Half the opium smokers in this nation

2282
00:38:42,84 --> 00:38:44,63
都是黄老爷您在贩卖
rely on Master Huang for their supply!

2283
00:38:44,80 --> 00:38:48,75
错！不过是给刘都统当跑腿的
No, I'm only a pawn for General Liu.

2284
00:38:48,92 --> 00:38:51,15
而且只是其中一条腿
I'm just one of his runners!

2285
00:38:51,32 --> 00:38:53,43
那么刘都统到底有几条腿呢？
How many runners does Liu have?

2286
00:38:53,64 --> 00:38:55,11
三条叹
Three.

2287
00:39:50,36 --> 00:39:55,03
明白！事成之后，一百八十万如数奉还
Yes, we'll pay you back $1.8 million,

2288
00:39:55,20 --> 00:39:59,07
咱们分两大家族那点儿钱！
and split the dollars from the others.

2289
00:39:59,84 --> 00:40:01,83
一百八十万不用还！
There's no need to pay him back!

2290
00:40:02,08 --> 00:40:03,79
不就是剿匪么！剿！
We'll hit these bandits hard!

2291
00:40:03,96 --> 00:40:06,19
咱们把张麻子劫走的那点钱
Whatever they seized in the past,

2292
00:40:06,36 --> 00:40:08,55
全拿回来，还给黄老爷！
we will retrieve for the Master.

2293
00:40:09,52 --> 00:40:10,23
到那个时候
Look at the bigger picture,

2294
00:40:10,40 --> 00:40:13,71
这一百八十万就是九牛身上的一根毛
the $1.8 million bounty is but a strand of hair.

2295
00:40:13,88 --> 00:40:14,71
您还在意吗？
Surely you won't mind!

2296
00:40:14,88 --> 00:40:17,91
不就是个小小的张麻子吗？办他！
We'll get rid of Pocky Zhang!

2297
00:40:18,36 --> 00:40:18,83
硬！
Cool!

2298
00:40:19,00 --> 00:40:19,98
硬吗？够硬！
- Cool enough? - Very cool!

2299
00:40:20,16 --> 00:40:21,51
硬不硬以后再说！
We can discuss that later.

2300
00:40:21,68 --> 00:40:23,35
我脑子里想的只有一件事
The only thing I want to do now

2301
00:40:23,56 --> 00:40:26,35
替黄老爷把这条腿接上！
is to fix Master's crippled leg.

2302
00:40:26,76 --> 00:40:29,03
一个张麻子也太嚣张了！
Pocky Zhang's such a nuisance.

2303
00:40:29,24 --> 00:40:31,87
欺负到黄哥头上了，不答应
He shouldn't have messed with Master Huang!

2304
00:40:32,24 --> 00:40:32,75
喝酒
Let's top up.

2305
00:40:34,88 --> 00:40:37,67
我以为，酒一口一口喝
I believe in taking our time,

2306
00:40:37,84 --> 00:40:39,27
路一步一步走
doing things step by step!

2307
00:40:39,44 --> 00:40:41,07
步子迈大了，喀！
I don't want to break my balls

2308
00:40:41,36 --> 00:40:42,27
容易一场空
by over-stretching!

2309
00:40:42,44 --> 00:40:44,51
应该先把钱分清楚
We should agree on the split first,

2310
00:40:44,68 --> 00:40:45,87
再说接腿的事儿
before thinking of how to fix his leg.

2311
00:43:10,76 --> 00:43:14,03
嘘！安静一点
Quiet, quiet...

2312
00:43:14,40 --> 00:43:16,39
那么彼时彼刻
So it was there and then...

2313
00:43:16,60 --> 00:43:21,39
,｝合如此时此刻
A bit like, here and now!

2314
00:43:23,56 --> 00:43:26,67
竟能如此相像
What a coincidence!

2315
00:43:26,84 --> 00:43:29,40
像！很像！
Exactly!

2316
00:43:29,88 --> 00:43:33,19
不过你比他缺了一样东西
But you're missing something.

2317
00:32:03,44 --> 00:32:05,19
大哥不应该听他的
Chief should have ignored Tang.

2318
00:32:05,36 --> 00:32:07,35
姓汤的不是个好玩意
He is a good-for-nothing!

2319
00:32:13,88 --> 00:32:17,63
六爷，黄四郎这招叫杀人不用刀
Huang kills without lifting a finger!

2320
00:32:17,80 --> 00:32:20,71
我给你爹出的招叫杀人诛心
We must retaliate by destroying his soul.

2321
00:32:20,88 --> 00:32:24,35
不能拼命啊！拼命还怎么赚钱！
We can't jeopardise our chance to get rich!

2322
00:32:34,00 --> 00:32:34,98
六子
Six...

2323
00:32:35,76 --> 00:32:37,87
赚钱对我算个事儿吗？
I do not care about being rich.

2324
00:32:38,04 --> 00:32:40,87
我不是要杀人诛心，是没想出好办法
But I must come up with a game plan

2325
00:32:41,28 --> 00:32:43,99
我要把黄四郎连根都拔掉
to rid of Huang once and for all

2326
00:32:44,88 --> 00:32:46,23
给我点时间
Give me time,

2327
00:32:47,24 --> 00:32:50,67
六子，爹发誓一定给你报仇！
Pop will avenge your death.

2328
00:32:55,40 --> 00:32:56,79
把脸收拾收拾
Show your respect!

2329
00:32:58,00 --> 00:33:00,07
六爷，一路走好
Have a safe journey, Six.

2330
00:33:00,80 --> 00:33:03,55
六爷，一路走好！
Safe travel, Six!

2331
00:33:08,56 --> 00:33:09,91
先打哪一张牌？
How should I play my hand?

2332
00:33:11,00 --> 00:33:15,07
请客、斩首、收下当狗！
Banquet, kill him or throw him to the dogs?

2333
00:33:15,24 --> 00:33:15,91
斩！
I'd say kill him!

2334
00:33:16,08 --> 00:33:16,91
错！
No!

2335
00:33:17,08 --> 00:33:18,14
错？
No?

2336
00:33:18,76 --> 00:33:20,11
请客！
Host a banquet!

2337
00:33:20,84 --> 00:33:22,51
鸿门宴！凶多吉少
Dinner invitation! It's a death trap!

2338
00:33:22,68 --> 00:33:24,95
杀人诛心，赫然奏效！
Our ploy is working!

2339
00:33:25,12 --> 00:33:26,39
我再送你一个字
I have another idea: delay tactics.

2340
00:33:26,60 --> 00:33:28,79
拉！拉得越久，赚得越多
The longer we drag this on the better!

2341
00:33:28,96 --> 00:33:31,03
到时候跪在这儿的就是黄四郎本人
Huang will end up kneeling here.

2342
00:33:31,20 --> 00:33:32,55
什么鸿门宴！
What kind of banquet is this?

2343
00:38:26,52 --> 00:38:30,75
这小子到底在哪呢？
Where is he, then?

2344
00:38:30,92 --> 00:38:33,51
听黄爷给咱们聊聊
Let Master Huang enlightens us.

2345
00:38:33,92 --> 00:38:36,67
此人盘踞鹅城周边交通咽喉
He has grabbed Goose Town by its balls!

2346
00:28:49,20 --> 00:28:51,31
你要是肚子里只有一碗粉
If there's only one,

2347
00:28:51,52 --> 00:28:53,23
我死！
I'll die.

2348
00:28:55,56 --> 00:28:58,67
要是有两碗粉，我陪六爷一起死
If he has two bowls in him, I'll die with him!

2349
00:28:59,04 --> 00:29:00,55
凉粉呢？
Where's the jelly?

2350
00:29:01,44 --> 00:29:05,31
太浅了，我看不见
Deeper! I can't see.

2351
00:29:09,12 --> 00:29:10,87
六爷！佩服！
Very gutsy, sir!

2352
00:29:11,04 --> 00:29:14,15
凉粉在肠子里，你得横着拉一下
Try sliding the blade sideway,

2353
00:42:28,24 --> 00:42:30,31
你们可以把我供出来嘛！
Implicate me for all you like.

2354
00:42:30,68 --> 00:42:32,27
不要委屈自己哦！
I couldn't care less!

2355
00:42:32,44 --> 00:42:36,39
马县长，我早看出，你非等闲之辈
Governor. I sense that you're special.

2356
00:42:36,60 --> 00:42:37,15
不敢当
I am flattered.

2357
00:42:37,32 --> 00:42:39,88
不过，有胆子剿匪的人
But those who waged war on the bandits,

2358
00:42:40,04 --> 00:42:41,67
九死一生
none has survived.

2359
00:42:41,84 --> 00:42:44,14
哦，何以见得？
Why not?

2360
00:42:44,32 --> 00:42:46,99
张麻子非同凡人
Pocky Zhang is a tough cookie.

2361
00:42:48,32 --> 00:42:52,15
二十年前，我们有过一面之缘
I met him once 20 years ago.

2362
00:42:53,40 --> 00:42:55,51
竟有如此的缘分
Isn't that fate?

2363
00:42:56,52 --> 00:42:59,35
那么，缘从何起呢？
How did it happen?

2364
00:42:59,60 --> 00:43:02,83
灯火阑珊，他蓦然回首
He stood by a lantern and turned towards me,

2365
00:43:03,00 --> 00:43:06,78
而我，却隐藏在灯影里
and I was standing in the shade.

2366
00:43:07,88 --> 00:43:09,39
一个在明处
He was well lit up,

2367
00:43:09,68 --> 00:43:10,59
一个在暗处
and you're in the dark!

2368
00:35:17,12 --> 00:35:19,27
当我的介错人
to ritualistically cut my head off

2369
00:35:19,64 --> 00:35:23,59
砍下我人头，高挂艳阳楼顶！
and hang it from the restaurant.

2370
00:35:28,20 --> 00:35:29,31
万一不是我
If I'm proven innocent,

2371
00:35:29,52 --> 00:35:32,67
那就是辱我名声
those who slandered me

2372
00:35:33,08 --> 00:35:34,71
欺骗县长
and shamed you in the process...

2373
00:35:36,60 --> 00:35:37,43
你们自裁
will have to kill themselves.

2374
00:35:37,64 --> 00:35:40,99
要么三命抵一命，要么随时告发我
It's me against these three.

2375
00:35:41,16 --> 00:35:42,99
我随时死
I am ready.

2376
00:35:49,16 --> 00:35:52,75
黄老爷，我听说自裁用短刀
You should use this for disembowelment.

2377
00:35:53,00 --> 00:35:54,59
长刀归介错人
The full blade is for your second.

2378
00:35:54,76 --> 00:35:55,79
是吗？
Really?

2379
00:35:58,24 --> 00:36:03,59
果然在行！县长随时可以当我的介错人
It's great to have an expert as my second!

2380
00:36:05,72 --> 00:36:07,51
马县长，请！
This way, please.

2381
00:38:55,60 --> 00:38:57,35
黄老爷还是条大腿
And Master is the most able one!

2382
00:38:57,56 --> 00:38:59,27
对！大腿！
Yes, the strongest one!

2383
00:38:59,44 --> 00:39:00,87
可是我这条腿…
But this runner,

2384
00:39:01,04 --> 00:39:02,15
断了！
is now crippled!

2385
00:39:02,60 --> 00:39:03,11
断了？
Crippled?

2386
00:39:03,28 --> 00:39:03,83
怎么断的？
What happened?

2387
00:39:04,00 --> 00:39:07,23
我的货十回有八回被张麻子劫走了！
Zhang has seized nearly all my goods.

2388
00:39:07,40 --> 00:39:09,83
你想想，他赚了多少钱？
Imagine what he can make from them.

2389
00:39:10,00 --> 00:39:12,07
那这个张麻子很富有啊！
He must be very well off!

2390
00:39:12,24 --> 00:39:13,63
还有这种事儿？
I wonder if this is true.

2391
00:39:14,12 --> 00:39:16,71
如果你们可以去剿匪的话
You can write your own cheque,

2392
00:39:16,88 --> 00:39:19,39
钱要多少有多少
if you can take him out!

2393
00:39:19,60 --> 00:39:21,43
我们没胆子剿匪
We wouldn't dare to!

2394
00:39:21,68 --> 00:39:24,19
但是，借剿匪之名敛财的胆子
But if this can make us rich,

2395
00:39:24,36 --> 00:39:26,43
还是有，而且很大！
I wouldn't mind having a go!

2396
00:39:28,36 --> 00:39:31,79
那就不要怪我！就怪你们没出息
Then blame yourself for your timidity!

2397
00:39:32,08 --> 00:39:34,75
不过，我还可以帮你们一个忙
But I would be happy to assist.

2398
00:39:34,92 --> 00:39:36,99
我出钱，当诱饵
I can put up money as a bait.

2399
00:39:37,16 --> 00:39:40,94
我出多少，两大家族必须出多少！
The families have to match my contribution.

2400
00:39:41,12 --> 00:39:43,68
就等您这句话呢！足够！
We're hoping you'd say that.

2401
00:39:43,84 --> 00:39:45,19
那您出八十万？
How about $800,000?

2402
00:39:45,32 --> 00:39:48,15
不！我出一百八十万
No! I'll put up $1.8 million!

2403
00:39:48,32 --> 00:39:50,19
出得多，赚得多！
The more the merrier!

2404
00:43:33,36 --> 00:43:35,43
不会是脸上的麻子吧
You mean his facial scars?

2405
00:43:35,64 --> 00:43:36,75
当然不是
Of course not.

2406
00:43:37,16 --> 00:43:38,30
那么是什么呢？
Then what is it?

2407
00:40:46,04 --> 00:40:47,99
你还聊钱是吧？不聊接腿？
If you want to settle the split now,

2408
00:40:48,16 --> 00:40:49,38
那你们俩聊吧
then just carry on.

2409
00:40:49,88 --> 00:40:51,43
师爷，你定
Counselor, you decide.

2410
00:40:52,44 --> 00:40:53,66
先聊钱吧
About the dollars,

2411
00:40:53,84 --> 00:40:56,11
钱到手，按照惯例，三七分
Iet's do a customary 30-70 split.

2412
00:40:56,28 --> 00:40:58,71
你也太不仗义了吧！
How can you even say that?

2413
00:40:58,88 --> 00:41:01,44
黄老爷为这事忙前忙后
Master Huang is so instrumental.

2414
00:41:01,64 --> 00:41:04,02
你就分人家三成？
And you give him only 30%?

2415
00:41:04,92 --> 00:41:07,03
怎么也得对半分啊！
Let's go 50-50!

2416
00:41:10,40 --> 00:41:11,87
那我…那我错了
My apologies, Master Huang.

2417
00:41:12,04 --> 00:41:12,99
你太错了
So inconsiderate!

2418
00:41:13,16 --> 00:41:14,19
师爷
Counselor,

2419
00:41:14,36 --> 00:41:17,79
我们还是听县长的，对半分
I'll go along with that: 50-50.

2420
00:41:19,04 --> 00:41:20,95
如果真有胆子剿匪
If you've the guts to take on the bandits,

2421
00:41:21,12 --> 00:41:23,03
两大家族的钱
the dollars from the two families,

2422
00:41:23,96 --> 00:41:25,15
就值一根毛
are but strands of hair!

2423
00:41:25,32 --> 00:41:25,91
一根毛！
Strands of hair!

2424
00:41:26,08 --> 00:41:27,79
哪是一根啊！
May not be even that!

2425
00:41:28,00 --> 00:41:29,91
胆子你是有的
I know you have the courage.

2426
00:41:30,28 --> 00:41:31,26
本事呢？
But ability-wise...?

2427
00:41:31,44 --> 00:41:35,51
我凭什么相信你能剿张麻子？
How do I know if you can overcome Zhang?

2428
00:41:36,44 --> 00:41:39,39
黄老爷，容兄弟问你个问题
May I ask you a question, sir?

2429
00:41:39,60 --> 00:41:40,15
请
Go ahead.

2430
00:41:40,32 --> 00:41:42,88
张麻子能劫你的货
If Zhang can seize your goods,

2431
00:41:43,04 --> 00:41:44,99
为什么不能进你的家呢？
why can't he break in here?

2432
00:41:45,16 --> 00:41:48,70
我这碉楼，固若金汤
My citadel is impregnable.

2433
00:41:48,88 --> 00:41:51,51
易守难攻，他进不来！
There's no way that he can get in.

2434
00:41:51,68 --> 00:41:53,71
那你怎么就真的相信
Are you sure

2435
00:41:53,88 --> 00:41:56,95
只有我跟师爷进了你的碉楼呢？
that we're the only ones here?

2436
00:42:04,32 --> 00:42:05,27
说让咱们撤？
An order to retreat!

2437
00:42:05,44 --> 00:42:06,95
撤？ 那撤么？
- Split? - You sure?

2438
00:42:07,16 --> 00:42:08,14
撤
Let's split.

2439
00:42:10,52 --> 00:42:12,95
“遵命，但我很担心你”
"Chief, watch your back."

2440
00:42:13,12 --> 00:42:14,15
听见了吧？
Did you hear that?

2441
00:42:14,40 --> 00:42:15,11
听见了
Yes.

2442
00:42:15,28 --> 00:42:18,67
张麻子进不来的地方，我能进来
Where Pocky fails to breach, I succeeded!

2443
00:42:18,84 --> 00:42:22,07
张麻子不想死的时候，我能让他死
I can kill him when he is least expecting it.

2444
00:42:27,60 --> 00:42:28,07
又死一个！
Another one bites the dust!

2445
02:06:39,80 --> 02:06:41,23
好，保重大哥
Chief, take care.

2446
02:06:41,44 --> 02:06:41,91
保重
Take care.

2447
02:06:42,00 --> 02:06:42,79
大哥再见
Goodbye, Chief!

2448
02:06:44,68 --> 02:06:45,82
大哥再见
Bye, Chief!

2449
02:06:48,60 --> 02:06:49,74
再见大哥
Bye, Chief!

2450
02:06:54,92 --> 02:06:58,23
张麻子！
"Pocky" Zhang!

2451
02:07:19,16 --> 02:07:23,51
老六，老二，师爷，夫人
Six, Two, Counselor, Madam...

2452
02:07:23,68 --> 02:07:25,11
你们看到了吧
Did you see that?

2453
02:08:13,36 --> 02:08:15,82
老三，去上海还是浦东？
Three, Shanghai or Pudong?

2454
02:08:16,64 --> 02:08:19,10
老三，去浦东还是上海？
Three, Pudong or Shanghai?

